{"_id":"05kZRxohecDDT5LP","name":"魂刃（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_bastion_rogue1.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<p><q>我也有让我的思想以割伤人们的能力，我将这份力量称为——言语。</q></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>——塔莎</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>绝大多数的刺客都用物理的武器袭击，而许多的夜贼和密探利用盗贼工具来潜入安全的位置。与他们相反，一个魂刃者利用心灵的力量来攻击和渗透，击穿阻碍他们的物理和心灵障碍。这些游荡者们从内心之中发掘出灵能之力，并且引导灵能来协助他们的老本行。尽管有些游荡者极力排斥“奇怪的心灵力量”，并对使用这一力量经营生意的魂刃者表示怀疑，但魂刃者依然能轻易成为盗贼行会的一员，同时大多数政府也乐意雇佣他们作为间谍。</p>\n<p>在物质界和妖精荒野的古老森林中，一些木精灵踏上了魂刃者之道，使他们成为森林中无声而致命的守护者。在吉斯人永无止境的战争中，当吉斯瑟雷人需要对吉斯洋基仇敌进行秘密行动时，他们会被鼓励成为魂刃者。</p>\n<p>身为一名魂刃者，你的灵能可能从你还是个孩子的时候就一直伴随着你，直到你在面临冒险的压力时才显露潜能。或者你可能找到了一个隐居的灵能修士团，花了很多年的时间学习如何显现你的力量。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游荡者等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"0DjKOCFyAb5mljbS","name":"神力掌控 Harness Divine Power","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_FlashHeal.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以花费一次你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.WPevnsjK8Cjd9Fcl]{引导神力}次数来充能你的法术。你可以用一个附赠动作触碰你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.TJi1q6Bm8IGoJJVL]{圣徽}并祈祷，你恢复一个环阶不超过你熟练加值的一半（向上取整）的法术位。</p>\n<p> </p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"ceil(@prof._baseProficiency/2)","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"牧师等级 2、6、18","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"0GTSK4qqF2k6C3HN","name":"剑咏者 Bladesinging（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/INV_Weapon_Shortblade_99.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>剑咏者一开始是作为一个剑术和魔法相结合的艺术，一把剑，更具体来说长剑是剑咏者的基础。然而经过一代又一代的学习与发展，各种各样的基于近战武器发展出的剑歌风格出现了。这些不同风格的知识在各种不同的小学校中由导师一代一代传承给学徒们。即使最新创造出的风格也有着上百年的历史，但是由于精灵们拥有着漫长的生命，最初的创造者仍可以亲自传承他们所创造的风格。大部分剑咏者的学校坐落在永聚岛或者埃弗拉斯卡。曾经有一所学校坐落在密斯卓诺，但是由于城市的毁灭，那些幸存下来的学徒们已经走失分散在世界各地。</p>\n<p>剑歌的风格种类基于武器运用的类型以及分别对应的动物类型来分别。这些特定的风格类型通过偏爱法术类型的运用，导师技艺的风格和特殊武器的运用来用特定的动物类型进行命名。剑咏者学徒们通常会得到一个他们所选择导师风格的动物纹身。一些剑咏者会学习多种剑歌风格，并获得许多的纹身，通过他们皮肤上的纹身警告那些不怀好意的人，他们拥有着致命的技艺。</p>\n<p> </p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"法师等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"0MMEa2Ks0eC5Gvs9","name":"哀惧灵袭 Dreadful Strikes","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_ardenweald_warrior.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你能够使用来自妖精荒原中黑暗空洞的摄心魔法以强化你的武器攻击。当你使用武器命中一个生物时，你可以对目标造成额外的[[/r 1d4]]心灵伤害，一个目标一回合只能够受到一次这个伤害。该额外伤害在你的游侠升到11级时变成[[/r 1d6]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d(ceil(@classes.ranger.levels/10)*2+2)","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"妖精漫游者等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"0MpOWyxcdeRCw42w","name":"优异灵活 Superior Mobility","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Kick.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在9级时，你的行走速度增加10尺。若你具有攀爬或游泳速度，这个能力也会增加在这些速度上。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"斥候等级 9","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"dKVSbIhkPKwKYLNX","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.movement.walk","mode":2,"value":"10"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Kick.png","label":"增加 10 尺步行速度","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.0MpOWyxcdeRCw42w","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"0dvnmcfFn2Nf1DMP","name":"渗透者 Infiltrator","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/images/b_64.PNG","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>　　任何被你@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.E06roEzIAhw8cXnY]{闪电发射器}造成闪电伤害的生物将在你的下个回合到来前发光。发光的生物会放出 5 尺半径的微光光照，当它试图攻击你时，光芒会突然增强，使其在针对你的攻击检定中具有劣势。另外，下次针对发光生物的攻击检定具有优势。如果那次攻击命中，将额外造成[[/r 1d6]]闪电伤害。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","lightning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"装甲师等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"0eSDePMWApq9RHqv","name":"念力擅长 Telekinetic Adept","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_socererking_arcanereplication.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你已经掌握了使用念力异能的新方式，细节如下。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.6s7P6OwuQlVpfnDQ]{灵力跃动 Psi-Powered Leap}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.dkpQJsciaVomruu7]{念力突刺 Telekinetic Thrust}</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"灵能武士等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"0eaSz6EHRtN6yv8o","name":"驾驭神力 Harness Divine Power","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Priest_DivineStar_Holy.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>　　你能够消耗一次@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.3J9VuFAJehLvYKHX]{引导神力}的使用次数来驱动法术。以一个附赠动作，你能够通过接触@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.TJi1q6Bm8IGoJJVL]{圣徽}，并献上祈祷，来恢复一个已消耗的法术位，其环数不能超过你的一半熟练加值（向上取整）。你能使用此能力的次数取决于你的圣武士等级。3级1次，7级2次，15级3次。当你完成一次长休时，你重新获得已消耗的使用次数。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"floor((@classes.paladin.levels+1)/8)+1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"ceil(@prof._baseProficiency/2)","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"圣武士等级 3，7，15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"0eyURezkOgpPkTf5","name":"原初学识 Primal Knowledge","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_shaman_giftearthmother.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你的野蛮人职业等级达到3级和10级时，你可以从野蛮人1级所提供的技能熟练项列表中选择一个技能，获得该技能的熟练。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"野蛮人等级 3，10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"0ojpWyRTzAiDiaSg","name":"灵能武士 Psi Warrior（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_AuraOfLight.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>觉醒了内在心灵力量的灵能战士使用灌注灵能力量的武器攻击、念力鞭挞和灵能屏障来强化自己肉体力量的战士。很多吉斯洋基人受训成为这样的战士，一些极度自律的高等精灵也会这么做。在艾伯伦的世界中，许多年轻的离梦人（kalashtar）梦想着成为灵能武士。</p>\n<p>作为一个灵能武士，你必须通过极度的自律来磨砺灵能力量，在一个大师的指导下觉醒，或在一个学院中精进对于灵能粉尘化为武器或盾牌力量的掌握。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"0uLaKVQh12z0TOMj","name":"命流宗 Way of Mercy（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Monk_TouchofKarma.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>命流宗的武僧们习得了如何操纵他人的生命能量来帮助那些需要帮助的人。他们四处流浪，为穷人和伤员提供医疗。然而，对于那些无可救药之人——无论是生性邪恶，还是病入膏肓——他们施予仁慈的方式会改变为给个痛快。</p>\n<p>那些遵循命流之道的人可能是一名谦卑的教会成员，施予他人最需要的帮助，做出植根于现实而非理想的严峻抉择。一些人可能是和颜悦色的治疗师，受到所住社区的喜爱，而另一些可能是带来痛快之死的蒙面人。</p>\n<p>命流宗的人通常穿着简单的长袍，戴着厚厚的头巾，常常用面具遮住自己的脸，把自己表现成一名无貌的生死判官。如果你戴着面具，请选择它的外观，或利用命流面具表格通过掷骰来决定。</p>\n<h3><strong>命流之器 Implements of Mercy</strong></h3>\n<p>你获得洞悉和医药技能熟练项，以及你获得@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.2B61FBFC173EAEA3]{草药工具}的熟练项。</p>\n<p>你还可以获得一个特殊的面具，当你使用这个子职的特性时，你通常会戴着它。你可以自由决定它的外观，或者通过命流面具表来投骰随机决定。</p>\n<h3><strong>命流面具</strong></h3>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>[[/r D6]]</th>\n<th>面具</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>渡鸦</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>黑白</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>哭脸</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>笑脸</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>骷髅</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>蝴蝶</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"武僧等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"6rtvTZ9OwF0UV3Gt","changes":[{"key":"data.skills.ins.value","mode":4,"value":"1"},{"key":"data.skills.med.value","mode":4,"value":"1"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Monk_TouchofKarma.png","label":"获得洞悉、医疗熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.0uLaKVQh12z0TOMj","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null},{"_id":"mOHErGMJQ9MqzsJv","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.toolProf.value","mode":2,"value":"herb"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Monk_TouchofKarma.png","label":"获得草药工具熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.0uLaKVQh12z0TOMj","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
