{"_id":"1E19Tn2jHof6kqSZ","name":"凝神聚气Focused Aim","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_monk_domeofmist.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>当你攻击检定未命中时，你可以花费1到3点气来使该次攻击检定获得加值，每点气的消耗能获得+2加值，这可能会使原本的未命中改为命中。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":"攻击检定未命中；1 到 3 点气。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"武僧等级 5","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"1IPJQatumXftq8Q0","name":"警觉赐福 Vigilant Blessing","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_shadow_twistedfaith.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>夜晚教会了你时刻保持警惕。你能用一个动作触碰一个生物（包括你自己），并赋予该生物下次先攻检定优势。此增益在该生物骰先攻检定或你再次使用此特性后立刻结束。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"暮光领域等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"1NDFlKVd6mm6K1Fs","name":"超魔法选项Metamagic Options","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/red_25.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你选择超魔法选项时，你能够选择以下超魔法选项。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.l4lNH8vyG9P8hyPv]{超魔法：转化法术}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.Opql2v9FQ3knZ7nh]{超魔法：追踪法术}</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"术士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"1OH2IVGfO4fYd5y6","name":"野火结社 Circle of Wildfire（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_racial_foregedinflames.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>野火结社的德鲁伊们知晓破坏有时是创造的先驱，就如森林大火促进之后的生长。</p>\n<p>这些德鲁伊们与具有破坏力与创造力的原始精魂连接在一起，使德鲁伊能够创造出可控的火焰，焚烧某样事物却又给予它者生命。</p>\n<h3><strong>结社法术 Circle Spells</strong></h3>\n<p>你与野火精魂——一位兼具创生和毁灭的原初存在——之间的神秘连接业已形成。当你在此职业到达特定等级时，你与精魂的连接使你获取了一些特定法术的使用权，就如野火结社法术列表所示。</p>\n<p>一旦你获得了其中某个法术的使用权，你就会一直准备着它，且不计入你的每日准备法术上限。如果你学会一个不在德鲁伊法术列表中的法术，该法术对你来说视作德鲁伊法术。</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>2nd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.CB9z74KJLWMplGuz]{燃烧之手}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.a5wqDP53A5UvGvSK]{疗伤术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.TEZY0aYJtnuU4FlW]{炽焰法球}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.IkgKSSiBuGa5TPLB]{灼热射线 }</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.1TP8dARdcRojx7P1]{植物滋长}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.TkFsGmyAeHknESJ4]{回生术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.9WDd3gopYOGyYnrT]{生命灵光}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.AdWubx1kFJLe8QDa]{火焰护盾}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Q8XNvy4kwTSQVizo]{焰击术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.UBLAtJuRhRB3GokC]{群体疗伤术}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"德鲁伊等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"1ViKFKTqfFSHAiM5","name":"原始意识 Primal Awareness","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Druid_NaturalPerfection.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<p>替代@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.7ogU5SrAvrawwEr5]{原初意识}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>       你可以通过与自然的共鸣而集中你的意识：若你尚未习得下方表格种的法术，那么你在抵达对应等级时学会下方原始意识法术表格中的法术。这些法术不占用你的游侠已知法术。</p>\n<p>　　你每天可以施展这些对应的法术每个一次而不需要消耗法术位，一旦你用这种方式施法，你在完成一次长休前不能再这么做。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>游侠等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.3JUEqJSbgArlUBR5]{动物交谈}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.aCbWarazGEZ7fMnd]{野兽知觉}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.n61LzTyqnbhiYxre]{植物交谈}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.s9CC5wvKMHq42hPY]{生物定位术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.tnDSVQwVqkmqWFPP]{问道自然}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 92","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"spec"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"游侠等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"1d0UIp7RHG48TRBU","name":"灿若繁星 Full of Stars","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003556.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>当你处于星耀形态时，你的身体部分无实质化，使你对钝击，穿刺和劈砍伤害具有抗性。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"星辰结社等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"lClO9mjbo4nPjT8W","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"bludgeoning"},{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"piercing"},{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"slashing"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003556.png","label":"获得钝击，穿刺、劈砍抗性","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.1d0UIp7RHG48TRBU","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"1gcaaO8XwATHOiaM","name":"强化链接 Enhanced Bond","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/inv_misc_volatilefire.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>你与野火精魂的连接增强了你的破坏与恢复法术。</p>\n<p>当你在野火精魂处于召唤状态下施展一个造成火焰伤害或回复生命值的法术时，骰一个[[/r d8]]，你在该法术的一次掷骰时获得等同于骰出数值的加值。</p>\n<p>此外，当你施展一个射程非自身的法术时，该法术可以源自你或你的野火精魂。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"d8","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"野火结社等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"1ijPpQjLqsCpk3E8","name":"历经死亡 Among The Dead","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_deathwing_bloodcorruption_death.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从1级起，你学会戏法@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.EslxcnZE2B9JYgF1]{维生术}，并将它视作一个邪术士戏法。你同时在对任何疾病的豁免上具有优势。<br />        此外，不死生物将更难伤害你。若有不死生物直接指定你为攻击或者有害法术的目标，这个生物必须进行一次感知豁免来对抗你的施法DC（但他不需要在使用包括你在内的区域能力时进行豁免，比如@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Uh3zcz4PO4DXP3Dj]{火球术}）。若失败，这个生物必须选择一个新的目标，如果他没有除你以外的目标可以选择则他失去这次法术或者攻击。若他成功通过了豁免，或者你以他为目标进行攻击或者施放有害法术，那么这个不死生物在接下来24小时里对这个效果免疫。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"不朽者等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"287BQYB3OGGZhVth","name":"索命镰 Hour of Reaping","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/1Ability_Mage_NetherWindPresence%20-%20.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从6级起，你可以展现出你灵魂本质中的死亡阴影，使周围的人感到惊惧和恐慌。</p>\n<p>以一个动作，你使距离你30尺内的所有能看见你的生物立即进行一次感知豁免。若豁免失败，他们将对你恐慌直到你的下回合结束。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"wis","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"wis"},"requirements":"永亡宗等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2JSV2d5Xm2DBvXFz","name":"醉人表演 Enthralling Performance","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_Fanaticism.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从3级起，你能将诱惑力和妖精的魔法充入你的表演。若你表演至少1分钟，你可以尝试通过歌唱，吟诗或舞蹈的方式来让你的观众们感受到美。在这次表演的结束时，选择一定数量的类人生物，他们需要处于你周围60尺内，并完整的观看并聆听了你的表演，可以选择的数量至多等于你的魅力调整值（至少1个）。每个目标必须通过一次感知豁免检定，对抗你的法术豁免DC，否则被你魅惑。当被你以此法魅惑时，目标视你为偶像，他会热情的和任何和他交谈的人谈论你，反对任何对抗你的人，他会避免暴力，除非他已经站在你这边加入了战斗。此效果在一个目标上持续1小时，或当他受到任何伤害，你攻击他，以及他目睹你对任何他的盟友进行攻击或造成伤害时结束。</p>\n<p>         若一个目标在对抗此效果的豁免检定中成功，该目标对于你试图魅惑他的行为没有任何察觉。</p>\n<p>         一旦你使用此特性，直到你完成了一次短休或长休前，你都不能再次使用它。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"minute","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"迷惑学院等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2JbjMYpSiJM5QotY","name":"召唤野火精魂 Summon Wildfire Spirit","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_racial_fireresist.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>你能召唤出与你灵魂连接的原初精魂。以一个动作，你可以消耗一次@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.pORTgCToV9NLPWo1]{荒野形态}使用次数召唤你的野火精魂，而不是变化为野兽形态。</p>\n<p>精魂出现在你所选择的距离你 30 尺内未被占据的可见空间内。每个精魂 10 尺内的生物（除你之外）在它出现时都必须成功一次对抗你法术豁免 DC 的敏捷豁免否则受到[[/r 2d6]]火焰伤害。</p>\n<p>野火精魂对你与你的同伴保持友善并遵从你的命令。在野火精魂资料表中可以看到这只生物的游戏数据，其中几处采用了你的熟练加值（PB）。由你来决定精魂的外形。一些精魂是熊熊燃烧的枝条虬结而成的人形，而另一些则像是被火焰包裹的野兽。</p>\n<p>在战斗中，野火精魂与你使用同一先攻，但在你的回合之后紧接着行动。它仅能使用回避动作，除非你使用一个附赠动作命令它采取其他动作。那个动作可以是其资料表上的一个，也可以是其他动作。如果你陷入失能，精魂可以采取任何它选择的动作，不只是回避。</p>\n<p>野火精魂持续存在 1 小时，直到其生命值降低至 0，或直到你再次使用此特性召唤此精魂，或直到你死亡。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":10,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d6","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"野火结社等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2Rgb3ND4IL7eMZgg","name":"显现回音 Manifest Echo","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Magic_LesserInvisibilty.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从3级起，你能使用一个附赠动作来在你可见的15尺内，一处尚未被占据的空间处，魔法地显现一个你自身的回音。该回音是魔法的，半透明的，形如你的黑白形象，回音持续直到被摧毁、你用一个附赠动作消解、显现另一个回音，或你处于失能状态。</p>\n<p>         你的回音的AC值为14+你的熟练值，生命值为1，并对所有的状态都免疫。如果回音要进行一次豁免，它在这次豁免中使用你的豁免调整值。它的体型和你一样，并且会占据空间。在你的回合时，你能精神地命令回音朝任意方向移动至多30尺（无需动作）。如果你的回音在你的回合结束时远离你超过30尺，那么它会被摧毁。<br />         你能按照以下方法使用回音：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>使用一个附赠动作，你能消耗15尺的移动力进行传送，魔法地与你的回音交换位置，且无论回音与你之间的距离。</li>\n<li>当你在你的回合里进行攻击动作时，你用该动作进行的任何攻击可以用你或回音的空间作为源点。每一次攻击的源点都由你决定。</li>\n<li>当一个位于你的回音5尺内，且你可见的生物远离回音至少5尺时，你能用你的反应动作来对该生物进行一次借机攻击，就如同你位于回音的空间上一样。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EGtW","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":15,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"回音骑士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2dqkKB0KNItEKuCk","name":"壁垒之力 Bulwark of Force","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_mage_focusingcrystal.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>你可以使用念力庇护你自己和其他人。你可以使用一个附赠动作选择一些可包括你在内且30尺对你可见生物，数量等于你的智力调整值（最少为1）。每个被选中的生物获得一分钟的半掩蔽状态，该状态将会在你失能时提前结束。</p>\n<p>每当你使用这个附赠动作，你无法再次使用该特性直到你完成一次长休，除非你消耗一个灵能骰来再次使用该特性。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"灵能武士等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2emodcKE6ZwTnbhg","name":"瞬时静止 Momentary Stasis","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Mage_TimeWarp.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从6级起，以一个动作，你可以魔法地迫使60尺内你可以看见的一个大型或更小的生物进行一次对抗你法术豁免DC的体质豁免检定。若失败，该生物将被禁锢于一个魔法力场中，直至你的下回合结束或者该生物受到任何伤害。当以此法被禁锢时，该生物陷入失能，并且速度被降至0。</p>\n<p>          你可以使用这一特性等同于你智力调整值的次数（至少一次）。你在完成一次长休后重获所有已消耗的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EGtW","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"可以看见的一个大型或更小的生物。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"max(@abilities.int.mod,1)","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"时间魔法等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2h9mW7HNrl1CO8Mu","name":"风暴之心 Heart of the Storm","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Warlock_SiphonLife.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从6级起，你对闪电和雷鸣伤害获得抗性。每当你施展一个1环或以上且造成闪电或雷鸣伤害的法术时，猛烈的魔法从你身体内爆发而出。这次爆发导致所有10尺内你选择的可见生物（每次使用此能力都指定），都承受等于你术士等级一半的闪电或雷鸣伤害。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":"施展一个1环或以上且造成闪电或雷鸣伤害的法术时。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["floor(@classes.sorcerer.levels/2)","lightning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"狂怒风暴等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"dR4bH7aTKnYE7WKk","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"lightning"},{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"thunder"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Warlock_SiphonLife.png","label":"获得闪电、雷鸣抗性","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.2h9mW7HNrl1CO8Mu","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2hMuY5PjvH1Nc345","name":"黑夜明目 Eyes of Night","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_Sentinal.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你的双眼可以洞穿最深沉的黑暗。你获得300尺的黑暗视觉，而你的视力在微光光照下视为等同于明亮光照，而在黑暗中则视为等同于微光光照。</p>\n<p>以一个动作，你可以用魔法将这个特性分享给你10尺内最多等同于你感知调整值数量（最少1名生物）的可见自愿生物。共享的黑暗视觉持续1小时。一旦如此做，直到你完成一次长休或消耗一个任意环阶的法术位，你无法再次分享此特性。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"暮光领域等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"R3XQwDd6tSSl4su8","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.senses.darkvision","mode":4,"value":"300"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_Sentinal.png","label":"获得 300 尺黑暗视觉","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.2hMuY5PjvH1Nc345","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2mHUbEdRsx9jwwOb","name":"幽影魔法 Shadow Magic（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_mage_GreaterInvisibility.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你是一个幽影的生物, 你内在的魔力来自堕影冥界本身。你可以把你的世系追溯到那个地方实存的某处， 又或者你将自己暴露在了它的能量之下并被其所改变。暗影魔法的力量给你的肉身蒙上了一层怪异的柩衣。维持你生命的火花被抑制，犹如它为了存留而挣扎着与灌输了你灵魂的黑暗力量对抗。在你的选择下，你可以从下列幽影术士异闻表中自选或投掷出属于自己角色的特点。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>“有时候，当我看到自己的影子时我会对他用离解射线。因为我以为那是另一只眼魔。”</p>\n<p><em>——珊娜萨</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>[[/r d6]]</th>\n<th>异闻</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>你摸起来一直是冰冷的。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>当你熟睡时看上去没有呼吸。（尽管你需要呼吸来维生。）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>你很少流血，即使受了重伤。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>你的心脏一分钟才脉动一下，有时候你自己都感到吃惊。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>你难以记住生物和尸体应该被区别对待。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>你上周只眨了一次眼。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"术士等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2qyvDJtbsF8bGjnQ","name":"预备射击 Ever-ready Shot","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_Efficiency.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         15级起，每当战斗开始时，你都可以使用你的魔法箭术。如果你投了先攻骰且没有任何@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.w3EVK3XBgi1HZ5K2]{奥术射击}使用次数，你重新获得一次使用机会。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魔射手等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"33uiZeA8YUJ27xSh","name":"憎恨灵光 Aura of Hate","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Fire_BlueFire.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         7级起，该圣武士本身，以及其身边 10 尺内的所有邪魔和不死生物，都将获的与该圣武士魅力调整值相同(至少为+1)的近战武器伤害掷骰加值。一个生物一次只能从一名圣武士的该特性中获益。</p>\n<p>         第18级时，该灵光的覆盖范围增加至 30 尺。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"破誓者等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"384mTNKNQe0BgK5C","name":"额外圣武士法术 Additional Paladin Spells","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/light_03.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>　　下表中的法术扩充了圣武士在玩家手册中的法术列表。此列表以法术环数而非角色等级排序。以下法术均存在于玩家手册中，除非其标有星号*（这说明该法术来自TCE的第三章）。珊娜萨的万事指南同样提供了更多可使用的新法术。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>2环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.uzWirpWyQshzp1l0]{遗体防腐（仪式）}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.9h978cNv0y7ZOepO]{治疗祷言}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.DLyjjM6qTHBCSFCx]{守护之链}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.TH2wXQ3yssrGZ821]{魂灵环绕(TCE)*}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.vYaGuPlgPM3SsUC2]{天界召唤术(TCE)*}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"圣武士等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"39YlsyoJXTtDSGf4","name":"战栗形态Form of Dread","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/achievement_dungeon_hallsofattonement_aleez.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你显现出你宗主可怕力量的一个侧面。作为附赠动作，你变身持续1分钟。变身时你获得以下好处。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你获得相当于1d10+你的邪术师等级的临时生命。</li>\n<li>在你的每个回合中只有一次，当你攻击检定命中一个生物时，你 可以强迫它进行一次感知豁免。若失败，目标会对你恐慌，直到你的下一个回合结束。</li>\n<li>你对恐慌状态免疫。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>你可以变身的次数等于你的熟练值，当你完成长休时，你会恢复所有消耗的次数。</p>\n<p>你战栗形态的外观反映了你宗主的某些方面。例如，你的形态可能是一个阴影纱幕，形成你巫妖宗主的王冠和长袍，或者你的身体开始发光，显现出古代葬礼仪式的符印，并被沙尘旋风所环绕，暗示着你的木乃伊宗主。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"VRGR","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"wis","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d10+1d10+ @classes.warlock.levels","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"死灵宗主等级1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"IQE6hAV3ygaTICtD":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.SoROktB6wHO25o9l"}}}
{"_id":"39vgDk1ARYUxfuoE","name":"勇气联结 Emboldening Bond","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_Crusade.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你创造出一条联结，赋予彼此之间和平相处的人以力量。以一个动作，你可以选择30尺内等同于你熟练加值数量的自愿生物（可以包括你自己）。你在他们之间创造出一条持续10分钟或直到你再次使用该特性的魔法联结。当联结生物在彼此30尺内，其进行攻击检定，属性检定或豁免检定时，可以额外掷一次[[/r d4]]并加在其结果上。每个生物每回合只能加一次[[/r d4]]。</p>\n<p>你可以使用此特性的次数等同于你的熟练加值，当你完成一次长休时恢复所有使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"和平领域等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"3APHcggPa8gRvchw","name":"咒缚幽灵 Accursed Specter","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Shadow_Shadowfiend.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从6级开始，你可以诅咒一个命丧你手者的灵魂，暂时束缚它为你服务。当你杀死一个类人生物，你可以让它的灵魂从尸体出现，成为一个@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.PuPo4H4Dcxigf0fY]{幽灵}，其数据见怪物手册。当幽灵出现时，它获得等同于你邪术士等级一半的临时生命。为幽灵的投掷先攻，它有自己的回合、服从你的口头命令，并获得特殊的命中加值，加值等于你的魅力调整值（最少0）。</p>\n<p>        幽灵一直为你服务中直到你的下一个长休结束，然后它消失进入来世。</p>\n<p>        一旦你用这个特性唤起了一个幽灵，你就不能再次使用该能力直到你完成一次长休。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"咒剑士等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"3NFC4X4zW9fGuJr6","name":"灵能面纱Psychic Veil","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Priest_DivineStar_Shadow2.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>　　你可以编织一层灵能面纱来掩盖你。以一个动作，你连同你所穿或携带的任何东西可以魔法性地隐形至多1小时，或直到你主动解除隐形（无需动作）。如果你发动攻击或迫使一个生物进行豁免检定，则此隐身状态结束。</p>\n<p>　　一旦你使用了此特性，除非你选择消耗一个灵能骰，否则将无法再次使用，直到你完成一次长休。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魂刃等级 13","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"3WduPYXM4xkBwqrz","name":"收束未来 Convergent Future","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/SPELL_HOLY_BORROWEDTIME.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从14级起，你可以透视可能的未来，并魔法地将其中一个未来引导至你周遭发生的事物上，以确保特定的结果发生。当你或60尺内一个你可以看见的生物进行一次攻击检定，属性检定或者豁免检定时，你可以以你的反应来跳过掷骰，直接决定骰子结果将会是使检定成功的最低骰值，或者比该骰值低出一点（由你选择）。</p>\n<p>         当你使用该特性时，你获得一级力竭。你只能通过长休来移除以此法获取的力竭。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EGtW","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"时间魔法等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"3c678QuDLdblTLXm","name":"射手座 Archer","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_Boss_Algalon_01.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>一名弓箭手形态的星座于你身上浮现。你可以使用一个附赠动作进行一次远程法术攻击，对你60尺内可见的一个生物射出一发光箭。命中时，此次攻击造成[[/r 1d8]]+你的感知调整值的光耀伤害。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":60,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"rsak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+ @abilities.wis.mod","radiant"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"星辰结社等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"3enDH0S0L54atap0","name":"往生咒 Touch of Death","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_DeathKnight_DeathSiphon%20-%201.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从3级起，你对死亡的研究使你能在临近的生物逝去前抽取他们的生命力。</p>\n<p>        当你使一个5尺距离内的生物生命值下降到0点时，你得到你的感知调整值+武僧等级的临时生命值（最小1点）。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["max(@abilities.wis.mod + @classes.monk.levels,1)","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"永亡宗等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"3waZF6rwkaUJVGJV","name":"林地之语 Speech of the Woods","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpcloud3steamusercontentcomugc842585608940172239B30BDDD88E6298EA4FFF2EEA58C071309C0C31F1.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>          2级时，你获得了和野兽以及许多精类进行交流的能力。</p>\n<p>         你学会对于木族语的说、读、和写的能力。此外，野兽能理解你的语言，而你也能理解它们的声音和动作。大多数野兽缺乏足够的智力去表述或理解复杂的概念，但友善的野兽可以复述它在最近听到或看到的事物。此能力并不会让你和野兽形成特别的友谊，尽管你可以将此技能与讨好它们的礼物结合使用，就像是你能对其他NPC做的那样。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"牧人之环等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"DR2c9QFKvcqQQiST","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.languages.value","mode":2,"value":"sylvan"},{"key":"data.traits.languages.custom","mode":2,"value":";与野兽交流"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpcloud3steamusercontentcomugc842585608940172239B30BDDD88E6298EA4FFF2EEA58C071309C0C31F1.jpg","label":"习得木族语、野兽交流","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.3waZF6rwkaUJVGJV","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":""}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"43ixbr7CHIZP2QHF","name":"秩序之怒 Order's Wrath","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Paladin_Inquisition.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从 17 级起，你所指定要毁灭的敌人将会在你和你盟友的共同努力之下凋零。如果在你的回合里你对一名生物造成了你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.p3ygdJ5jnwNfzLQL]{神圣打击}的伤害，你可以诅咒该生物直到你下回合的开始。</p>\n<p>         下一次当你的一名盟友以一次攻击击中被诅咒的生物时，目标将额外受到[[/r 2d8]] 心灵伤害，随后诅咒结束。你一回合只能以这种方式诅咒一名生物一次。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GGR","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d8","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"秩序领域等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"4LK5hBpIFgx8ttxC","name":"灵能术法 Psionic Sorcery","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_priest_voidsear.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>6级起，当你施放一个你通过@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.subclass.V4Xk3D90t3HpdL06]{灵能法术}特性知晓的法术时，你可以改为使用等同于该法术环数数量的术法点而非消耗法术位施放该法术。你依然可以用法术位正常施放这些法术。</p>\n<p>当你通过此能力施放法术时，你无视该法术施法需要的语言成分或姿势成分。你同时无视该法术需要的不会消耗的材料成分。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"畸变心智等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"4LvVKKPL68AFJiwL","name":"领导风范 Commanding Presence","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/light_07.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你进行一次魅力（威吓）、魅力（表演）或魅力（说服）检定时，你能够消耗一枚卓越骰，将消耗的卓越骰加入此次属性检定中。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战斗大师等级 3，卓越技巧，战技专家","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"4k8CkHDM05RJUQF4","name":"幽灵漫步Ghost Walk","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_shadow_coneofsilence.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以部分的进入死亡的领域，变得如同一个幽灵。作为一个附赠动作，你化为灵体的形态。处于这种形态时，你拥有10尺的飞行速度，能够盘旋，并且针对你的攻击都具有劣势。你也可以如同是困难地形那样穿过生物或者物品，但是如果回合结束时你仍然在内部，你将受到[[/r 1d10]]点力场伤害。</p>\n<p>该形态持续10分钟或直到你以一个附赠动作将其解除。你再次使用此特性前必须完成一次长休。或者你以同一个附赠动作销毁一个你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.eXk4FM2eHvy3WS67]{魂器}并激活幽灵漫步。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d10","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"鬼魅等级 13","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"vSijTZvtSwJq8sI8","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.movement.fly","mode":4,"value":"10"},{"key":"data.attributes.movement.hover","mode":5,"value":"true"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_shadow_coneofsilence.png","label":"获得 10 尺飞行速度","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.4k8CkHDM05RJUQF4","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"4sBphHebB1yIIcaO","name":"妖冶嫺都 Otherworldly Glamour","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_ardenweald_priest.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你的妖精本质给予了你超脱凡俗的魅力。因此，每当你进行一次魅力检定时，你可以在结果中加入等于你的感知调整值的加值(最低为1)。</p>\n<p>另外，你得到下列技能中你选择的一项的熟练：欺瞒，表演，游说。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"妖精漫游者等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"4xZZ0tToXgEQ8hhs","name":"时械矩阵 Clockwork Cavalcade","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_bastion_paladin.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>18级起，你召唤出秩序的精魂以抹除周遭的混乱。以一个动作，你在以你为中心30尺立方空间的范围内召唤出精魂。这些精魂看起来像是魔冢或你选择的其他构装体，没有实体也不能摧毁，并在消失前使立方范围内产生以下效应：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>精魂合计提供至多回复100生命值，由你随意分配给范围内任意数量的生物。</li>\n<li>范围内受到伤害的物件被立即修复。</li>\n<li>你选择范围内任意数量的生物或物件，其承受的任何6环或以下的法术结束。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>一旦你使用了此能力，你在完成一次长休之前必须消耗7术法点以再次使用此能力。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"cube"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"时械之魂等级 18","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"5FYxkwe3rwfnDmFl","name":"反抗死亡 Defy Death","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Rogue_DeviousPoisons.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从6级起，你为成功欺骗了死亡而感到振奋。当你成功进行一次死亡豁免，或者在你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.EslxcnZE2B9JYgF1]{维生术}帮助其他生物稳定伤势的时候，你可以立即回复[[/r 1d8]]+你的体质调整值（最少为1点）的生命值。<br />        一旦你使用了这个能力，直到一次长休之前你不能再次使用。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":"成功进行一次死亡豁免；或你使用维生术帮其他生物稳定伤势。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"con","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["max(1d8+@mod,1)","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"不朽者等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"5Ihf64ozVvDdDguh","name":"幽影漫步 Shadow Walk","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Fire_TwilightFire.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         14级时，你获得在暗影间穿梭的能力。当你处于微光或黑暗中时，以一个附赠动作你可以魔法地将自己传送至120尺内另一处未被占据并自己可见的微光或黑暗中。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":"处于微光或黑暗中。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"space"},"range":{"value":120,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"幽影魔法等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"5M9eFqLMIbkwKy0b","name":"战斗风格：盲斗","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/light_01.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>        </strong>你获得10尺盲视。在10尺范围内，你可以看见除了处于全遮掩后的任何东西，哪怕你正在被目盲或是在黑暗之中。另外，你可以看见该范围内的未对你成功躲藏的隐形生物。   </p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":"","long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"战士等级 1，勇士等级 10，圣武士等级 2，游侠等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"wa874yOJTDAQmPEy","changes":[{"key":"","mode":2,"value":""}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/light_01.jpg","label":"获得 10 尺盲视","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.5M9eFqLMIbkwKy0b","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"5RpPB6Lwkva1meGG","name":"神圣打击（死亡） Divine Strike","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_shadow_curse.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         第8级时，该牧师可以使其武器打击充满负能量。该牧师在每个其自己回合里有一次机会，可以在用武器攻击命中某生物时额外造成[[/r 1d8]]的黯蚀伤害。第14级时，该伤害提升到[[/r 2d8]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(min(max(floor(((@classes.cleric.levels)-2)/6),1),2))d8","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"死亡领域等级 8","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"5TenPB4x7b6FubXO","name":"引导神力:征服威压 Conquering Presence","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_ShieldoftheTemplar.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你可以使用你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.3eyfqXMTJMG9AxYH]{引导神力}来发出一阵可怕的威压。以一个动作，你强迫每个处于你周围30尺内、你能看见的、由你选择的生物各进行一次感知豁免检定。若豁免失败，目标变得恐慌于你，持续1分钟。变得恐慌的生物可以在其每个回合的结束时重复此豁免检定，成功则结束其身上的此效果。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"征服之誓等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"5XXA79JOX0zakWef","name":"活杀自在Flurry of Healing and Harm","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Monk_ChiCocoon.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你现在能施以疾风般的治疗与伤害。当你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.vLuoFN1x3tRWTPdm]{疾风连击}时，你现在可以用你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.R9VbDJOCQk2Mb9eG]{予命之手}代替每一次徒手打击，而不用花费气来治疗。</p>\n<p>另外，当你进行徒手攻击时，你可以使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.bolUalIQ1Ad2I6Mg]{夺命之手}进行攻击，而不必花费夺命之手所须的气，你仍然在每回合只能使用夺命之手一次。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"命流宗等级 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"5uD9A8KhKLjUNYMP","name":"灵魂之刃：寻的攻击Soul Blades：Homing Strikes","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_bastion_warlock1.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.yeqpLzvtDcAw6UBm]{念刃}现在成为了你那充盈灵能之灵魂的具现，这使你能够通过以下的方式更好地控制它：</p>\n<p>如果在使用念刃进行的攻击中失手，你能掷灵能骰，将掷骰结果加到这次攻击检定中。如果这会使攻击变为命中，你将消耗一个灵能骰。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"d(floor((1+@classes.rogue.levels)/6)*2+6)","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魂刃等级 9","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"5xnWV6pqjvB7lgls","name":"阳光爆 Searing Sunburst","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/PALADIN_HOLY.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从11级起，武僧可以创造出一个纯粹的光能量球以引起一场毁灭性的爆炸。</p>\n<p>以一个动作，你可以魔法般地创造一个球体并且向150尺内的任意一点投掷，在那里瞬间扩张成一个光芒四射的区域。以目标点为中心半径20尺内的所有生物必须立即通过一次体质豁免，若未通过将受到[[/r 2d6]]的光耀伤害。若生物处于全掩护环境并且掩体不透光，那么他不需要进行豁免。</p>\n<p>你可以花费额外的气以提高这个能量球的威力。每花费1点可以使伤害上升[[/r 2d6]]，上限3点。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":20,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":150,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d6","radiant"]],"versatile":"2d6"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"wis"},"requirements":"日魂宗等级 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"68Z67XSaFvk8OcP6","name":"符文骑士 Rune Knight（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_deathknight_hungeringruneblade.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>符文骑士使用超自然符文和沿袭于远古巨人传统的力量来增强他们的威能。在任何一个巨人家族中，符文切割者随处可见，并且你很可能直接或间接地从这样一个神秘的工匠那里学到了你的方法。无论你是在山丘或洞穴中发现了巨人的雕刻艺术；跟从贤者研习符文；或是亲自和巨人会面，你研究巨人的工艺并学会了如何使用魔法符文来增强你的装备。</p>\n<h3><strong>额外熟练项 Bonus Pro iciencies</strong></h3>\n<p>你获得对于铁匠工具的熟练项，并且你学会了说、读和写巨人语。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"vFtAFGGYMxbYvG2t","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.toolProf.value","mode":2,"value":"smith"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_deathknight_hungeringruneblade.jpg","label":"获得铁匠工具熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.68Z67XSaFvk8OcP6","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null},{"_id":"sAI45HWZPa4LV1o4","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.languages.value","mode":2,"value":"giant"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_deathknight_hungeringruneblade.jpg","label":"习得巨人语","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.68Z67XSaFvk8OcP6","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6XNKdSZKaddzjZ1F","name":"改良守卫 Improved Defender","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_siege_engineer_automatic_repair_beam.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在第15级，你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.mu9IA3SphVBRiv63]{钢铁守卫}和@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.Cst5SSYPhKUEAtf1]{奥能摇荡}变得更强：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>奥能摇荡的额外伤害和生命恢复变为[[/r 4d6]]。</li>\n<li>你的钢铁守卫AC+2</li>\n<li>当你的钢铁守卫使用偏转攻击时，攻击者受到[[/r 1d4]]+你的智力调整值的力场伤害。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d4+@abilities.int.mod","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战地匠师等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6jGuuF5BdCqhifqA","name":"律令之壁 Bastion of Law","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_broker_groundstate.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>6级起，你可以利用事物的壮丽联系为一个生物激发闪烁的秩序之盾。以一个动作，你可以使用1至5术法点创造出一个环绕你或30尺内一个你可见的生物的魔法屏障。此屏障持续存在直到你完成一次长休或直至你再次使用此能力。</p>\n<p>屏障具有等同于你所消耗术法点数量的[[/r d8]]骰。当被守护的生物受到伤害时，其可以消耗任意数量的这些[[/r d8]]骰，并使该伤害减少掷出结果的数值。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"1 至 5 术法点。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"d8","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"时械之魂等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6jV77ZyNW6LlfVY8","name":"魔射手 Arcane Archer","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Monk_SpearHand.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         一个魔射手会学习能将魔法注入到攻击中并产生超自然效果的独特精灵箭技。魔射手是精灵中最精锐的战士。他们会驻足守望精灵国土的边界，着重留意那些入侵者并在那些怪物和入侵者来到精灵的居住地之前用注魔箭矢击败他们。在这数个世纪之间，这种精灵箭技已经被其他能够在魔法和箭艺中找到平衡的种族习得。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6phT9JzgLIAgIu4Y","name":"剑舞 Blade Flourish","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ABILITY_PALADIN_DIVINESTORM.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>3级时，你学会通过表现令人惊讶的战斗技巧和速度来进行展示。</p>\n<p>当你在自己回合执行攻击动作时，你的步行速度提升10尺直到该回合结束。当作为该动作的一部分，由你发动的武器攻击命中生物时，你能选择使用以下剑舞选项之一，每回合你只能使用一项剑舞。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>防御剑舞。</strong>你可以消耗一次@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.FSr7TfaoWRPpUtkD]{诗人激励}的次数，并使该武器对你命中的目标造成额外的伤害。伤害等于你的激励骰投掷结果。直到你的下回合开始，你也将该数值加在你的AC上。</li>\n<li><strong>乱击剑舞。</strong>你可以消耗一次@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.FSr7TfaoWRPpUtkD]{诗人激励}的次数，并使该武器对你命中的目标和你5尺范围内能被你看见且受你选择的其他生物造成额外伤害，伤害等于你的激励骰投掷结果。</li>\n<li><strong>灵活剑舞。</strong>你可以消耗一次@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.FSr7TfaoWRPpUtkD]{诗人激励}的次数，并使该武器对你命中的目标造成额外的伤害。你还能将目标向远离你的方向推动至多5尺，再加上激励骰结果的尺数。然后你能立即使用你的反应移动至多你的步行速度到距离目标5尺内的一个未被占据的空间。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"剑舞学院等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6qqLbKy8xduVuv7b","name":"归复平衡 Restore Balance","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_paladin_savedbythelight.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>1级起，你与绝对秩序之位面的联系使你能重整混沌的时刻。当你60尺内一个你可见的生物即将进行一次具有优势或劣势的检定时，你可以用反应使其免受优势或劣势的影响。</p>\n<p>你可以使用此能力的次数等同于你的熟练加值。每当你完成一次长休，你重新获得已消耗的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"目标将进行有优势或劣势的检定时。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"时械之魂等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6rwXriorWeuTTrvn","name":"集群守卫 Swarmkeeper（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/sha_spell_shadow_shadesofdarkness_nightborne1.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>有的游侠感受到了与周身自然之间的紧密联系，他们通过自己与世界之间的魔法联系向自然的本源伸出双手，并通过一片自然精魂的集群与自然本身羁连。集群随后化作战斗中的强力帮手，或游侠的一位得力助手。有的游侠是被放逐者或是隐士他们更在意修行自我而非与他人打交道并找不快。而其他的集群守卫则乐意创造服务于所有被他们视为自然集群的一部分者集体利益的美丽社会。</p>\n<h3><strong>集群守卫魔法 Swarmkeeper Magic</strong></h3>\n<p>如果你之前并未掌握，你学会@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.H5gghxp0hfT3BAlC]{法师之手}戏法，当你施展它的时候，其形式是聚集在一起的自然精魂。 同样，你会在到达指定游侠等级时，学会一个额外的1环或更高环阶的法术，如集群守卫法术列表所示。这些法术对你视为游侠法术，但它不计入你的已知法术总数中。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>职业等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.sLkNbDcU39qcVt14]{妖火}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.oopuSIBsaXzQKw1Q]{蛛网术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.gjE6zBmfdUOwXiae]{气化形体}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.uF6bn9CQaLwvmxwv]{秘法眼}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.eGYMgP3fmIUQEXMm]{疫病虫群}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游侠等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6s7P6OwuQlVpfnDQ","name":"灵力跃动 Psi-Powered Leap","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/movement/feet-winged-boots-glowing-yellow.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以使用一个附赠动作用你的意志来驱使你的身体。你获得等同于两倍步行速度的飞行速度直到该回合结束。每当你使用这个附赠动作，你无法再次使用该异能直到你完成一次短休或长休，除非你消耗一个灵能骰来再次使用该异能。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"灵能武士等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6tL2DF7EFrYNcZki","name":"魔法克星 Magic-user's Nemesis","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Druid_Cower.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         11级时，你获得打断其他人的魔法的能力。60尺内，当你看到一名角色使用法术或者传送，你可以用你的反应魔法性地来尝试打断它。角色必须成功通过一个难度等同于你的施法DC的感知豁免，否则它的法术和传送失败并浪费。</p>\n<p>         你使用该特性后，不能再次使用它直到你完成一次短休或者长休。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"怪物杀手等级 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6tZeJ4sDyNLBoRXY","name":"偏斜罩幕 Deflecting Shroud","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Arcane_MassDispel.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从14级起，你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.WsBRhWXSAk452GUy]{奥术偏斜}被灌注了致命的魔法。当你使用你的奥术偏斜特性时，你可以让魔法能量从你身上涌出。至多三个60尺内你能看见的目标受到半数于你法师等级的力场伤害。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":3,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(floor(@classes.wizard.levels /2))","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战争法师等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6vwfgAaM0sZsXi5H","name":"替换诗人法术  Bardic Versitility","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/002609.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你的吟游诗人职业等级抵达能让你获得属性值提示职业特性时，你能进行以下一项改变。这种变化代表着你改变了使用法术和技能的重点。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>替换一个你已经选择专精的技能，你可以选择专精于另一个你已经有熟练但还没有专精的技能。之后，你原先专精于的技能变回熟练而非专精。</li>\n<li>从诗人戏法列表中选择一个你未习得的戏法，替换一个你已经习得的戏法。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"吟游诗人等级 4","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"70pWX5593uWhDFSO","name":"野蛮冲撞 Ferocious Charger","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ABILITY_HUNTER_INVIGERATION.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>          无论你是否乘骑，你都可以撞倒你的敌人。若你在攻击一个生物之前直线移动至少10尺，且该攻击命中，则目标必须成功通过一次力量豁免（DC为8 + 你的熟练加值 + 你的力量调整值），否则被击倒地。你在每个你的回合只能使用这个能力一次。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"str","dc":null,"scaling":"str"},"requirements":"骑兵等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"71aSuFiaQn7QPgiQ","name":"擒拿击 Grappling Strike","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/yellow_08.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>当你在一次近战武器攻击命中一个生物时，你能够立即消耗一枚卓越骰，以一个附赠动作对目标进行一次擒抱。将消耗的卓越骰加入你的力量（运动）检定中。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战斗大师等级 3，卓越技巧，战技专家","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"7BefhtXtZoz4BHvd","name":"位面战士 Planar Warrior","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/000151.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>3级起，你学会通过吸取多元宇宙的能量来强化你的攻击。以一个附赠动作，选择一名在你30尺范围内对你可见的角色，这回合你对其的下一次武器攻击造成的伤害变成力场伤害，且目标额外受到来自于该攻击的[[/r 1d8]]力场伤害，当你的游侠等级到达11级时，额外伤害变成[[/r 2d8]].</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(ceil(@classes.ranger.levels/10))d8","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"边界行者等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"7ShzwIqbtJW9M2cg","name":"锋锐剑影 Sharpen the Blade","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Gouge.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>第11级起，你能使用“气”进一步地增强你的武器。你可以用一次附赠动作，消耗最多3点“气”灌注进你接触的一件剑圣武器，在你使用它攻击时获得攻击检定和伤害投骰的加值。加值等于你为此消耗的“气”点数。这一加值效果持续1分钟，除非你再次使用该特性。该特性无法作用于一件已经提供攻击检定与伤害骰加值的魔法武器。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":"最多 3 点气。"},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"剑圣宗等级 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"7pO8fIZR2rXCHdjF","name":"奇械师专业 Artificer Specialist","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Arcane_Rune.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在第3级，你造成自己将成为哪方面的专家。这几个专业会在职业描述的最后进行说明。你的选择将决定你在5级、9级和15级获得的特性。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.subclass.TsvhgdDRQPNMmC01]{炼金师}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.subclass.TsvhgdDRQPNMmC02]{魔炮师}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.subclass.TsvhgdDRQPNMmC03]{战地匠师}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.subclass.TsvhgdDRQPNMmC04]{装甲师（TCE）}</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奇械师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8Cjmf3NW28tKmeXq","name":"战争法师 War Magic（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_Purify.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>奥术学院专门培养用于战争的法师。战争传承精妙地融合了塑能与防护的机理，而非专精于独一学派。它既授予施法者增进法术威力的技巧，同时也为法师提供了改良防御能力的手法。这个奥术传承的追随者被称为战争法师。他们将他们的魔法视为武器和盔甲，比任何一块钢铁都更为坚韧的材料。战争法师在战斗中行动迅速，用他们的法术夺取对战局的战术控制。他们的法术迅猛非常，而他们的防守技巧挫败了对手的反击势头。战争法师也善于导引其他施法者的魔法能量反过来攻击他们。</p>\n<p>于恢弘的大战中，战争法师时常与塑能师、防护师和其他类型的法师相共事。塑能师最常嘲笑战法师分心于攻守之间，一位战法师的典型回应是：“死人可丢不了火球。”</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"法师等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8ELKR6Qzmagy4RYK","name":"魔能祈唤：符令责斥Eldritch Invocation：Rebuke of the Talisman","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/green_15.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当该护符的佩戴者被一个30尺以内对你可见的攻击者攻击，你可以使用你的反应动作对于攻击者造成等于你熟练加值的心灵伤害，并将它推至护符佩戴者10尺以外。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["@prof","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"邪术师等级 2，符之魔契","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8G7nq89gk6vghWp6","name":"镇定之眼 Steady Eye","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpcloud3steamusercontentcomugc842585513743722038541E22C5E7675E37020A757B418B492F00C46FFD.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         9级时，你可以在进行任何感知（观察）检定或智力（调查）检定中得到优势，只要你在同一回合中移动不超过一半的速度。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"审判官等级 9","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8JJgEqQGD4xj4to4","name":"加速愈合Quickened Healing","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_monk_vivify.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>以一个动作，你能消耗2点气并且投掷一粒武艺骰，你恢复等同于掷骰结果加上你的熟练加值的生命值。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"2点气。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d((floor((@classes.monk.levels+1)/6))*2+4) + @mod","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"武僧等级 4","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8QWuVUvYP7CQ6ERH","name":"引导神力：驱散异域 Channel Divinity： Abjure The Extraplanar.","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Priest_BurningWill.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以使用你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.3eyfqXMTJMG9AxYH]{引导神力}惩罚来自异界的存在。以一个动作，你展示你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.TJi1q6Bm8IGoJJVL]{圣徽}，你30尺范围内能够听到你祷言的异怪、天界生物、元素、精类或邪魔都必须进行一次感知豁免，豁免失败者将受到驱散，其效应持续1分钟或直至其受到任何伤害。以此方式被驱散的生物必须花费其回合内的所有移动速度尽量远离你，且无法主动靠近你30尺内。被驱散的生物无法执行反应，只能使用既有的疾走动作或从任何妨碍其移动的效应中挣脱。该生物无路可走时将执行回避动作。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"守望之誓等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8Ron0AAuUy21J0D1","name":"守护者 Guardian","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/images/b_75.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>　　对你奥能装甲能量系统的改进使你能够释放强大的拉力。当你可见的一个体型为巨型或更小的生物在距离你 30 尺内的地方结束其回合时，你能以一个反应迫使该生物对你的法术豁免 DC 进行一个力量豁免检定，失败将被拉向你最多 30 尺。如果你将目标拉到距离你 5 尺的地方，作为此反应的一部分，你能对该生物进行一次近战武器攻击。</p>\n<p>　　你每天能够执行此反应的次数等于你的熟练加值。在完成一次长休后将恢复所有可用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":5,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"str","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"装甲师等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8TU66NBWGPJ6wRNt","name":"直觉猛扑 Instinctive Pounce","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_druid_bristlingfur.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>作为你进入狂暴状态的附赠动作的一部分，你可以移动一段距离。这段距离长度是你速度的一半。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"野蛮人等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8fO6wjfLt8LT8lg7","name":"热能袭 Searing Arc Strike","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Paladin_icon_speedoflight.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从6级起，武僧可以转换自己的气变为灼热的能量。</p>\n<p>如果你在你的回合内进行了攻击动作，你可以立即消耗2点气来用附赠动作施放一环@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.CB9z74KJLWMplGuz]{燃烧之手}。</p>\n<p>你可以花费额外的气来施展更高环的燃烧之手法术，每一点额外的气都使法术等级上升1环。你最多可以在这个法术上花费的气（2+额外的点数）等同你一半的武僧等级（向下取整）。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"回合进行了攻击动作；至少 2 点气。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":15,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"cone"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["3d6","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"日魂宗等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8h2z8Kfz7wXyIvwM","name":"战意 Fighting Spirit","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/002503.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从3级开始，你在战斗中的气势能保护你并帮助你精准攻击。在你的回合以一个附赠动作，你可以让你自己在该回合结束前的武器攻击检定都具有优势。当你这么做时，你同时获得5点临时生命值。这个临时生命值的数量将会在你本职业升至特定等级时增加，10级时增加至10点，15级时增加至15。</p>\n<p>         你可以使用这个能力三次，且你在完成一次长休后恢复所有你花费掉的次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":3,"max":"3","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["max(min(floor(@classes.fighter.levels/5),3),1)*5","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"武士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
