{"_id":"91cuCtFwcWhR8O2Z","name":"战斗风格（剑舞） Fighting Style","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_DualWieldSpecialization.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>3级时，你可以选择一种战斗风格，以求专精。选择下述战斗风格之一。你不能多次选择同一种战斗风格，即使你今后仍可有选择战斗风格的机会。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.VoKRG6XqUxTz4rT3]{战斗风格：对决}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.9U4ePVABZME8Syk9]{战斗风格：双武器战斗}</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"剑舞学院等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"94prCWbgDDsOtodq","name":"巨灵器皿 Genie's Vessel","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_monk_ironskinbrew1.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你的宗主赐予你一个包含巨灵之力的魔法器皿。该器皿是一个微型物件，你可以将其作为施展你邪术师法术的法器。你决定物件的类别，或者你可以通过巨灵器皿表来决定。</p>\n<p>当你触碰器皿时，你可以用以下方式使用它:瓶中小憩、巨灵之怒</p>\n<p>器皿的AC等同于你的法术豁免DC。它的生命值等于你的邪术师等级加熟练加值，并免疫于毒素和心灵伤害。</p>\n<p>倘若器皿被摧毁或是丢失，你可以进行一场持续1小时的仪式来从你的宗主处获得一个替代品。这一仪式可于短休或长休时进行，并会摧毁之前仍存在的器皿。当你死亡时，器皿在一阵元素能量的闪耀中消失。</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>[[/r D6]]</td>\n<td>器皿种类</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>油灯</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>瓮</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>可装东西的戒指</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>被塞住的瓶子</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>空心小雕像</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>华丽提灯</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"巨灵宗主等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9DryG6ut4sWR92bm","name":"战地匠师 Battle Smith","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_rogue_reinforcedleather.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         军队需要保护，但当防卫战失败时，需要有人来进行重整。身为守护者和医生的结合，战地匠师是进行防卫，以及重整工事与人员的专家。战地匠师大多都携带一个由自己制造的防卫性随从——钢铁守卫来辅助自己。无数士兵都曾讲述过关于濒临死亡的自己被一名战地匠师，以及他的钢铁守卫所拯救的故事。</p>\n<p>         战地匠师在卡尼斯家族制造战斗构装体和最初的战俑时扮演了关键的角色。在终末战争过后，这些奇械师致力于救助在恐怖的战争中受伤的人。</p>\n<h3><strong>本职工具</strong></h3>\n<p>         当你在第3级选择此专业时，你获得@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.B97AB85722BCF651]{铁匠工具}的熟练。如果你已经拥有此熟练，作为代替，你能获得另一种工匠工具的熟练。</p>\n<h3><strong>战地匠师法术</strong></h3>\n<p>         从第3级起，只要你达到相应的职业等级，战地匠师法术表格中的法术总是被视为已准备。这些法术对你来说是奇械师法术，且不会计入你可以准备法术的总数。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>职业等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.eatsvLyUqyzEFzCv]{英雄气概}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.6EjLIIN4ug7eSp4P]{护盾术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.JTEqFylsjhdBhz3c]{印记斩}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.DLyjjM6qTHBCSFCx]{守护之链}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.XfYgB18GC8OgETjG]{活力灵光}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Ijq7k3y3AZoC76VF]{召唤箭雨}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.ujZGFLEqgI0L6oli]{净化灵光}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.AdWubx1kFJLe8QDa]{火焰护盾}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.2CIeVJ6dzmDcGfic]{放逐斩}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.UBLAtJuRhRB3GokC]{群体疗伤术}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奇械师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"u8W81hwz6RfD3KD5","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.toolProf.value","mode":2,"value":"smith"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_rogue_reinforcedleather.png","label":"获得铁匠工具熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.9DryG6ut4sWR92bm","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9IoLBGEaRRm3vd6G","name":"暗影箭 Shadow Arrow","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_TheBlackArrow.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你施加幻术魔法到你的箭上，使其能用暗影蒙蔽敌人的视野。被这发箭击中的角色会额外受到[[/r 2d6]]的心灵伤害，而且目标必须成功通过一个感知豁免，或者无法看见5尺之外的任何事物直到你的下一个回合开始。</p>\n<p>         当你的战士等级到18级时该心灵伤害增加到[[/r 4d6]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(ceil(@classes.fighter.levels/17)*2)d6","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"int"},"requirements":"魔射手等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9Plsb93N8fdRkpoo","name":"守卫缠绕 Guardian Coil","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_mage_waterjet.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.AO1g9WjlmCTq9KE8]{深海触手}可以保护你和其他人，用自己将你们和危险隔开。当你或你可以看见的一个位于触手10尺内的生物承受伤害时，你可以使用反应选择这些生物中的一个并使该生物遭受的伤害减少[[/r 1d8]]。当你达到邪术师10级时，触手可以抵消的伤害增加到[[/r 2d8]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"(min((ceil(@classes.warlock.levels/9)),2))d8","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"深海意志等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9XTkHHU2VpBZRkDl","name":"不竭鼓舞 Unfailing Inspiration","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Warrior_RallyingCry.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         6级起，你鼓舞人心的言词有着很强的说服力，它们能够驱使别人走向成功。当一个生物将一个你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.FSr7TfaoWRPpUtkD]{诗人激励}骰加到其属性检定、攻击检定或豁免检定而掷骰失败时，该生物可以保留那个诗人激励骰。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MOT","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d(min(floor(@classes.bard.levels/5)*2+6,12))","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"雄辩学院等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9buzNONalBOaemQE","name":"荣耀之誓 Oath of Glory（MOT）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_Crusade.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         以荣耀为誓的圣武士相信他（们）会因其行为成为命定的英雄。他们勤奋训练，互相勉励，故命定之时，万事备矣。</p>\n<h3><strong>荣耀之信条</strong></h3>\n<p>         荣耀之誓信条驱策圣武士向着有朝一日终将闪耀的传奇之道前进。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>行在意前:</strong>尽量以行动而非语言来成名。</li>\n<li><strong>战仅为炼:</strong>面对困难的鞭挞，也鼓励你的伙伴和你共同面对。</li>\n<li><strong>磨练其身:</strong>犹若刻石，体需淬炼方能觉醒潜能。</li>\n<li><strong>坚毅其魂:</strong>你必须严格锻炼来克服你自己那些可能会有损荣耀的缺点。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>圣誓法术Oath Spells</strong></p>\n<p><em>你获得以下圣誓法术。</em></p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>圣骑士等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>3rd</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.PHYXwNkXSdJjDCSD]{曳光弹}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.eatsvLyUqyzEFzCv]{英雄气概}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>5th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.SCmGEYM6V880rfaW]{强化属性}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.14a3v5NF5h5Lgm9J]{魔化武器}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>9th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.YLYeCtTmbjIZsPvN]{加速术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.DBrh7ALD21UoUApP]{防护能量伤害}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>13th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.RpBbOYseLZCFXaFY]{强迫术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.OZMc9g7XaWuRc36J]{行动自如}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>17th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.7tphgwQJI7dKIyfE]{通神术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Q8XNvy4kwTSQVizo]{焰击术}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MOT","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"圣武士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9e501Yzw4iBL4Csm","name":"守望之誓 Oath of Watcher（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_Crusade.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>守望之誓使圣武士们承担着保护凡人国度免受异界生物掠夺与捕食的责任，而这之中有许多是凡俗的兵卒所难以匹敌的。因此，守望者们磨炼自己的心智、灵魂和肉体，以成为对抗此类威胁的终极武器。</p>\n<p>遵循着守望之誓的圣武士们总是警戒着异界力量的影响，他们时常会通过建立间谍和线人的情报网络来收集可疑邪教的信息。对于一个守望者来说，对周围环境保持一种积极态度的怀疑和警戒就像在战斗中穿着盔甲一样自然。</p>\n<h3>守望之信条</h3>\n<p>接受守望之誓的圣武士发誓要保护凡人国度不受来自其他位面的威胁。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>警惕：</strong>你所面临的威胁狡猾、强大而又超乎常理。时刻警惕他们的腐化。</li>\n<li><strong>忠诚：</strong>永远不要接受来自邪魔或其同伙的礼物或恩惠。忠于你的使命，忠于你的同志，忠于你的职责。</li>\n<li><strong>纪律：</strong>你是抵御星辰之外无尽恐怖的盾牌。你的剑刃必须永远锋利，你的头脑必须永远清晰。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>圣誓法术Oath Spells</strong></p>\n<p><em>你获得以下圣誓法术。</em></p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>圣骑士等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>3rd</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.xS2Astj9zhhqw7el]{警报术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.cGO3m3Xu4mtPegr4]{侦测魔法}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>5th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Vf5ZLLqRsGSy5ckY]{月华之光}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.AYqzOw6GE7NT3FhJ]{识破隐形}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>9th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.895yeeloz2EhpEYC]{法术反制}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.VT60UFGIZOZhPgMi]{回避侦测}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>13th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.ujZGFLEqgI0L6oli]{净化灵光}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.lopw7wVkPoE7gbNu]{放逐术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>17th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.abm5MgV3kejSatZt]{怪物定身术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.OA4mCsVxg6nUrLjV]{探知}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":nu