{"_id":"Cnl1XvqavxBl4WUo","name":"额外牧师法术 Additional Cleric Spells","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_HopeAndGrace.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>下方列出的法术是对玩家手册中牧师法术列表的补充。若一个法术能够以仪式施法的方式施展，那么仪式标签会记在法术名字后方。除了标有星号(说明这是一个来自第三章的法术)的法术以外，其他法术均来自玩家手册。萨娜珊的万事指南中也提供了更多的法术。</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>环阶</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>三环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.XfYgB18GC8OgETjG]{活力灵光}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.TH2wXQ3yssrGZ821]{魂灵环绕*}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>四环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.9WDd3gopYOGyYnrT]{生命灵光}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.ujZGFLEqgI0L6oli]{净化灵光}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>五环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.aJR797NIkIG7k9uN]{召唤天界生物*}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>六环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.oU9SfwCYsV2eiZiQ]{阳炎射线}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>八环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.P8biBjQGeqe3c7M8]{阳炎爆}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>九环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.FfrtzwJUyOdNzB5q]{律令医疗}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"牧师等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Cnnnn1bEyEy3myma","name":"符文之盾 Runic Shield","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_racial_holyresistance.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从7级起，你学会了激活你的符文魔法来保护你的盟友。当另一个60尺内且对你可见的生物被一次攻击检定命中，你可以使用一个反应动作来强迫攻击者重新投掷[[/r d20]]并采用新的攻击检定结果。</p>\n<p>该特性的可使用次数等于你的熟练加值，且你可以在完成一次长休之后恢复所有已使用的次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":3,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"d20","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"符文骑士等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"CpHkK2DKqVud7MoZ","name":"咒剑士 Hexblade（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/INV_Sword_143.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你和一个来自堕影冥界的神秘实体订立了契约，那些由阴影物质雕琢的智能魔法武器隐约显露了其力量。强悍的魔法剑黑刃blackrazor是这些武器中最令人瞩目的，它在无数年间辗转于多元宇宙之中。这些武器背后的暗影之力，能为与其立契的邪术士提供力量。许多咒剑邪术士模仿那些在堕影冥界中锻造的武器塑造自己的兵刃，而其他人则选择放弃这些武器，转向链接堕影冥界的暗影魔法网络来施展法术。</p>\n<p>鉴于人尽皆知是鸦后锻造出了最初的此类武器，许多贤者推测她就是暗影武器的幕后黑手，而这些武器——以及咒剑邪术士们——都是她用来玩弄物质位面的是非，以实现她难以揣测的目的的工具。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">扩展法术列表</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.ccsNUAD2zK3esckm]{激愤斩}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.6EjLIIN4ug7eSp4P]{护盾术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.2XwLnziQi0Iv7GQT]{朦胧术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.JTEqFylsjhdBhz3c]{印记斩}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.bj6fUAFiJScoI6wb]{闪现术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.srjt2KPpCAtQGe7W]{元素武器}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.BLNE7S7l2uTkx7w6]{魅影杀手}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.0GPWp8Rwlm5AizJD]{惊惧斩}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.2CIeVJ6dzmDcGfic]{放逐斩}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.z9HXB89B3uO5NHW8]{寒冰锥}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"邪术师等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Cst5SSYPhKUEAtf1","name":"奥能摇荡 Arcane Jolt","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_siege_engineer_magnetic_crush.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在第9级，你学会了新的方法来引导奥术能量进行伤害或治疗。当你使用魔法武器或指挥@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.mu9IA3SphVBRiv63]{钢铁守卫}命中目标时，你可以将奥术能量引导至攻击中，以获得以下一种效应：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>目标受到额外的[[/r 2d6]]力场伤害。</li>\n<li>选择距离目标30尺以内的一个可见生物或物体。治愈能量涌进选择的对象，为其恢复[[/r 2d6]]生命值。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>         你可以引导奥术能量的次数等同于你的智力调整值（至少1次），但每回合只能这么做一次。在你完成长休时，恢复所有可用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"2d6","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战地匠师等级 9","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"D9m3lfskS3rte0XT","name":"狂热者 Path of the Zealot（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_AshesToAshes.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>一些神灵激励他们的追随者们投身于残酷的战斗狂怒中。这些野蛮人是狂热的战士，他们引导自己的愤怒转化为强大的神赐力量。</p>\n<p>在DND世界中有许多神祇都会鼓励自己的追随者寻求狂热者道途。最著名的是费伦的Tempus，以及灰鹰的海克斯托（Hextor）和Erythnul。一般来说，那些培养狂热者的神祇往往是偏向于战斗、破坏和暴力等神职。当然，不是所有（这样的）神都是邪恶，但只有少数是例外。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"野蛮人等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"DHRB0zFNBcOkuto3","name":"诱饵战术 Bait and Switch","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/blue_03.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你距离一个盟友5尺以内时，你能够消耗一枚卓越骰，如果你同时消耗5尺的移动力，你能与该盟友互换位置，这一移动不会引发借机攻击。</p>\n<p>掷消耗的卓越骰。直到你的下个回合开始前，你或另一个生物（由你选择）的AC获得等于掷骰结果的加值。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战斗大师等级 3，卓越技巧，战技专家","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"DJRq6UQrQzGZRSXG","name":"神之勇者 Warrior of the Gods","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_HolyGuidance.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在3级时，你的灵魂被无尽的战斗所烙印。若一个法术（例如@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.63gAxMpLpbVW9Oja]{死者复活}）——有且仅有让你起死回生（但不能是变成不死生物）的效果，该施法者在对你施展法术时不需要材料成分。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"狂热者等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"DcQOhZPhVZbslq9W","name":"精宸所与 Fey Reinforcements","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_ardenweald_shaman.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>妖精荒原的皇庭赐予你获得精类援助的祝福：你习得@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.p12lhL5QyiAvgpTx]{精类召唤术}。这不占用你的已知游侠法术，且你可以施展它而无需材料成分。你可以不消耗法术位而施展这个法术一次，并在你完成一次长休后重获该能力。</p>\n<p>当你开始施展这个法术时，你可以对其进行调整使其无需专注。若你这么做，那么法术的持续时间会在那一次施展时变为一分钟。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"妖精漫游者等级 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"DeqMj9ld6ZN2TKgB","name":"剑歌 Bladesong (TCE)","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/INV_Knife_1h_PanDung_C_01.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>2级起，你可唤起一种特殊的精灵魔法——剑歌之术——只要你并未穿着中甲、重甲或使用盾牌。它赐予你超自然的速度、敏捷与专注。</p>\n<p>你可以用一个附赠动作启动剑歌，并使之维持1分钟。当你陷入失能，或完成中甲、重甲或盾牌的着装，又或者用双手发动一次攻击时，你的剑歌将提前终止。你也可以随时随意的解除剑歌（不需要动作）。</p>\n<p>在剑歌激活期间，你获得以下好处：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你的AC获得等于你智力调整值的加值（最少+1）。</li>\n<li>你的陆地移动速度增加10尺。</li>\n<li>你在敏捷（杂技）检定上获得优势。</li>\n<li>你在为维持法术专注所进行的体质豁免检定上获得加值，加值等于你的智力调整值（最少+1）。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>你能使用本特性的次数等于你的熟练加值。完成一次长休后，你将重获所有消耗掉的使用次数。（TCE）</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"剑咏者等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"DjgLxtHabE23Vldt","name":"人工生命仆从","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2>人工生命仆从</h2>\n<p><em>先决条件：</span></em><em>6</span></em><em>级奇械师</span></em><em><br /></span></em><em>物品：一颗价值至少</span></em><em>100gp</span></em><em>的宝石或龙晶</span></em><br /></span>　　你习得了如何魔法性的创造一个为你服务的特殊@Actor[j6VaBrD3jatNli2k]{人工生命仆从&nbsp;Homunculus Servant}。你在注法中使用的物品将变成人工生命的心脏，而它的身体会立即围绕心脏成型。</span><br /></span>　　你能够决定人工生命的外观。有些奇械师喜欢看上去像机械的鸟，也有些喜欢长翅膀的小瓶或是拥有生命的小坩埚。</span><br /></span>　　人工生命对你和你的同伴都十分友善，且服从你的命令。炼金人工生命的游戏数据见下。</span><br /></span>　　在战斗中，人工生命使用你的先攻，并且在你的回合后立即行动。它能自由移动和执行反应，但除非你以一个附赠动作命令它进行数据中列出的动作或疾行、撤离、协力、躲藏、搜索动作，否则它在回合中只能进行闪避动作。</span><br /></span>　　如果你对人工生命施放修复术，它将恢复</span>2d6</span>生命值。如果它死亡，它会消失，只有心脏会留在它之前占据的地方。</span><br /><br /></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_siege_engineer_overload.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"DzcVAdj0FNlaVlua","name":"众神眷恩 Favored By The Gods","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_HolyNova.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从1级起，神圣力量指引着你的命运。若你未通过一次豁免检定或在一次攻击检定中失手，你可以投[[/r 2d4]]，并将它加到总值上，这可能会改变结果。</p>\n<p>         一旦你使用了此特性，你无法在完成一次短休或长休前再次使用它。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":"未通过豁免检定或攻击检定。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d4","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"神圣之魂等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"DzcewKuAHAUP8yEn","name":"引导神力：铁匠祝福 Channel Divinity: Artisan's Blessing","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_EnchantArmor.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从2级开始，你可以以此创造简易物品。</p>\n<p>花费一小时来引导仪式，你可以创造包含有金属的非魔法物品：一件护甲，一把简易或军用武器，十份弹药，工具或是其他物品。在仪式的结束，物品被创造并且出现在你选择的，一个五尺内未被占据的空间内。</p>\n<p>你创造的物品的价值必须低于100gp。作为仪式的一部分，你必须提供等同于物品价值的金属物品，比如钱币。在仪式的结束，这些物品会不可逆地变成你创造的物品，魔法会形成非金属的部分。</p>\n<p>仪式可以创造包括金属的非魔法物品的复制品，例如钥匙，但你在仪式过程中必须拥有原件。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"hour","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"锻造领域等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"E06roEzIAhw8cXnY","name":"闪电发射器 Lightning Launcher","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/images/sffi_02.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你在胸部或复盖装甲的拳头（根据你的选择）上安装了一个宝石状的节点。它被视为一件简单远程武器，它拥有 90 尺的常规射程和 300 尺的最大射程，在命中后会造成[[/r 1d6]]闪电伤害。每个你的回合一次，你在通过闪电发射器命中一个生物时，能够额外造成[[/r 1d6 ]]闪电伤害。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":90,"long":300,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"rwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","lightning"]],"versatile":"1d6"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"装甲师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"E0L7yAUqsq3jghRa","name":"不懈 Tireless Spirit","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/000151.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从10级开始，当你投先攻且没有剩余的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.8h2z8Kfz7wXyIvwM]{战意}使用次数时，你重新获得一次使用机会。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"武士等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"name":"光耀武器","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2>光耀武器</h2>\n<p><em>先决条件：</span></em><em>6</span></em><em>级奇械师</span></em><em><br></span></em><em>物品：一把简易或军用武器（需调谐）</span></em><br></span>　　该魔法武器在攻击和伤害检定中具有</span>+1</span>加值。该武器被拿在手中时，持有者能以一个附赠动作让它放出半径</span>30</span>尺的明亮照明以及该范围外</span>30</span>尺范围的微光照明。持有者也能以一个附赠动作熄灭武器的光芒。</span><br></span>　　当该武器的持有者被近战攻击命中时，持有者能够以一个反应让攻击者对你的法术豁免</span>dc</span>进行一次体质豁免检定，若失败，攻击者将目盲直到他的下个回合结束。该反应动作在使用后必须经过一次短休或长休后才能再次使用。</span><br></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_SheathofLight.png","_id":"E4Se3O8rP1d351lx"}
{"_id":"E7IXEz4SVc0bXppU","name":"时械之魂 Clockwork Soul（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/SPELL_HOLY_BORROWEDTIME.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>一股力量，一股源自宇宙本身的秩序力量，从机械境————或其他类似的位面之中产生，并扩散到你的灵魂之中，使你充满了魔力。你或你宗族中的某个人也许已经卷入到魔冢的阴谋之中，那是一种居住在机械境的秩序生命。又或许，你的先祖甚至参与过魔冢长征。无论是何种起源，秩序的力量也许对旁人来说有些奇怪，但于你而言，它是一个宏伟而璀璨的系统的一部分。</p>\n<h3><strong>时械法术</strong></h3>\n<p>当你升至相应的术士等级时，你习得下表中的额外法术。这些法术对你而言视为术士法术，且不受术士表上已知法术一栏的数量限制。</p>\n<p>每当你提升术士等级时，你可以选择一个环数相同的新法术来替换你因此特性习得的一个法术。该法术必须为术士、邪术师或法师法术列表中的一个防护系或变化系法术。</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.xS2Astj9zhhqw7el]{警报术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.IuzXxwP3EhWGhtXC]{防护善恶}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.hAL0Dxp9w7gvkfZm]{援助术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.I1C2EQxwynPd7dOC]{次级复原术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.as6xgBANCbyoWPXX]{解除魔法}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.DBrh7ALD21UoUApP]{防护能量伤害}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.OZMc9g7XaWuRc36J]{行动自如}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.46SldCNyO92qIwfQ]{构装体召唤术*}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.7dqplcsKNYQgRh2S]{高等复原术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.31jKHMGJ0vlqdvQU]{力场墙}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3><strong>秩序显现</strong></h3>\n<p>此外，你可以从秩序显迹表格中选择或掷骰决定一种你在施法时显现出与秩序之联系的方式。</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>[[/r d6]]</th>\n<th>显迹</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>幽灵般的虚幻齿轮在你身后旋转。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>时钟的指针出现在你的眼中。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>你的皮肤发出如黄铜般的金属光泽。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>你的体表浮动着方程式和几何图形。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>你的法器短暂地变化成小巧的机械装置。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>你和那些受到你法术影响的生物都会听到齿轮的滴答声或是钟表的响铃。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"术士等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ECu6x73eCp8IKGq7","name":"驭气以击Ki-Fueled Attack","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_monk_BoughStrike.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>如果你在你的回合中执行动作时花费了1点或更多的气，则你可以在回合结束前用1附赠动作以徒手打击或武僧武器进行一次攻击。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":"在你的回合中执行动作时花费了1点或更多的气。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"武僧等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ELPUdbp1apIhMzQH","name":"精魂学院 College of Spirits （VRGR）","type":"subclass","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_ardenweald_paladin_spring.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>精魂学院的吟游诗人们寻找那具有内在力量的故事——无论是传说、历史还是虚构的故事——并且赋予其生命。这些吟游诗人使用玄秘的道具，召唤出强大力量的精神化身，再次改变世界。不过，这样的精魂往往变化多端，吟游诗人们所召唤的力量并不总在自己的控制之下。</p>\n<p><strong>精魂故事 Spirit Tales</strong></p>\n<p>讲故事的人，比如精魂学院的吟游诗人，时常受到更伟大的主题或者作品的启发来讲述故事。在你决定自己所讲述的故事时，要考虑是什么把它们联系在一起的。他们是来自某个特定组合中的不同角色吗——比如塔罗卡牌中的原型、星座中的人物、儿时想象中的朋友的或是某本故事书中的角色？还是说，带给你灵感的，是更加脍炙人口的历史名人、神话英雄或坊间传奇？作为一个讲故事的冒险者，好好运用你所讲述的故事来定位你的职业风格。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"VRGR","identifier":"college-of-spirits","classIdentifier":"bard","advancement":[{"_id":"kl6f63ffge5zm6nd","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.csxVkdUoKkeiFOjN","Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.dpOHLoQUpFbxl3Nj","Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.Sew4Tj3ec9CwH53H"],"optional":false},"value":{},"level":3,"title":"职业特性","icon":""},{"_id":"90ur8r9bjwaj9aol","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.AVUZ9OuiFXpfOOla"],"optional":false},"value":{},"level":6,"title":"职业特性","icon":""},{"_id":"v25ogicanjfpnasz","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.NfG2UVzVTsJOkcct"],"optional":false},"value":{},"level":14,"title":"职业特性","icon":""},{"_id":"g29cfo4gqwesqjti","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.QiU2ZZ09lBye0Iy4"],"optional":true},"value":{},"level":3,"title":"获得法术","icon":""}],"spellcasting":{"progression":"none","ability":""},"attunement":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"IQE6hAV3ygaTICtD":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.subclass.dP3iX2uL3SU5Mq07"}}}
{"name":"增强奥术法器","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2>增强奥术法器</h2>\n<p><em>物品：一根权杖、法杖或是魔杖（需调谐）</span></em><br></span>　　当持续此物品时，持有者的法术攻击检定获得</span>+1</span>加值，同时在进行法术法术攻击时无视半身掩护。</span><br></span>　　当你拥有</span>10</span>个奇械师等级时，该加值变成</span>+2</span>。</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_StoneSkinTotem.png","_id":"EjRepZBmGwbmRKp0"}
{"_id":"EzFJHWfeZ4YNEn5L","name":"魔能祈唤：护符庇佑Eldritch Invocation：Protection of the Talisman","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/blood_01.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当佩戴者在一次豁免检定中失败，他们可以在骰掷结果上增加一个[[/r d4]]骰，这可能将结果变为成功。这一能力可使用的次数等于你的熟练加值，且所有已消耗的次数将会在你完成一次长休之后全部恢复。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"2","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d4","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"邪术师等级 7，符之魔契","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FDeshu0CHiVdxvCp","name":"征服之誓 Oath of Conquest（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_SheathofLight.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         征服的誓言吸引着在战斗中寻求荣耀与征服的圣武士。对他们来说，简单地建立秩序是不够的，混乱的势力必须被粉碎。有些征服圣武士会被称为暴君骑士或战争贩子，他们聚集成严酷的军队或组织，来为秩序与战争的神明或哲学服务。</p>\n<p>         有些这样的圣武士走得太远，甚至会与九狱合流，他们的眼中法治凌驾于仁慈。大魔鬼巴尔，Avernus的战争领主，统领着许多这样的骑士——他们被称为地狱骑士——视为他最热诚的追随者。地狱骑士用倒下的敌人身上的战利品来装饰他们的盔甲，警告着任何敢于反抗他们乃至他们领主的法令的人的可怕下场。这些骑士往往会受到其他征服圣武士的抵制——他们认为地狱骑士在黑暗中走得太远了。</p>\n<h3><strong>征服之信条</strong></h3>\n<p>         选择征服之誓的圣武士会将征服信条烙印在他们的上臂上。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>掐灭希望：</strong>仅仅在战斗中击败敌人是不够的。你的胜利必须显著到彻底击碎敌人的战斗意志。刀剑只能结束生命。恐惧却能终结国家。</li>\n<li><strong>铁腕统治：</strong>一旦你完成了征服，不要容忍任何异议。你说出的话就是法律。遵循的人会被偏爱。不服从的人则会受到惩罚，以儆效尤。</li>\n<li><strong>力量至高：</strong>你会一直统治下去，直到更强的势力兴起。到那时，你必须变得更强并面对挑战，否则就迎来自己的毁灭。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>圣誓法术Oath Spells</strong></p>\n<p><em>你获得以下圣誓法术。</em></p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>圣骑士等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>3rd</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.l1SThGbqPfk8SZa7]{艾嘉西斯之铠}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Ja6HpsLeGA9MQ0Rm]{命令术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>5th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.syHHJlRPS4rVwCQA]{人类定身术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.uLEtdTC6yBxuLNFe]{灵体武器}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>9th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.kqh0eV640hXk4flg]{降咒}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.wnJNHkm5kThiJixx]{恐惧术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>13th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.xaSXewdCx3aWtczk]{支配野兽}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.8xmyW0Ynz0z7Kt3X]{石肤术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>17th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.T39k39dbE2poIFc5]{死云术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.JudswpO6E5GBlyfQ]{支配人类}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"圣武士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FGMHkQNKqKDa4M8P","name":"强力召唤 Mighty Summoner","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/000517.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>          6级起，你获得了召唤强力野兽和精类的能力。任何你法术召唤或创造出的野兽或精类获得两种好处：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>该生物出现时具有比正常情况下更多的生命值：它具有的每个生命骰会给它2点额外的生命值。</li>\n<li>在克服对于非魔法攻击和伤害的免疫和抗性时，来自该生物天生武器的伤害被视为是魔法的。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"牧人之环等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FRsOak029n5r5Gi2","name":"化学专家 Chemical Mastery","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Druid_EarthandSky.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在第15级，你已经接触了太多的化学物质，并解开了它们的秘密，它们对你的危害很小，你可以使用它们来迅速治愈某些疾病。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你获得了对强酸伤害和毒素伤害的抗性，同时对中毒状态免疫。</li>\n<li>只要你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.EFBBAE8B63126638]{炼金工具}作为法器，就能够在不消费法术位和材料成分的情况下施展@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.7dqplcsKNYQgRh2S]{高等复原术}或@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.nCLJRsp7CWAACqGE]{医疗术}。一旦你通过此特性施法，必须完成一次长休才能再次使用此特性。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"炼金师等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"Nt4ZjbWjzFXLkRCv","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"poison"},{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"acid"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Druid_EarthandSky.png","label":"获得强酸、毒素抗性","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.FRsOak029n5r5Gi2","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null},{"_id":"ozCKPzxa8jDCYCcB","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.ci.value","mode":2,"value":"poisoned"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Druid_EarthandSky.png","label":"获得中毒免疫","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.FRsOak029n5r5Gi2","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FXRY6408tUuCLPqZ","name":"替换戏法 Cantrip Versatility","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_priest_clarityofpurpose.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你在此职业获得了属性值提升，你可以将一个你通过此职业的施法特性学会的牧师戏法替换为牧师法术列表中的另一个戏法。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"牧师等级 4","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FbhwZkQGMDZCnhIy","name":"孢子结社 Circle of Spores（GGR）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_Druid_Wildmushroom.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         孢子之环的德鲁伊善于发现腐朽之美，他们在霉菌和其他真菌中看到了无生命物质如何转化为丰饶、尽管又有点奇怪的生命。</p>\n<p>         这些德鲁伊认为，生死是一个大循环的周期，从一个循环通往另一个循环，周而复始。死亡不是生命的终结，而是转化为另一种新形式的生命形态。</p>\n<p>          这个学社的德鲁伊与不死生物有着复杂的关系，与大多数德鲁伊不同，他们不认为不死生物是错的。但是这些德鲁伊相信自然循环最为健康，它的每一个部分都生机盎然。那些试图用亡灵来代替所有生命的不死者，或是那些企图避免最终永眠的不死者都违反了这个循环运行，因此必须被阻止。</p>\n<h3><strong>结社法术</strong></h3>\n<p>          你和真菌间形成了共生连接，而你踏入生死循环的能力为你带来了特定的法术。在 2 级时，你学会戏法@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.JyNtTLwpaHOZqdZx]{冻寒之触 Chill Touch}。在 3 级，5 级，7 级，和 9 级你获得下表：孢子结社法术中对应等级列出的法术。</p>\n<p>          结社法术一旦获得，将会一直在你的已准备法术列表中，且不计入你的每日准备法术上限。任何结社法术对你而言都是德鲁伊法术，而不论其是否在德鲁伊法术列表之上。</p>\n<table border=\"1\"><caption>孢子结社法术</caption>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>3rd</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.uzWirpWyQshzp1l0]{遗体防腐}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.5GWYJBfc1aZ6415M]{目盲/耳聋术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>5th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.xYpJGRI4xcMa41kO]{操纵死尸}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.gjE6zBmfdUOwXiae]{气化形体}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>7th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.AVumturalJuP4paw]{枯萎术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.MZ1jwLEJukFjSv1a]{困惑术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>9th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.T39k39dbE2poIFc5]{死云术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.gbHBG4jYU3I06JQO]{疫病术}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GGR","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"德鲁伊等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FghPh1QoXjq2lH5W","name":"杀手反制 Slayer's Counter","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Parry.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         15级时，当你的猎物企图干扰你时你能够反击。如果你的狩猎开始特性目标使你做出一个豁免骰，你能够使用你的反应来对其做出一次武器攻击。你在进行豁免检定前立刻做出该攻击。如果你击中，你的豁免自动成功，否则只造成普通攻击效果。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"怪物杀手等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"name":"连射武器","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2>连射武器</h2>\n<p><em>物品：一把具有弹药特性的简单或军用武器（需调谐）</span></em><br></span>　　此魔法武器在远程攻击的攻击和伤害检定上获得</span>+1</span>加值，并且无视它的装填Loading</span>特性（如果有的话）。</span><br></span>　　此武器不需要弹药；除非你手动为它装填弹药，否则每次你以它远程攻击时，它会魔法地创造一根子弹。此武器创造的弹药在击中或失误之后立即消失。</span><br></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_RunningShot.png","_id":"FiRczet0VH4xz5FV"}
{"_id":"FrwqtWbSJPp4hEHR","name":"边界行者 Horizon Walker（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/000407.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         边界行者会保护世界不受其他位面的威胁或者通过其他位面的魔法来找到并破坏其他有威胁的位面，他们会找出传送门并看守他们，会为了追捕他们的敌人而穿梭于表里位面。这些游侠也是多元宇宙中任何势力的盟友，尤其是那些守护位面的生灵和秩序的善良龙类，精怪和元素。</p>\n<h3><strong>边界行者魔法</strong></h3>\n<p>         3级起，当你到达指定游侠等级时你学会一个额外法术，如边界行者法术列表所示。这些法术对你视为游侠法术，它不计入你的已知法术总数中。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>职业等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.IuzXxwP3EhWGhtXC]{防护善恶}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Cnzcy1Tu7gt6xYHm]{迷踪步}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.YLYeCtTmbjIZsPvN]{加速术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.lopw7wVkPoE7gbNu]{放逐术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.mcQ5lehafMClomzc]{传送法阵}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游侠等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"G2j6gL7q6TmZHs2B","name":"巨灵器皿:瓶中小憩  Genie's Vessel:Bottled Respit","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_monk_fortifyingelixir.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>以一个动作，你可以用魔法消失并进到你的器皿内，器皿将留在你所在的原地。器皿内是与其本身相似的20尺半径，20尺高的圆柱形超维度空间。器皿内部温度适宜，并安放有舒适的垫子和茶几。在器皿之中时，你可以如同身在器皿所在之处一般听到外界的声音。你在器皿内可停留的时间等同于你熟练加值双倍数目的小时。如果你死亡，或是器皿被摧毁，抑或是使用一个附赠动作离开，你将提前从器皿中出来。当你离开器皿时，你出现在距离它最近的不被占据的空间中。在器皿内的一切物件将被留在其中直到被取出，而倘若器皿被摧毁，其中的物品则会完好无损地出现在距离它最近的不被占据的空间中。一旦你进入器皿，直到你完成一次长休后你不能再度进入。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"巨灵宗主等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GTSTP2qr10wmyLDC","name":"符之魔契 Pact of the Talisman","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_warlock_darkarts.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你选用魔契恩泽的时候，此选项可供你选择。</p>\n<p>你的宗主赐予你一个护身符，一个当需要的时候可以帮助佩戴者的护身符。当佩戴者在一次属性检定中失败，他们可以在骰掷结果上增加一个[[/r d4]]骰，这可能将结果变为成功。这一能力可使用的次数等于你的熟练加值，且所有已消耗的次数将会在你完成一次长休之后全部恢复。</p>\n<p>如果你弄丢了护身符，你可以进行一个1小时的仪式从你的宗主那里得到一个替代品。这一仪式可以在一个短休或一个长休过程中完成，且它将会破坏之前的护身符。护身符将会在你死亡时消散为灰尘。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"2","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d4","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"邪术师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GUKctWtG0m69VgFk","name":"激励光环 Mantle of Inspiration","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_AuraMastery.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         当你在3级加入迷惑学院时，你获得将妖精的魔法浸入歌曲的力量，这会为你的盟友带来活力与速度。</p>\n<p>         一个附赠动作，你可以消耗一次@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.FSr7TfaoWRPpUtkD]{诗人激励}的次数，让自己得到华美而出尘的外貌。当你这样做时，选择处于你周围60尺内的一定数量的盟友，你必须能看到他们而他们也必须能看到你，至多等于你的魅力调整值的数量（至少1个）。每个目标获得5点临时生命值。当一个生物获得这些临时生命值时，它可以用反应以其速度移动且不引发借机攻击。</p>\n<p>         临时生命值在你达到此职业的特定等级时得到提升，在5级时提高到8，10级时11，15级时14。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["min(floor(@classes.bard.levels/5)*3+5,14)","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"迷惑学院等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GVKQPsXXOPkZHp8H","name":"引导神力:神助打击 Guided Strike","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/002603.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你可以使用你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.3eyfqXMTJMG9AxYH]{引导神力}来以超自然的精确性进行打击。当你进行一次攻击检定时，你可以使用你的引导神力以在此检定中得到+10加值。你在你看到掷骰后进行决定，但需要在DM宣布此攻击命中与否前声明。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"征服之誓等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"H5J2aANa4OhuuPmv","name":"精魂之盾 Spirit Shield","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Warrior_VictoryRush.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从6级开始，卫士之魂会帮助你为你的盟友提供超自然保护。若你处于@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.gLNFWGL05O0FUNTD]{狂暴}，而一个处于你周围30尺内的，你能看到的其他生物受到伤害，你可以用一个反应动作来降低[[/r 2d6]]的伤害。</p>\n<p>当你达到这一范型的更高等级，你可以防止更多的伤害：10级[[/r 3d6]]，14级[[/r 4d6]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"(min((floor(@classes.barbarian.levels+2)/4),4))d6","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"先祖守卫等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HFbxNO9vpaxzbBFH","name":"恐惧奇兵 Dread Ambusher","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Mage_PotentSpirit.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你精通于伏击的艺术。你在你的先攻投上获得一个等同于你的感知调整值的加值。</p>\n<p>         在每一场战斗的你的第一个回合的开始，你的移动速度增加10尺，直到那个回合结束。如果你在那个回合进行攻击动作，你可以做一次额外的武器攻击作为那一个动作的一部分。如果那次攻击命中，目标受到额外[[/r 1d8]]的武器伤害。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d8",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"幽域追踪者等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HLXS5pd6WfRE3anL","name":"缠绕箭 Grasping Arrow","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_CobraShot.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         当这次攻击击中目标时，咒法魔法会创造一团紧抓着的毒性荆棘来困住目标。被这发箭击中的角色会额外受到[[/r 2d6]]的毒性伤害，他的速度减少10尺，当他在每个回合第一次不使用传送移动1尺以上的距离时他会受到[[/r 2d6]]的挥砍伤害。这个目标或其他能触碰到荆棘的角色可以使用一个动作，以一个成功对抗你的奥术射击DC的力量（体能）检定来解除荆棘。否则，荆棘会在1分钟后或者你再次使用该选项时结束。</p>\n<p>         当你的战士等级到18级时该毒性和挥砍伤害增加到[[/r 4d6]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"abil","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(ceil(@classes.fighter.levels/17)*2)d6",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"int"},"requirements":"魔射手等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HqwYiStgiunCmEG7","name":"奥术射击选项","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_MasterMarksman.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         @Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.w3EVK3XBgi1HZ5K2]{奥术射击}特性允许你在对应等级选择选项。以下选项以字母顺序排列，而且每一个选项都对应一个魔法学派。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.Xr8uiPr41sHR1Uwt]{放逐箭 Banishing Arrow}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.leabhG1wc0d4vP8C]{欺诈箭 Beguiling Arrow}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.yQGz7bYFsOumtt2M]{爆裂箭 Bursting Arrow}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.uCwcaFGcyIGftJr4]{凋零箭 Enfeebling Arrow}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.HLXS5pd6WfRE3anL]{缠绕箭 Grasping Arrow}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.O3iKK0vtmoVxfUqo]{穿透箭 Piercing Arrow}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.i3YthtU7oYjfnZgB]{追踪箭 Seeking Arrow}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.9IoLBGEaRRm3vd6G]{暗影箭 Shadow Arrow}</li>\n</ul>\n<p>         如果选项要求豁免骰，则你的奥术射击豁免检定DC的计算方式如下：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>奥术射击豁免DC</strong> = 8 + 你的熟练加值 + 你的智力调整值</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魔射手等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"IGFbodPoYQ6aujAT","name":"庇护力场 Protective Field","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-flaming-pentagon-red.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你或者另一个对你30尺内可见的生物受到伤害，你可以使用一个反应动作消耗一枚灵能骰，对其降低等同于灵能骰骰出的数值加你的智力调整值的伤害（最小为1），如同你创造了一面瞬间的念力盾牌。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"1 灵能骰。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"max(d(floor((@classes.fighter.levels+1)/6)*2+6)+@abilities.int.mod,1)","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"灵能武士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"IMV7fmo8A5rk0rzm","name":"群逸逃散 Swarming Dispersal","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_animaardenweald_groundstate.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你能将自己散入集群来躲避危险。当你受到伤害时，你能使用你的反应动作让自己活得对该次伤害的抗性。你消失在自己的集群之中，然后传送至30尺内一个未被占据的空间，你在那里与自己的集群一同重新出现。</p>\n<p>你能使用该特性的次数等于你的熟练加值，而你在结束一次长休后重新获得所有消耗的次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"space"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":5,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"集群守卫等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ITah2P5pGZ16tznf","name":"符文大师 Master of Runes","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/inv_misc_profession_book_inscription.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从15级起，你可以对每个你在@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.PcvAQB9tBL9gJkzc]{符文雕刻者}特性中已知的符文激活两次，而不是一次，且你可以在完成一次短休或长休之后恢复所有已使用的次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"符文骑士等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"IVYt0wRd4gXpDjxW","name":"战狂装甲 Battlerager Armor","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/INV_Chest_Chain_13.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从3级起，你得到将@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.Mr81USo2ivUynQ7F]{钉刺甲}作为武器使用的能力。</p>\n<p>        当你穿着钉刺甲并在狂暴中，你可以使用你的附赠动作用钉刺甲对5尺内的目标进行一次近战武器攻击。若攻击命中，钉刺将造成[[/r 1d4]]的穿刺伤害。把你的力量调整加在武器的攻击和伤害骰上。</p>\n<p>另外，当你使用攻击动作去擒抱一个生物，你在擒抱检定成功时对他造成3点穿刺伤害。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4+@mod","piercing"]],"versatile":"3"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战狂道途等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Il7oiu5wAWIjE0lI","name":"醉汉机运 Drunkard’s Luck","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_PowerInfusion.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你11级时，你似乎总是能在最正确的时刻获得机运的反弹。当你进行一次属性检定，攻击检定或豁免检定并在检定中拥有劣势时，你可以花费2点气抵消这个劣势。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":"2 点气。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"醉拳宗等级 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"IlN2GNYt8WWp0txu","name":"奇伟身躯 Great Stature","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_toughness.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从10级起，符文的魔力永久性的改变了你。当你获得该特性时，投掷[[/r 3d4]]。你的身高增加该骰结果的寸数。</p>\n<p>此外，你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.ZMsWAAnCbFFgih3H]{巨人之力}特性造成的额外伤害提高至[[/r 1d8]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"3d4","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"符文骑士等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"IlZZD1Jbpz94jgIG","name":"死之环","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_Chastise.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在一级，你获得操控生死之线的能力，当你使用法术投掷骰子用于恢复生命值为0的生物的生命时，你的每个骰子都可以直接取满。</p>\n<p>         此外，你获得@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.EslxcnZE2B9JYgF1]{维生术}戏法，这不会计入你已知的牧师戏法。对你来说，此法术射程为30尺，并且你可以用附赠动作施展他。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"坟墓领域等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"IrZuNJvar506SCUa","name":"奇械师注法","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Shaman_ImprovedStormstrike.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>　　奇械师发明了许多特殊的注法工艺来快速制造魔法物品。对于没有受过训练的人来说，奇械师就像神奇的工匠，能够在数小时内完成别人需要数周才能完成的事情。</p>\n<p>　　每个注法的描述都会告诉你可以接受它的物品类型。以及所产生的魔法物品是否需要调谐。</p>\n<p>　　有些注法规定了最低的奇械师等级。你必须达到那个等级才能学习该注法。</p>\n<p>　　除非注法的描述中写明，否则你无法重复学习同一个注法。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.1Bu59nkUbv8mf8V4]{折返之靴}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.EjRepZBmGwbmRKp0]{增强奥术法器}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.UgvGe7Lo9kDclj7I]{增强防御}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.wMAuU3oeWrKC1v5a]{增强武器}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.DjgLxtHabE23Vldt]{人工生命仆从}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.E4Se3O8rP1d351lx]{光耀武器}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.FiRczet0VH4xz5FV]{连射武器}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.JoDmNGOyxjhZWulO]{复制魔法物品}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.o71qOD8b8xxWoD7i]{斥力之盾}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.vJma5h5ugW4h3z8m]{抗性盔甲}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.nTzVQzQGCnGoQRKH]{回力武器}</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奇械师等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"IyU8WAr5a0PGGWZM","name":"法器 Spellcasting Focus","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/affliction_04.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以使用一件@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.lHNXs2W0UrXyZ07i]{德鲁伊法器}作为你的游侠法术的法器。一件德鲁伊法器可能会是一枝槲寄生或者冬青木的枝条，用紫衫木或者其他特殊木材制作而成的魔杖或权杖，一柄从活化树木上取来的法杖，或是一件混合了神圣动物的羽毛、毛发、骨头与牙齿的物件。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游侠等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"J3kFXzNNsl6MAAYH","name":"妖思魅缕 Beguiling Twist","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_ardenweald_paladin_spring.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>妖精荒原的魔法护卫着你的心灵。你在对抗造成恐惧与魅惑的豁免检定上具有优势。</p>\n<p>另外，120尺内你可见的一个生物成功地通过了一个对抗魅惑或恐惧的豁免检定时，你可以用你的反应迫使120尺内你可见的另一个生物通过一个DC为你的法术DC的感知豁免。若其豁免失败，则目标会被你魅惑或恐惧(由你选择) 一分钟。目标能够在他的每回合结束时重复豁免，若其豁免成功，则效果终止。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":120,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"妖精漫游者等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"J4PCHlmBmtS4CRSB","name":"战斗洞察 Insightful Fighting","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_deathwing_assualtaspects.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         3级时，你得到了解到一个敌人的战术并加以反制的能力。以一个附赠动作，你对于一个你能看见的，并非失能的生物进行一次感知（洞察）检定，对抗目标的魅力（欺瞒）检定。若你成功，你可以在你并未对该生物具有优势时对他发动@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.AlFAC3Lz1ud2ry9T]{偷袭}攻击，但在你的攻击骰有劣势时不行。</p>\n<p>         这个效果持续1分钟或直到你成功的对另一个目标使用了战斗洞察为止。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"审判官等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"JRyFQmsWflAFkBgN","name":"咒剑诅咒 Hexblade's Curse","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/1Ability_Rogue_CutToTheChase%20-%20.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从1级起，你得到了向一个敌人施加恶毒诅咒的能力。以一个附赠动作，选择一个处于你周围30尺内，你能看见的生物。该目标被诅咒1分钟。该诅咒将会在目标死亡、你死亡、你陷入失能时提前结束。直到诅咒结束，你得到下述的好处：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你对被诅咒目标的伤害检定中得到加值。加值等于你的熟练加值。</li>\n<li>你对被诅咒目标的任何攻击检定，若在[[/r d20]]中投出19或20，则形成一次重击。</li>\n<li>若被诅咒的目标死亡，你恢复等于你邪术士等级+你的魅力调整值（至少为1）的生命值。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>直到你完成了一次短休或长休，</span>你不能再次使用此特性。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["max(@classes.warlock.levels+@abilities.cha.mod,1)","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"咒剑士等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
