{"_id":"Js0Gw3ObrSuyKZPO","name":"额外德鲁伊法术 Additional Druid Spells","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/nature/leaf-juggle-humanoid-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>以下列表中的法术扩展了《玩家手册》中的德鲁伊法术列表。该列表是按法术环阶而非角色等级来编排的。如果一个法术可以作为仪式施放，仪式标签会出现在法术名称之后。每个法术都在《玩家手册》中，除非它有一个星号（TCE第三章的法术）。《珊娜萨万事指南》也提供了更多法术。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>环阶</th>\n<th>扩展法术</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>一环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.IuzXxwP3EhWGhtXC]{防护善恶}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>二环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.umqpL5B9ccbkpJtJ]{卜筮术[R]}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.t8Kc66UhZbrerC9x]{不灭明焰}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.1bUnNgI45qffE1P9]{变巨/缩小术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.exBreA0aIOBCV2hi]{野兽召唤术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>三环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.XfYgB18GC8OgETjG]{活力灵光}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.srjt2KPpCAtQGe7W]{元素武器}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.TkFsGmyAeHknESJ4]{回生术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.p12lhL5QyiAvgpTx]{精类召唤术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>四环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.0An7Gb3wSSffcHhV]{预言术[R]}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.AdWubx1kFJLe8QDa]{火焰护盾}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.9Yhs9yVaMLPnDlSC]{元素召唤术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>五环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.z9HXB89B3uO5NHW8]{寒冰锥}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>六环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.oLtyOvrWeLNEJDIE]{石化术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>七环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.eyGGLBnzrsZ5wCRB]{魔法徽记}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>八环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.FUiSyN2j2j3ufukn]{焚云术}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability"