{"_id":"K1uqnxIh9uueqWon","name":"钉刺反冲 Spiked Retribution","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Warrior_Safeguard.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从14级起，每当你5尺内有生物用近战攻击命中你，同时你处于@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.gLNFWGL05O0FUNTD]{狂暴}中且并非失能，攻击者将立即受到3点穿刺伤害。你必须穿着@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.Mr81USo2ivUynQ7F]{钉刺甲}才能使用这个能力。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["3","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战狂道途等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"KBa0zvvGmsIQzAWM","name":"警戒 Brace","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/light_02.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当一个生物移动进你的触及范围而你手握武器时，你能以一个反应消耗一枚卓越骰对该生物进行一次武器攻击。如果攻击命中，将消耗的卓越骰加入此次攻击的伤害检定中。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战斗大师等级 3，卓越技巧，战技专家","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
