{"_id":"Ke8bj2JtOarcO9Rh","name":"灵能天赋：心灵低语 Psionic Power：Psychic Whispers","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_bastion_druid1.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你能够利用灵能力在自己和他人之间建立起基于心灵感应的交流——在需要无声渗透时这堪称完美。以一个动作，掷一个灵能骰，从可见的生物中选择一到至多等同于你熟练加值数量的生物，你和选择的生物获得通过心灵感应进行交流的能力。在等同于灵能骰结果个小时内，你可以和选择生物进行双向的心灵感应交流，但在发送或接收信息时（无需动作），你和选择生物之间的距离不可超过一英里。不会说任何语言的生物无法通过此方法进行交流，而且生物可以随时终止心灵感应的链接（无需动作）。你和链接的生物不需要能说同一种语言也能互相理解话语。</p>\n<p>你每次长休后的第一次使用这个能力不会消耗你的灵能骰，在其它情况下使用这个能力的话，你会消耗灵能骰。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":2,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"d(floor((1+@classes.rogue.levels)/6)*2+6)","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魂刃等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"KgKexdofASH0yWMb","name":"梦幻舞步 Fancy Footwork","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ABILITY_HUNTER_POSTHASTE.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从第 3 级选择该范型起，你学会了如何闪身避过攻击并化解对方追加的攻势。你在自己回合内对一个生物发动一次近战攻击后，该生物在你回合剩下的时间内都将无法对你发动借机攻击。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游荡剑客等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"KyGD0UqLk90Er2cd","name":"熟练探险家 Deft Explorer","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_Zone_Feralas.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<p>替代@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.KVZtpKSvwrkYSE5p]{自然探索者}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>　　你是一个无与伦比的探险家和求生专家。你在1级时获得对应的特性，然后在第6级和第10级时再各获得对应的特性。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1级：@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.dyR8ImgN3MyQCMJ1]{精明 Canny}</li>\n<li>6级：@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.WYSbzjOzh5IVQYR1]{越野 Roving}</li>\n<li>10级：@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.xFXT58CpzavsEswS]{不知疲倦 Tireless}</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":"","long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"游侠等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"KyeKeVKvTJbZdiBG","name":"完美装甲 Perfected Armor","type":"feat","img":"icons/commodities/tech/claw-mechanical.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.wefEDw2QaHeaBZig]{奥能装甲}根据其型号获得下列额外好处。</p>\n<dl>\n<dt><strong>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.8Ron0AAuUy21J0D1]{守护者}</strong></dt>\n<dd>　　对你奥能装甲能量系统的改进使你能够释放强大的拉力。当你可见的一个体型为巨型或更小的生物在距离你 30 尺内的地方结束其回合时，你能以一个反应迫使该生物对你的法术豁免 DC 进行一个力量豁免检定，失败将被拉向你最多 30 尺。如果你将目标拉到距离你 5 尺的地方，作为此反应的一部分，你能对该生物进行一次近战武器攻击。<br />　　你每天能够执行此反应的次数等于你的熟练加值。在完成一次长休后将恢复所有可用次数。</dd>\n<dt><strong>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.0dvnmcfFn2Nf1DMP]{渗透者}</strong></dt>\n<dd>　　任何被你闪电发射器造成闪电伤害的生物将在你的下个回合到来前发光。发光的生物会放出 5 尺半径的微光光照，当它试图攻击你时，光芒会突然增强，使其在针对你的攻击检定中具有劣势。另外，下次针对发光生物的攻击检定具有优势。如果那次攻击命中，将额外造成[[/r 1d6]]闪电伤害。</dd>\n</dl>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"装甲师等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Kz5Ylv8DxVzoXvV9","name":"超然抗性 Supernatural Resistance","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_DeathKnight_IceBoundFortitude.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         第 15级时，该圣骑士获得对非魔法武器的钝击、刺穿、挥砍伤害的抗性。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"破誓者等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"VvH1R7vylcS99tLw","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"physical"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_DeathKnight_IceBoundFortitude.png","label":"获得非魔法的钝击、刺穿、挥砍抗性","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.Kz5Ylv8DxVzoXvV9","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LAl07qwQm6SRZ3TY","name":"创造学院 College of Creation（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_racial_mastercraft.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>吟游诗人相信这个宇宙是一个艺术作品&mdash;&mdash;是第一群的巨龙和神的造物。这种创造工作包含了韵律，并且一直到今天，通过我们处在的现实，都能听到其袅袅不绝的回音。这种有魔力的韵律被称作造物之歌。创造学院的吟游诗人引用这原始的歌曲，以此为基础创作舞蹈，音乐和诗篇。他们的师长们大多如此教诲：&ldquo;在日月周转出现之前，那一曲颂歌就已经存在于这世上，它唤醒了这个世界的第一次黎明破晓。它的旋律是如此的欢快，就连树木和石头听了也会开口歌唱。世间万物，包括树木和石头，都无时不吟唱着这曲子。学习这造物之歌吧，我的学生们，你也能让群山与你合唱，与你共舞。&rdquo;</p>\n<p>矮人和侏儒经常鼓励他们之中的吟游诗人去学习造物之歌，以之为师。而在龙裔之间，造物之歌有着崇高的地位，因为传说中所描绘的巴哈姆特和提亚马特&mdash;&mdash;巨龙中的最杰出者&mdash;&mdash;是造物之歌最早的两位歌者。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"吟游诗人等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LC0R71ezPGGNlSco","name":"回音化身 Echo Avatar","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_SpellWarding.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从7级起，你能暂时地将你的意识转移到回音上。使用一个动作，你能用你的回音的双眼和双耳来视物与聆听。在这期间，你本体处于目盲和耳聋状态。你能维持这种效果至多10分钟，并且你能随时终止该效果（无需动作）。当你用这种方法操纵回音时，它能远离你至多1000尺而不被摧毁。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EGtW","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"回音骑士等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LDGNpqngq73M9oZs","name":"死卫","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_SpiritualGuidence.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从六级开始，你可以阻碍死亡的前进。作为一个反应，当你或你30尺内的可见盟友被重击，你可以将此变为普通命中，所有重击引起的效果无法起效。</p>\n<p>         你可以使用此能力的次数等同于你的感知调整值（至少一次），当你完成长休，你重获使用过的次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"max(@abilities.wis.mod,1)","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"坟墓领域等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LKHVFz6EN8esfr4O","name":"细致入微 Eye for Detail","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Druid_PredatoryInstincts.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         3级起，你可以使用附赠动作来进行一次感知（观察）检定来侦测到一个隐藏的生物或物体，或者是进行一次智力（调查）检定来揭示和破译线索。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"审判官等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LKeN570q23kXHc7k","name":"高潮乐章 Creative Crescendo","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_priest_wordsofmeaning.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.SoROktB6wHO25o9l]{造物表演}特性创造物品时，你可以一次性不只一件物品。你能一次创造的物品数量等于你的魅力调整值（最低为两件物品）。如果同时创造的物品总数超过了这个数值，那么你可以选择你先前创造的物品中的哪几件将会消失不见。你所创造的物品中只有一件可以达到你创造物品的大小峰值，其他的必须是小型或者微型。</p>\n<p>你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.SoROktB6wHO25o9l]{造物表演}特性不再有使用所创造物品的价值限制。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"创造学院等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LNfcTaOrXMOayKyK","name":"魔炮师 Artillerist","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_LockAndLoad.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         魔炮师是在战场上投射能量、炮弹和爆炸物的专家。这种破坏力在终末战争中受到所有军队的重视。而现在，战争已经结束，这一专业的部分人员开始试图运用自己的力量来消灭科瓦雷中的战争火种，从而建立一个更加和平的世界。</p>\n<p>         看上去不像，但事实上是卡尼斯家族战俑计划关键人物的侏儒奇械师Vi一直都大力宣扬要做正确的事：“现在这个时代，应该致力于修复，而不是把一切都轰下地狱。”</p>\n<h3><strong>本职工具</strong></h3>\n<p>         当你在第三级选择此专业时，你获得@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.A4B41FB9DAE8B865]{木匠工具}的熟练。如果你已经拥有此熟练，作为代替，你能获得另一种工匠工具的熟练。</p>\n<h3><strong>魔炮师法术</strong></h3>\n<p>         从第3级起，只要你达到相应的职业等级，魔炮师法术表格中的法术总是被视为已准备。这些法术对你来说是奇械师法术，且不会计入你可以准备法术的总数。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>职业等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.6EjLIIN4ug7eSp4P]{护盾术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.8GM6YBgYFPIcFXKg]{雷鸣波}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.IkgKSSiBuGa5TPLB]{灼热射线}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.3m0QZZAQfR4jXS9q]{粉碎音波}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Uh3zcz4PO4DXP3Dj]{火球术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.WLWSZA4pZSGb0Mku]{风墙术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.u2MG84qW8YLuECHa]{冰风暴}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.agTzLRmgNSVghaGk]{火墙术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.z9HXB89B3uO5NHW8]{寒冰锥}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.31jKHMGJ0vlqdvQU]{力场墙}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奇械师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"HVIxV4A7HjdGVPtt","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.toolProf.value","mode":2,"value":"calligrapher"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_LockAndLoad.png","label":"获得木匠工具熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.LNfcTaOrXMOayKyK","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LUKdeJg2uAVPG7Jh","name":"风暴之盾 Shield of The Storm","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_ShieldofVengeance.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在10级时，你学会了运用你的风暴的掌控力来保护你的盟友。处于你灵光内的、你选择的生物得到你的风暴之魂特性所带来的伤害抗性。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"风暴先驱等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LY72E6ulmIxqadFA","name":"奥术宗师 Arcane Mastery","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_BG_winEOS.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从17级起，你从法师的施法列表中选择6环、7环、8环、9环法术各一，并将它们加入自己的领域法术列表。你总是准备了它们，并且对你而言它们被视为牧师法术。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奥秘领域等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LhefyQBwJJlkUD96","name":"狂怒风暴 Raging Storm","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_ElementalAbsorption.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在14级时，你能引导的风暴之力变得更加强大，足以打击你的敌人。效果基于你为风暴灵光选择的环境类型。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>沙漠。</strong>当处于你灵光中的生物在一次攻击命中你后，你可以用你的反应迫使该生物立刻做一次敏捷豁免。豁免失败则受到等于你野蛮人等级一半数值的火焰伤害。</li>\n<li><strong>海洋。</strong>任何处于你灵光中的生物若被你以一次攻击击中，你可以用你的反应迫使该生物进行一次力量豁免，否则如同被波浪拍打般被击倒在地，变为俯卧状态。</li>\n<li><strong>冻原。</strong>每当你的风暴灵光激活时，你可以选择一个你可以看见的、处于灵光里的生物。该生物必须通过一次力量检定，否则其速度降为0，直到你的下一个回合开始，如同魔法的冰霜冻结了它。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"风暴先驱等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LiZlPc65hISeVSrS","name":"暴风狂怒 Storm's Fury","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_LightningOverload.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         14级起，每当你在一次近战攻击中被命中，你可以用你的反应动作对攻击者造成等于你术士等级的闪电伤害。此外，攻击者必须进行一次力量豁免，DC等于你的术士法术豁免。一旦豁免失败，攻击者将被直线推开20尺。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"被近战攻击命中。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["@classes.sorcerer.levels","lightning"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"str","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"狂怒风暴等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LqBlv1BYu1IQVkgj","name":"坚定之印 Warding Maneuver","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/1ability_toughness%20.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从3级起，你能够恐吓你的敌人，抑制他们的攻击并惩罚他们。当你以一次近战武器攻击击中一名敌人时，你可以标记他直到你的下一个回合，这个效果会提前结束，如果你失能，死亡或者有其他人标记该敌人。</p>\n<p>         在你的5尺之内，如果他的攻击不是以你为目标，该名被你标记的敌人的攻击骰承受劣势。另外，如果该敌人对除你之外的人造成了伤害，在你的下一个回合你可以用一个附赠动作对该敌人进行一次特殊近战攻击，你这次攻击骰有优势，且如果击中，攻击武器对目标额外造成等同于你战士等级一半的伤害。</p>\n<p>         无论你标记了多少名角色，你能够使用的特殊攻击次数等同于你的力量调整值（至少为1），而且你在长休后重新获得所有被消耗的特殊攻击次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"max(@abilities.str.mod,1)","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["floor(@classes.fighter.levels/2)",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"骑兵等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Lrza2kTrMaxpVtAn","name":"投火机 Flamethrower","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Fire_Ragnaros_LavaBolt.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>炮台在你指定的一个15尺锥形范围内发射火焰。该区域内的每个生物必须对你的法术豁免DC做一次敏捷豁免检定，如果豁免失败则受到[[/r 2d8]]火焰伤害，成功的豁免检定将使伤害减半。火焰会点燃该地区内任何未被穿戴或携带的易燃物品。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":15,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"cone"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"int","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d8","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魔炮师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
