{"_id":"Lyh1CHHHq3661ZBF","name":"精准之眼 Unerring Eye","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_MasterMarksman.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         13级时，你得到侦测魔法欺瞒的能力。以一个动作，你感知到你周围30英尺内的幻术存在，不在天生形态下的变形生物，和其他意在欺瞒感官的魔法，前提是你没有目盲或耳聋。你能了解到了有一个效果正在试图欺骗你，不过你并没有得到对其后所掩盖的真相和对他真实本质的特殊洞察力。</p>\n<p>         你可以使用这个功能的次数等于你的感知调整值（至少一次），当你完成一次长休，你重新获得所有次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"max(@abilities.wis.mod,1)","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"审判官等级 13","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"MHQWmwnAOD1ANEf0","name":"战术大师 Master of Tactics","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_Faction_LoreWalkers.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从第3级开始，你可以把协助动作作为附赠动作使用。此外，当你使用协助动作帮助一个盟友攻击一个生物时，如果目标可以看到你或者听到你的话，攻击的目标可以在30尺以内，而不是你的5尺之内。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"策士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"MbnpxEl8GyCGcs6u","name":"醉拳宗 Way of the Drunken Master（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Monk_DrunkenHaze.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>醉拳宗的导师教导其学徒跟随醉汉古怪且不可预测的行为来进行移动。一个醉拳大师总是摇摇晃晃、蹒跚摇摆着他的脚，表演出一个不尽人意，看似无能的战斗者。然而他们飘忽不定的跌撞通常掩盖了一个精心执行的阻挡，招架，推进，攻击和撤退，所有一切组合成完美的舞蹈。</p>\n<p>醉拳大师常常喜欢装疯卖傻，为沮丧者带来欢乐，或对傲慢者表现出谦卑，但当他们加入战斗时，醉拳大师或许会是一个令人发狂的，狡诈的敌人。</p>\n<p><strong>额外熟练项Bonus Proficiencies</strong></p>\n<p>    当你3级时，若你还没有获得表演技能项熟练，则你熟练之。你的武术技巧将战斗与舞者的精确及小丑的滑稽混合在一起。如果你还未获得@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.C0D09255C48343B1]{酿酒工具}的熟练，你也能同时得到。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"武僧等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"GYZNLz1EcCABtbBN","changes":[{"key":"data.skills.prf.value","mode":4,"value":"1"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Monk_DrunkenHaze.png","label":"获得表演熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.MbnpxEl8GyCGcs6u","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null},{"_id":"UFjLqhQyLB2UUmvh","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.toolProf.value","mode":2,"value":"brewer"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Monk_DrunkenHaze.png","label":"获得酿酒工具熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.MbnpxEl8GyCGcs6u","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Mbve5vcutPLRe7MJ","name":"炼金师 Alchemist","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Monk_Ability_CherryManaTea.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         炼金师是将奇异的原料混合在一起以产生种种新物质的专家，炼金师的创造物能用来延续生命，也能用来夺走生命。炼金术是最古老的奇械师技艺，它的多功能性在战争与和平时都长期受到重视。。</p>\n<h3><strong>本职工具</strong></h3>\n<p>         当你在第三级选择此专业时，你获得@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.EFBBAE8B63126638]{炼金工具}的熟练。如果你已经拥有此熟练，作为代替，你能获得另一种工匠工具的熟练。</p>\n<h3><strong>炼金师法术</strong></h3>\n<p>         从第3级起，只要你达到相应的职业等级，炼金师法术表格中的法术总是被视为已准备。这些法术对你来说是奇械师法术，且不会计入你可以准备法术的总数。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>职业等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.L6dK0A5IfpiXRhdm]{治愈真言}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.PZQqlG5R6G24aWtm]{致病射线}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.TEZY0aYJtnuU4FlW]{炽焰法球}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.jR5afVVOCCwjkbz2]{马友夫强酸箭}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.gjE6zBmfdUOwXiae]{气化形体}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.6PTF3SN0jxkEqv6W]{群体治愈真言}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.AVumturalJuP4paw]{枯萎术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.4gLdaCM7rxoNhj8d]{防死结界}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.T39k39dbE2poIFc5]{死云术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.63gAxMpLpbVW9Oja]{死者复活}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奇械师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"ij90jkWmQ2NPt2p2","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.toolProf.value","mode":2,"value":"alchemist"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Monk_Ability_CherryManaTea.png","label":"获得炼金工具熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.Mbve5vcutPLRe7MJ","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Mef6X3GisJm29HkN","name":"一人成军 Legion of One","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_PrayerofSpirit.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从18级起，当你用一个附赠动作使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.2Rgb3ND4IL7eMZgg]{显现回音}时，你能创造两个回音，并且这些回音能够共存。如果你尝试创造第三个回音，那么前面的两个回音就会被摧毁。你能够在其中一个回音的位置上进行的所有事情都能用另一个回音进行替换。</p>\n<p>         此外，当你投掷先攻时，如果你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.vZQhdyZfnTpMGVoJ]{释放化身}特性没有剩余可用次数，那么你重获一次释放化身的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EGtW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"回音骑士等级 18","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"My3oEiXWQLulUxDs","name":"扰神之词 Unsettling Words","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpsvignettewikianocookienetwowimages552Spellmiscemotionafraidpngrevisionlatestcb20090317211041pathprefixru.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         3级起，你可以编造一些带有魔法的词语，让一个生物感到不安并怀疑自身。你可以用一个附赠动作消耗一次@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.FSr7TfaoWRPpUtkD]{诗人激励}次数，并选择你身边60尺内一个你能看见的生物。骰掷一次诗人激励骰。在你的下一个回合开始前，该生物进行的下一次豁免必须在掷骰结果中减去你的激励骰结果的数字。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MOT","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d(min(floor(@classes.bard.levels/5)*2+6,12))","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"雄辩学院等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"N1XJB0t4e9GM93tI","name":"觉醒魔典 Awakened Spellbook","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/INV_Fabric_MoonRag_01.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>通过特别准备的墨水和书士会所传承的咒语，你唤醒了法术书中具有智能的奥法存在。</p>\n<p>当你持握法术时，它将为你提供以下增益：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你可以将本书用作施展法师法术的法器。</li>\n<li>当你消耗法术位施展一个法师法术时，你可以将它的伤害类型替换为你法术书内另一个法术的伤害类型：你的法术书用魔法改变了此次施法所用的奥法公式。后一个法术的等级必须与你花费的法术位等级相同。</li>\n<li>当你用仪式施法施展一个法术时，你可以使用法术的正常施法时间，而不用额外增加10分钟。你必须完成一次长休才能再次使用此增益。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>如有必要，你可以在一次短休时用你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.mWchknyJMnozqbPO]{法师之笔}，在空白书本或是你与之同调的魔法法术书上画下奥术魔印。短休结束时，你原本法术书内的意识将会带着旧书它所记载的所有法术转移到新书之中、将其变为你的法术书。如果旧书依旧在某处存在，它上面所记载的所有法术将消失。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"书士会等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"NBjwheX8oDN8LiWF","name":"力量涌动 Power Surge","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/SPELL_HOLY_PERSECUTION.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从6级起，你可以将魔法能量存于体内并于之后增幅你危险异常的法术。在这一存储模式中，这一能量被称为力量涌动。</p>\n<p>你不能储存超过你智力调整值（至少1）的力量涌动。当你完成一次长休，你的力量涌动数重置为1。当你成功用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.as6xgBANCbyoWPXX]{解除魔法}或@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.895yeeloz2EhpEYC]{法术反制}终结一个法术时，你获得1点力量涌动，因为你从你挫败的法术中窃得魔力。当你在没有力量涌动次数时完成一次短休，你获得1点力量涌动。</p>\n<p>每回合一次，当你用一个法师法术对一生物或物体造成伤害时，你可以消耗1点力量涌动来对目标造成额外的力场伤害。额外伤害值等于你的法师等级的一半。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"max(@abilities.int.mod,1)","per":"charges"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(floor(@classes.wizard.levels /2))","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战争法师等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"NOlqB0w6MVAEHyVZ","name":"幽域追踪者 Gloom Stalker（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Ambush.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         幽域追踪者居身于致暗之地：地表深处，暗巷之间，太古丛林，和其他任何光无法照亮的地方。很多人进入到这种地区都会有种强烈的不安，但是幽域追踪者却能在黑暗中大胆冒险，在敌人能够触及到更开阔的地区之前搜寻并袭击他们。这种游侠经常能在幽暗地区中被找到，但是他们会前往任何邪恶势力蛰伏的地区。</p>\n<h3><strong>幽域追踪者魔法</strong></h3>\n<p>         3级起，当你到达指定游侠等级时你学会一个额外法术，如幽域追踪者法术列表所示。这些法术对你视为游侠法术，它不计入你的已知法术总数中。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>职业等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.ju3LXSi72l6vso3l]{易容术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.NddIAsoWizuASEW2]{魔绳术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.wnJNHkm5kThiJixx]{恐惧术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Au584WRiGch84PXI]{高等隐形术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.pur5TFHAEgLmx0pz]{伪装术}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游侠等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
