{"_id":"O3iKK0vtmoVxfUqo","name":"穿透箭 Piercing Arrow","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_Quickshot.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你使用你的变化系魔法使你的箭变得虚无缥缈。当你使用该选项时，你不用为该次攻击投攻击骰，取而代之，这只箭会在消失前划出一条一尺宽30尺长的直线。这只箭会无害地穿过物品且无视遮蔽。每一个在这条直线上的角色都必须通过一个敏捷豁免。如果失败，角色会受到如同被这只箭击中的伤害和额外[[/r 1d6]]的穿刺伤害。如果成功，伤害减半。</p>\n<p>         当你的战士等级到18级时该穿刺伤害增加到[[/r 2d6]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"line"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(ceil(@classes.fighter.levels/17))d6","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"int"},"requirements":"魔射手等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"O58fjWGmw7bI6kmN","name":"坟墓领域（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_FiegnDead.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         死神俯瞰生死之线，对他们来说，死亡和死后生活是多元宇宙的基础组成，玷污死者的宁静不可饶恕。死神包括克蓝沃，维婕斯，不朽评议会的祖灵，哈迪斯，阿努比斯和奥西里斯。他们的追随者让彷徨的灵魂安息，摧毁不死生物，安抚垂死之人。他们的神术可以暂时让人远离死亡，特别是那些有重要的事要做的人。这是延迟死亡而非否定死亡，死亡终究到来。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>牧师等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.XT4GwLQNAuPvtnrF]{灾祸术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.DEl8kc5vGwLCNYpR]{虚假生命}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.uzWirpWyQshzp1l0]{遗体防腐}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.VRvKmIZL44nZWKaa]{衰弱射线}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.TkFsGmyAeHknESJ4]{回生术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.FKjra48NDHtB4518]{吸血鬼之触}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.AVumturalJuP4paw]{枯萎术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.4gLdaCM7rxoNhj8d]{防死结界}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.XK3IvcqPquyj1W3P]{防活物护罩}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.63gAxMpLpbVW9Oja]{死者复活}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"牧师等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OK8sGplGcTJljgcH","name":"牧人之环 Circle of the Shepherd（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/002587.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>          牧人之环的德鲁伊通晓如何与自然的精魂进行沟通，尤其是野兽之魂与妖精，他们也常常呼唤这些精魂援助自己。这些德鲁伊认为所有的活物都在自然界中发挥作用，因此他们致力于对动物的保护。游牧者们，会在已知范围内尽他们所能地聆听野兽的控诉。他们监视威胁到自然的怪物，斥退进行不必要杀戮的猎人，预防文明侵犯动物栖息地和迁徙所需路径。许多游牧之环的德鲁伊乐意远离城镇，为将时间花费于管理荒野生物而感到充实。</p>\n<p>          牧人之环的成员通常会因为以下理由进行冒险：对抗那些威胁到他们管理的势力，或者是寻找有助于自己护卫职责的知识和力量。无论这些德鲁伊走到哪里，荒野的精魂都会与他们同行。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"德鲁伊等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OONhbFq0WDjCE1uY","name":"减震场 Dampening Field","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/images/b_08.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你在敏捷（隐匿）检定中具有优势。如果你的盔甲原本会让你在此检定上具有劣势，优势和劣势将会正常抵消。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"装甲师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OdvtbOfnUru8HxOx","name":"力场弩炮 Force Ballista","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Fire_TwilightFlameBolt.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>对一个距离炮台120尺以内的生物或物体进行远程法术攻击。击中时，目标受到[[/r 2d8]]力场伤害，如果目标是一个生物，它将向远离炮台的方向推开5尺。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":120,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"int","actionType":"rsak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"如果目标是一个生物，它将向远离炮台的方向推开5尺。","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d8","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魔炮师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OiCopLiGu5RAozZl","name":"引导神力:和平使节 Emissary of Peace","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003556.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你可以使用你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.3eyfqXMTJMG9AxYH]{引导神力}来以神圣力量增强自己的存在。以一个附赠动作，你为自己在接下来的10分钟内进行的下次魅力（说服）检定中提供+5加值。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"救赎之誓等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OnxBC6Vx8CVxOc5c","name":"突袭打击 Sudden Strike","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_DualWield.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从17级起，你可以以致命的速度进行打击。若你在你的回合进行攻击动作，你可以以一个附赠动作进行一次额外的攻击。此攻击可以从你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.AlFAC3Lz1ud2ry9T]{偷袭}中收益，即使你已经在此回合中使用了它，但是你不能在一回合中对同一目标偷袭一次以上。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"斥候等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Opql2v9FQ3knZ7nh","name":"超魔法：追踪法术 Metamagic ：Seeking Spell","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/yellow_34.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>　　当你因法术进行一次攻击检定并击失时，你可以使用2术法点重投之。你必须使用重投的结果。</p>\n<p>　　追踪法术超魔可以与其他超魔法选项合用。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":"2 术法点。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"术士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OskQEW6LVtTAJKVm","name":"荒野伙伴 Wild companion","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/nature/wolf-paw-glow-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你获得召唤呈现动物形态的精魂的能力，以一个动作，你能够消耗一次@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.pORTgCToV9NLPWo1]{荒野变形}使用次数来施放一次无需材料的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.daB7oGSKy1BglKlt]{获得魔宠}法术。</p>\n<p>当你以此方法施放该法术时，魔宠的类型是精类而不是野兽，魔宠会在等同于你德鲁伊等级一半的小时数后消失。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"德鲁伊等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"PNbQpTrPiuMx4Ua4","name":"储法物品 Spell-Storing Item","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_Windfury.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         当你达到第11级时，你将习得如何在一个物体中储存一个法术。当你完成一次长休，你能够触摸一件简易武器、军用武器或一个你可以将其作为法器使用的物品，从@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.spell-table.7bW4ja0jU2axivqt]{奇械师法术列表}中选择一个施法时间为一个动作的1环或2环法术（你不需要准备这个法术）。</p>\n<p>         任何在手中持有该物品的生物能够使用你的施法关键属性来以一个动作通过该物品产生储存法术的效果。如果该法术需要专注，则启动物品的生物必须进行专注。该法术将留存在物品中，直到使用次数用完（最大使用次数等于你智力调整值的两倍（至少两次））或直到你再次使用该特性。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奇械师等级 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"PTCrPW76ym8UFl6t","name":"蜂聚集群 Gathered Swarm","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_ardenweald_priest1.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>无形自然精魂形成的集群与你形影不离并会在战斗中对你施以援手。直到你死亡，集群会存在于你的空间中，在你身上爬行或在你周身的空间里飞舞或窜动。你决定集群的外观，或者你通过按照集群外观表格掷骰生成其外表。</p>\n<h3>集群外观 Swarm Appearance</h3>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>[[/r D4]]</th>\n<th>外观</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>群聚的昆虫</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>微小的枯枝怪</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>飞舞的群鸟</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>好动的皮克精</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>在你的回合中每回合一次，当你以一次攻击命中一个生物之后，你能让集群以以下一种方式助你一臂之力。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>这次攻击的目标因集群受到[[/r 1d6]]穿刺伤害。</li>\n<li>这次攻击的目标必须成功通过对抗你法术DC的力量豁免检定否则被集群朝你选择的方向水平移动最多15尺。</li>\n<li>你被集群朝着你所选择的方向水平移动5尺。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"集群守卫等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"PcvAQB9tBL9gJkzc","name":"符文雕刻者 Rune Carver","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_paladin_empoweredseals.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从3级起，你可以使用魔法符文来增强你的装备。你可以从下列的被描述的符文当中，选择并学会两个符文，且每当你在此职业中升一级，你可以从此特性中选择一个不同的符文来替换一个你已知的符文。当你达到特定的职业等级，你可以学会更多的符文，具体数量如下表所示。</p>\n<h3><strong>已知符文数量 Runes Known</strong></h3>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>战士等级</th>\n<th>已知符文数</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>第3级</td>\n<td>2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>第7级</td>\n<td>3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>第10级</td>\n<td>4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>第15级</td>\n<td>5</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>每当你完成了一次长休，你可以接触数量等于你已知符文数物品，并在每个物品上铭刻不同的符文。符合条件的物品必须为一把武器、一套盔甲、一面盾牌、一件首饰或者任何其他你可以穿着或手持的物品。你的符文会保留在物品上直到你完成一次长休，且一件物品同时只能承载你的一个符文。</p>\n<p>当你研习符文时，下列的符文成为了你的可选项。如果一个符文具有等级需求，你的战士等级必须达到相应等级才能研习该符文。如果一个符文需要通过豁免检定，你的符文魔法豁免DC等于8+你的熟练加值+你的体质调整值。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>云之符文 Cloud Rune</strong>。该符文模拟了一些云巨人使用的欺骗性法术。当你穿着或持有一个铭刻此符文的物品，你在敏捷（巧手）检定和魅力（欺瞒）检定上获得优势。<br />此外，当你或一个对你30尺内可视的生物经过攻击检定被击中，你可以使用一个反应动作对此符文激活并选中一个除攻击者以外的其他生物。被选中的生物变成该攻击的目标，并适用同样的攻击检定。该异能可转换的攻击效应与攻击距离无关。每当你激活该符文，你无法再次使用该异能直到你完成一次短休或长休。</li>\n<li><strong>火之符文 Fire Rune</strong>。该符文的异能可以引导伟大铁匠的高超技艺。当你穿着或持有一个铭刻此符文的物品，你在进行使用工具的熟练项进行技能检定时，你的熟练加值翻倍。<br />此外，当你使用一次武器攻击击中了一个生物，你可以激活此符文来召唤炽热镣铐：目标受到额外[[/r 2d6]]的火焰伤害，且目标必须通过一次力量豁免检定，如果失败则被束缚1分钟。当目标被炽热镣铐束缚时，目标在它的每回合开始时受到[[/r 2d6]]的火焰伤害。目标可以在每个自己回合结束时重复进行此豁免检定，直到成功解除束缚。每当你激活该符文，你无法再次使用该异能直到你完成一次短休或长休。</li>\n<li><strong>霜之符文 Frost Rune</strong>。该符文的魔力唤起了那些在寒冷荒野中生存下来的存在的力量，比如霜巨人。当你穿着或持有一个铭刻此符文的物品，你在感知（驯兽）检定和魅力（威吓）检定上获得优势。<br />此外，你可以用一个附赠动作对该符文激活来提高你的体能。十分钟内，你的所有使用力量、体质的能力和相关豁免检定获得+2的加值。每当你激活该符文，你无法再次使用该异能直到你完成一次短休或长休。</li>\n<li><strong>石之符文 Stone Rune</strong>。该符文的魔力可以引导和石巨人相关的智慧（judiciousness）。当你穿着或持有一个铭刻此符文的物品，你在感知（洞悉）的检定上获得优势，且你获得120尺的黑暗视觉。<br />此外，当一个30尺内对你可见的生物结束它的回合，你可以使用一个反应动作来对该符文激活，并强迫该生物进行一次感知豁免检定。如果检定失败，该生物被你魅惑一分钟。如果以该形式被魅惑，此生物移动速度降为0且进入失能状态，陷入梦幻般的麻木状态。目标可以在每个自己回合结束时重复进行此豁免检定，直到成功解除该状态。每当你激活该符文，你无法再次使用该异能直到你完成一次短休或长休。</li>\n<li><strong>山丘符文 Hill Rune</strong>。（第7级或更高）该符文的魔力可以赋予如山巨人一般的坚韧。当你穿着或持有一个铭刻此符文的物品，你在中毒状态的豁免检定上获得优势，且你对于毒素伤害具有抗性。<br />此外，你可以使用一个附赠动作对该符文激活，获得1分钟的钝击、挥砍和穿刺伤害抗性。每当你激活该符文，你无法再次使用该异能直到你完成一次短休或长休。</li>\n<li><strong>风暴符文 Storm Rune</strong>。（第7级或更高）通过使用该符文，你可以像一个风暴巨人预言者一样瞥见未来。当你穿着或持有一个铭刻此符文的物品，你在智力（奥秘知识）检定上获得优势，且你不会被突袭只要你没有进入失能状态。<br />此外，你可以使用一个附赠动作对该符文激活来进入先知形态，时间为1分钟或直到你失能。在该形态结束之前，当你或另一个60尺内且对你可见的生物进行一次攻击检定、一次豁免检定或一次能力检定，你可以使用一个反应动作使这次检定获得优势或劣势。每当你激活该符文，你无法再次使用该异能直到你完成一次短休或长休。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"符文骑士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"PdBrw1PES4UJnlVT","name":"暗影闪避 Shadowy Dodge","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Arcane_PrismaticCloak.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         15级起，伴随着一缕围绕在你身边的神奇暗影，你能以某种让人始料未及的方式躲闪。无论何时一名角色对你做出一次攻击投掷且那次投掷没有优势，你都能用反应对其施加劣势。你必须在知道攻击投掷的结果之前使用该特性。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"幽域追踪者等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Pjul6aKNCszIRenl","name":"引导神力：无敌健将  Channel Divinity：Peerless Athlete","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpcloud3steamusercontentcomugc842585053237283234D48937CD7A317C4F5E20D8A028AB83BAE4DF370F.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         以一个附赠动作，你可以消耗@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.3eyfqXMTJMG9AxYH]{引导神力}增强你的运动能力。之后的十分钟里，你在力量（运动）和敏捷（杂技）检定上具有优势，你可以推拉抬两倍重量的重物。并且你的跳高跳远距离增加十尺（这会如常消耗你的移动力）。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MOT","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"荣耀之誓等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Px6U4uzpuITF8G2V","name":"迅捷灵光 Aura of Alacrity","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpcloud3steamusercontentcomugc842585136115869684C9C9F90108B8E18485A3B668FBF0DE79280B0176.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你发出灵光，让你和你的同伴以超自然的速度穿越战场。你的步行速度增加10尺。此外，如果你未失能，则任何在你周围5尺范围内开始其回合的同伴的步行速度将增加10尺，直到回合结束。</p>\n<p>         当你达到18级时，灵光的范围增加到10尺。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MOT","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"荣耀之誓等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"wmdHPpBIckys52qT","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.movement.walk","mode":2,"value":"10"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpcloud3steamusercontentcomugc842585136115869684C9C9F90108B8E18485A3B668FBF0DE79280B0176.jpg","label":"增加10尺步行速度","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.Px6U4uzpuITF8G2V","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"PxhqtGi9J3Doht6W","name":"仲夏庭院的芬馥 Balm of the Summer Court","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_ProtectionformNature.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>          2级起，你将被灌注来自仲夏庭院的祝福，由此成为缓解旅者乏顿和伤者痛苦的圣洗池。你得到等同于德鲁伊等级的[[/r d6]]作为代表的妖精能量池。</p>\n<p>          以一个附赠动作，你可以选择一名在你120尺内的可见盟友，并且花费最多等于你德鲁伊等级一半的[[/r d6]]骰。投掷那些骰子并把结果加在一起。目标恢复等于那个总值的生命值。目标同时也得到等同于花费骰子数目的临时生命值。</p>\n<p>          在你结束一次长休之后，你恢复所有花费掉的骰子。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":120,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"@classes.druid.levels","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","healing"],["1","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"梦境之环等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Q7NJcwdlXiX4SPFC","name":"怒不畏死 Rage Beyond Death","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Warrior_IntensifyRage.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从14级开始，驱使你狂暴的神力允许你忽视致命的打击。</p>\n<p>当处于狂暴时，具有0点生命值不会让你昏迷。你仍然必须进行死亡豁免检定，而你在0生命值下受到伤害时承受正常的效果。然而，若你因为未通过死亡豁免检定而即将死去，你拒绝死亡直到你的狂暴结束，如果你那时仍保持0生命值则死亡。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"狂热者等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QDdiLinrHSTLMFya","name":"潜能微尘 Mote of Potential","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/002612.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>每当你给予一个生物以@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.FSr7TfaoWRPpUtkD]{诗人激励}骰时，你可以唱出造物之歌的一个音符，创造一团微小的潜能微尘，在那个生物五尺以内的轨道上环绕。这个微尘是无形且不可被摧毁的，它将一直持续存在直到这个诗人激励骰被消耗掉。这团微尘看起来像一个音符，或是一颗星星，一朵花，抑或其他任何一种艺术或者生命的符号，这将由你来决定。</p>\n<p>当这个生物使用那个诗人激励骰时，这团微尘将会根据这个诗人激励骰被使用的方式——属性检定，攻击检定或者豁免检定——产生不同的额外效果。具体细节如下所示：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>属性检定</strong>。当该生物将诗人激励骰用于增益属性检定时，他可以重新掷一次诗人激励骰并且选择使用其中一个掷骰结果。这团微尘会炸开，发射出多彩而无害的闪光。</li>\n<li><strong>攻击检定</strong>。当该生物将诗人激励骰用于增益攻击检定时，掷出诗人激励骰后，这团微尘会立刻如雷霆般破碎。该生物这次攻击的目标以及其5尺距离内你能看到的由你决定的所有生物必须进行一次体质豁免，其DC为你的施法DC，如果豁免失败，将会承受等同于该诗人激励骰子所掷结果的雷鸣伤害。</li>\n<li><strong>豁免检定</strong>。当该生物将诗人激励骰用于增益豁免检定时，掷出诗人激励骰后，这团微尘会立刻伴随着一段舒缓的音乐消失不见，给予这个生物等同于该诗人激励骰子所掷结果加上你的魅力调整值的临时生命值（最低为1）。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"创造学院等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QNiJ6nJvw24FCLm0","name":"念力宗师 Telekinetic Master","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_mage_supernova_nightborne.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你用意念移动生物和物体的能力无人能及。你可以在无需施法材料的情况下使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.MTNfEcCXSJZ2m2nG]{心灵遥控 Telekinesis}，此时你的施法关键属性为智力。在每一个你对该法术维持专注的回合，包括你使用它的回合，你可以使用一个附赠动作进行一次武器攻击。</p>\n<p>每当你使用以特性施放此法术，你无法再次使用该特性直到你完成一次长休，除非你消耗一个灵能骰来再次使用该特性。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"灵能武士等级 18","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QXOrwsPs3IqQfONF","name":"问道精魂 Consult the Spirits","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Druid_HealingInstincts.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在10级时，你得到和你的先祖之魂进行交流的能力。当你使用此能力，你可以不消耗法术位和材料成分使用一次@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.umqpL5B9ccbkpJtJ]{卜筮术}或@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.WO2nFm8xEVkX4KJy]{鹰眼术}。取代法术描述里的球形探测器，这个法术会在指定位置创造一个无形的先祖之魂。感知是你的施法主属性。</p>\n<p>使用此能力施法后，直到短休或者长休你才可以重新释放。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"先祖守卫等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QcQzIXdwbG4226N9","name":"审判官 Inquisitive（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_Sentinal.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         作为一名典型的审判官，你精于揭开秘密，开解谜团。你不光用锐利的双眼去寻找细节，也使用磨练过的高超技艺去研读其他生物的言辞和表情，以发现他们真实的意图。你娴于找出并击败那些藏身于平民，也以平民为食的怪物，而你的对于知识的掌握和锐利的眼目也让你更好地揭示并终结潜藏的邪恶。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游荡者等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Qctmiuim4M9SfU1E","name":"星我之臂 Arms of the Astral Self","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Monk_DeadlyReach.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>第3级起，你对气的掌握允许你召唤出星我的一部分。以一个附赠动作，你可以花费1点气来召唤你的星我之臂，当你这么做时，你选择的每一个你所见的10尺范围内的生物必须进行一次敏捷豁免检定，如果失败则受到相当于你两倍武艺骰的力场伤害。</p>\n<p>在10分钟内，这些幽光般的手臂会盘旋在你的肩膀附近或环绕着你的手臂（由你选择），你来决定手臂们的外观，如果你失能或死亡，它们就会立即消失。</p>\n<p>当星我之臂出现时，你将获得如下增益：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你进行力量检定和力量豁免检定时，可以用你的感知调整值来代替力量力量调整值。</li>\n<li>你可以用星我之臂进行徒手攻击。</li>\n<li>当你在自己回合用星我之臂进行徒手攻击时，你的触及范围增加5尺。</li>\n<li>当你用星我之臂进行徒手攻击时，可以用感知调整值代替力量或敏捷调整值来进行攻击检定和伤害检定，它们的伤害类型是力场。</li>\n</ul>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":"1 点气。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"wis","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["d(ceil(((@classes.monk.levels)+2)/6)*2+2) + @mod","force"]],"versatile":"2*(1d(ceil(((@classes.monk.levels)+2)/6)*2+2))"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"wis"},"requirements":"星我宗等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QkDzUSuaqmTa1rwN","name":"魔能祈唤：永恒奴役Eldritch Invocation：Undying Servitude","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/affliction_17.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以在不消耗法术位的情况下使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.xYpJGRI4xcMa41kO]{操纵死尸}。每当你这么做时，你不能再次以这种形式使用该法术直到你完成一次长休。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"邪术师等级 5","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Qr4YJIOYH0ArVQVT","name":"妖精漫游者 Fey Wanderer（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_ardenweald_deathknight.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>或来自一位至高妖精的恩惠，或是来自你食用的一枚从能言之树上取下的闪亮果实，或是来自你曾浸游于中的魔法清泉，或是来自其它妙事，你的身侧因那次奇遇而有妖精的魔力缠绕。 无论你是怎么得到你来自妖精的魔法的，你现在是一名代表了凡间与妖精国度双方的游侠——妖精漫游者。你漫步于多元宇宙之时，你轻快的笑声为受压迫者们带来欣喜的希望，你英勇的技艺直击你敌人的恐惧，你所就的伟绩乃是妖精的喜悦，你散步的恐惧乃是妖精的愤怒。</p>\n<h3><strong>妖精漫游者法术</strong></h3>\n<p>你在达到特定等级时学会一个下方妖精漫游者法术列表中列出的魔法。这些法术对你而言视作游侠法术，且不占用你的游侠已知法术数量。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>职业等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.QFBZcGORjnBRgAYo]{魅惑人类}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Cnzcy1Tu7gt6xYHm]{迷踪步}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.as6xgBANCbyoWPXX]{解除魔法}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.u86hMx0ODfccAtu8]{任意门}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.nTjAezWWIOZnxoB1]{假象术}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3><strong>精野之赐</strong></h3>\n<p>你还获得了来自一位妖精盟友或一处妖精神力的神奇祝福。你可以在下方妖精荒原之赐表格中选择你的祝福或者随机决定。</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>[[/r D6]]</th>\n<th>赐礼</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>在你进行长休或短休时，缥缈的蝴蝶在你周身振翅。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>每天黎明，新鲜的、当季的花朵将在你的头发中生长。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>你身上有淡淡的肉桂、薰衣草或肉豆蔻，或另一种令人舒适的药草或香料的香味。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>你的影子会在没人直视它时起舞。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>你的头发中长出纤细的触角或鹿角。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>每天黎明，你的皮肤与头发的颜色会随季节的变换而变化。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游侠等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QrX49LgYJ95vEKEv","name":"鬼魅 Phantom（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_shadow_skull.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>把你击败的敌人的灵魂收集为日常的小物件里，真是个好主意。虽然，我可能需要一整个百科全书来容纳我的黑粉。\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><em>——塔莎</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>  游荡者的生活常常是日复一日的游走在生死边缘，一边冒着生命危险，另一边取走别人的性命。在生死之间冒险的时候，一些游荡者与死亡本身结下了奇妙的不解之缘。他们浸淫于与负能量之中，从死者那里获取知识，直到他们自身都变得如同幽灵一般。盗贼工会对鬼魅们高度重视，因为他们是极其高效的情报员和间谍。</p>\n<p>堕影冥界的诸多影灵专精于这些骇人的技艺，有些甚至愿意传授。在塞尔Thay（被遗忘的国度）与卡尔纳斯Karrnath（艾伯伦）有不少潜心修炼的死灵法师，一名鬼魅可能成为一位法师的密友抑或是左右手。在死神的神殿之中，鬼魅则会是追踪逃避死亡之人并获取墓穴中失落的知识的特工。</p>\n<p>你是如何发现的这一黑暗力量？你是否曾长眠于墓场之中并在醒来时意识到了自己的特异能力？抑或是你在侍奉于一名死神的神殿或盗贼工会中获取了这份力量？</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游荡者等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QskjWm8kaoUH0aGB","name":"钢铁意志 Iron Mind","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpcloud3steamusercontentcomugc842585053237283234D48937CD7A317C4F5E20D8A028AB83BAE4DF370F.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         7级时，你已经磨炼出用来抵御来自于你的猎物的精神影响能量的能力。你获得感知豁免熟练。如果你已经有这项熟练，你可以获得智力或者魅力豁免熟练（取决于你）来代替。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"幽域追踪者等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"N26w6jng5YmoN5JF","changes":[{"key":"data.abilities.wis.proficient","mode":4,"value":"1"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpcloud3steamusercontentcomugc842585053237283234D48937CD7A317C4F5E20D8A028AB83BAE4DF370F.jpg","label":"获得感知熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.QskjWm8kaoUH0aGB","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QwJc4R8XGcqifWRo","name":"锻造领域 Forge Domain（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_BlindingLight.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>    锻造之神是铁匠的守护神，从村里的，做马蹄铁和犁的小铁匠，到制作过击败了恶魔领主的钻石尖秘银箭的强大精灵工匠，锻造之神教导人们，锲而不舍，金石可镂。这些神明的牧师寻找因黑暗力量失落的物品，解放被兽人占领的矿山，发掘制造强力魔法物品必须的珍惜而奇妙的物品。他们为自己的工作自豪并且乐于制造和使用重甲和强力的武器保护自己。锻造之神包括贡德，李奥克斯，昂那塔，莫拉丁，赫淮斯托斯和吉欧布尼乌。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>牧师等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.tyshE8ZcV1Xniej3]{鉴定术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.73yB6CHxGk3Np5ME]{炽焰斩}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.tf3EIMrOkbZvOxSz]{灼热金属}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.14a3v5NF5h5Lgm9J]{魔化武器}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.srjt2KPpCAtQGe7W]{元素武器}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.DBrh7ALD21UoUApP]{防护能量伤害}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.u7JAeqMO5fYhTnMy]{鬼斧神工}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.agTzLRmgNSVghaGk]{火墙术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Lub4e9tYHMHeVo7Y]{活化物件}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Zwe287Drdl1TkG8e]{造物术}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>附赠熟练项Bonus Proficiencies</strong></p>\n<p>    在1级选择此领域时，你获得重甲熟练和铁匠工具熟练。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"牧师等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"HnTQuHlq6HxKzdO1","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.armorProf.value","mode":2,"value":"hvy"},{"key":"data.traits.toolProf.value","mode":2,"value":"smith"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_BlindingLight.png","label":"获得重甲、铁匠工具熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.QwJc4R8XGcqifWRo","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QzZhaAWQvPYyGE6Z","name":"凶蛮无羁 Reckless Abandon","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_Boss_Ignis_01.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从6级起，若你在@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.gLNFWGL05O0FUNTD]{狂暴}中使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.eHoAjddNTEm1m6Gn]{鲁莽攻击}，你可以得到等同你体质调整值的临时生命（最少1点）。当你结束狂暴时它们消失。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["max(@abilities.con.mod,1)","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战狂道途等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"R6yuNxTg2ivSHt8G","name":"洞察力 Insightful Manipulator","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Druid_SupriseAttack.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从第9级开始，如果你至少花1分钟观察或与战斗之外的其他生物进行交互，你可以了解到跟你自己的能力相比较的某些信息。DM告诉你，在你选择的下列两个特征中，是否你的相等、优越或低等：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>智力值</li>\n<li>感知值</li>\n<li>魅力值</li>\n<li>职业等级（如果有的话）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>         如果你的DM允许，你也有可能知道这个生物的一段经历或者它的一个性格特征，如果它有的话。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"minute","cost":1,"condition":"交互或观察"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"策士等级 9","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"R9VbDJOCQk2Mb9eG","name":"予命之手Hand of Healing","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Monk_ZenMeditation.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你的玄秘之触能够愈合伤口。以一个动作，你能花费1点气来接触一个生物，恢复目标1个你的武艺骰+感知调整值数量的生命值。</p>\n<p>当你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.vLuoFN1x3tRWTPdm]{疾风连击}时，你能在不消耗气的情况下用此特性替换一次徒手攻击。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"1 点气。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"touch","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["d(ceil(((@classes.monk.levels)+2)/6)*2+2) + @abilities.wis.mod","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"命流宗等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"RF3cORN1AMVCqgJu","name":"引导神力：暮光圣域 Twilight Sanctuary","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_unused2.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.WPevnsjK8Cjd9Fcl]{引导神力}，用柔和的暮光来振作你盟友的精神。</p>\n<p>你用一个动作展示@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.TJi1q6Bm8IGoJJVL]{圣徽}并使自身散发球体范围的暮光。球体以你为源心，具有30尺半径，其范围内被微光光照充斥。除非你失能或死亡，否则球体跟随你移动并持续存在1分钟。当一个生物（包括你）在球体内结束自己回合时，你能给予它以下好处之一：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>使目标获得[[/r 1d6]]加你牧师等级的临时生命。</li>\n<li>使目标结束一个正使他魅惑或恐慌的效果。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d6 + @classes.cleric.levels","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"暮光领域等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"RGyrqunuHjvYMaMW","name":"风暴之魂 Storm Soul","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Shaman_Ascendance.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在6级时，风暴在你不激活灵光时也能给你带来增益。增益效果基于你选择风暴灵光的环境类型。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>沙漠。</strong>你得到对火焰伤害的抗性，并不会受到极端高温的效果影响。此外，以一个动作，你可以触摸一个没有被他人穿戴或携带的易燃物体，并且点燃它。</li>\n<li><strong>海洋。</strong>你得到对闪电伤害的抗性，并能在水下呼吸。你还获得了30尺的游泳速度。</li>\n<li><strong>冻原。</strong>你得到对冷冻伤害的抗性，并不会受到极端低温的效果影响。此外，以一个动作，你可以触摸水并且把5立方尺的水冻结成冰，这种冰将会在1分钟后融化。如果有生物处于该立方空间中，你的行动将会失败。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"风暴先驱等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"RakISgKJ0fWy44XM","name":"一体共生 Symbiotic Entity","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_rogue_sturdyrecuperate.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在2级时，你获得了向体内的孢子引导魔法的能力。<br />         当你使用你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.pORTgCToV9NLPWo1]{荒野形态}特性时，你可以唤醒这些孢子，而非进行变形。当你这样做的时候，你每在此职业上具有一个等级便获得4点临时生命值。当你这样做时，你获得下列好处：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>当你的孢子光晕特性造成伤害时，额外骰一个伤害骰加在原有的伤害骰上。</li>\n<li>并且你的近战武器攻击对任何被击中的目标造成额外的[[/r 1d6]]点暗蚀伤害。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>         这些好处持续10分钟，或直到你失去所有临时生命值或再次使用了你的荒野形态。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["4*@classes.druid.levels","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"孢子结社等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"RblUGsE7qH9JxlZi","name":"装甲型号 Armor Model","type":"feat","img":"icons/commodities/tech/conduit-transmission-red.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你能够定制你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.wefEDw2QaHeaBZig]{奥能装甲}。当你这么做时，能够从以下两种型号中选择其一：守护者或渗透者。你选择的型号会在你穿着时提供特殊的好处。每种型号都包括一种特殊武器。当你使用该武器攻击时，你可以使用你的智力调整值，而不是力量或敏捷，来进行攻击和伤害检定。只要你手上有@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.B97AB85722BCF651]{铁匠工具}，就可以在完成一次短休或长休后更换你的装甲型号。</p>\n<p><strong>守护者 Guardian。</strong> 你将装甲设计为适合冲锋陷阵。它拥有下列特性：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.ynHB1r1UmBgTYP2t]{雷霆战拳 Thunder Gauntlets}。</strong> 每一只装甲附带的手套在没有持握任何物品时皆可被视为一件简单近战武器，命中后会造成 [[/r 1d8]]雷鸣伤害。被战拳击中的生物，会被装甲释放的魔法性干扰脉冲影响，使其对除你之外的目标攻击时有劣势，直到你的下个回合到来。</li>\n<li><strong>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.jVhNhMk1RTTsycau]{防护场 Defensive Field}。</strong> 在每个你的回合，你能以一个附赠动作获得等于你奇械师职业等级的临时生命值，这会取代你现有的任何临时生命值。如果你脱下装甲，你会失去这些临时生命值。你能执行此附赠动作熟练加值次，在完成一次长休后将恢复所有花费的使用次数。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>渗透者 Infiltrator。</strong> 你出于某些特殊需要对你的装甲进行了定制。它拥有下列特性：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.E06roEzIAhw8cXnY]{闪电发射器 Lightning Launcher}。</strong> 你在胸部或复盖装甲的拳头（根据你的选择）上安装了一个宝石状的节点。它被视为一件简单远程武器，它拥有 90 尺的常规射程和 300 尺的最大射程，在命中后会造成[[/r 1d6]]闪电伤害。每个你的回合一次，你在通过闪电发射器命中一个生物时，能够额外造成[[/r 1d6 ]]闪电伤害。</li>\n<li><strong>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.KPJKrW3H3MaDpzFR]{动力步伐 Powered Steps}。</strong> 你的步行速度增加 5 尺。</li>\n<li><strong>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.OONhbFq0WDjCE1uY]{减震场 Dampening Field}。</strong> 你在敏捷（隐匿）检定中具有优势。如果你的盔甲原本会让你在此检定上具有劣势，优势和劣势将会正常抵消。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"装甲师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"RjUIBp4J1ZHC9bw2","name":"自然面纱 Nature's Veil","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/green_18.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<p>替换@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.qr1XQlGLHVsZANuQ]{遁术}。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>你可以暂时地使用自然的力量将你的身形遮蔽。以一个附赠动作，你可以魔法地使自己与正携带、着装的任何装备变得隐形，直到你的下个回合开始。你可以使用该特性同等于你的熟练加值次，你在完成一次长休后恢复所有的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"round"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":4,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游侠等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"RwSc6vnSC6tO9lBu","name":"掌控浪潮 Controlled Surge","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_ThunderKing_Overcharge.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>每当你掷骰决定@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.qzKSooNxo2zww1oE]{狂野魔法效果}时，你可以掷两次骰子并且选择其中之一作为所释放的狂野魔法效果。如果你掷出的两个骰子数值相同，那么你可以无视这个数字，任意选择一个狂野魔法列表里的效果。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"狂野魔法道途等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"SAuUmmcShvHjX8S0","name":"神秘复原 Unearthly Recovery","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_SurgeOfLight.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>18级起，你具备了克服重伤的能力。当你的hp不足一半时，以一个附赠动作，你可以获得等同于你一半生命值的生命。</p>\n<p>         一旦你使用了这个特性，你就不能再使用它，直到你完成一次长休。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":"生命值不足一半。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["floor(@attributes.hp.max/2)","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"神圣之魂等级 18","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"SFFwY3txdXNZ2f9z","name":"虚体防御 Spectral Defense","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/000411.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在15级时，你的空间传送能力能让你在战斗中流转于空间边缘以减少伤害。当你受到来自于一次攻击的伤害时，你可以使用你的反应以让你自己获得所有对这回合该攻击伤害的抗性。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"边界行者等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"SGpM3zFoir5j7UBo","name":"兽性之魂Beast Soul","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_druid_incarnation.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你体内的野性力量不断增长，让你通过@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.Aaj9ZXCtEk5HagI8]{野兽之形}获得的天生武器被视作魔法武器，以穿透对非魔法伤害的抗性或者免疫。</p>\n<p>你也可以改变你身体的形态以更好的适应不同环境。每当你完成一次短休或者长休，你可以选择其中一项能力，你拥有该能力持续到你完成下一次短休或者长休。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你获得与你行走速度相同的的游泳速度，并且可以在水下呼吸</li>\n<li>你获得与你行走速度相同的攀爬速度，你可以攀爬困难表面，包括倒挂在天花板上。你做这些攀爬时不需要进行检定</li>\n<li>当你跳跃时，你进行一次力量（运动）检定，并把该检定的数值加到你本次跳跃的极限距离上。你每回合只能用这个方式加强跳跃一次。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"野兽道途等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"SInMrQl9LVBYKJYM","name":"狂怒风暴 Storm Sorcery（SCAG）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_UnrelentingStorm.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你内在的魔法源于风元素之力量。也许你在狂风呼啸中诞生，而那狂风因其威力之强而仍被市井传颂；也许你的血脉受到强大风元素生物的影响，比如风元素大公，又或风巨灵。不论情况如何，风暴之魔力早已浸透你的灵魂。</p>\n<p>         风暴术士是极有价值的海员。其魔法足以驾驭其周边的风与气象。他们的能力亦已被证明在对抗沙华鱼人或海盗等水上威胁时极为有效。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"术士等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"SZgmW7BMZyBMtCiz","name":"时间魔法 Chronurgy Magic（EGtW）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003550.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         追随时间使传承的法师们专注于操纵时间，他们学会了如何按照自己的想法来改写现实的流动。利用可预期的秘迹能量，这些法师可以像熟练的乐师演奏乐器那样扭曲时间的流动，在眨眼间赋予他们自己以及他们的盟友战斗优势。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EGtW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"法师等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Sdemym6EHOjHhXJq","name":"先祖守卫 Path of The Ancestral Guardian（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Monk_ChargingOxWave.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>一些野蛮人来自于崇敬他们祖先的文化。这些部落教导我们，过去的战士作为强大的灵魂在世界上徘徊，他们可以引导和保护活着的人。当一个走这条路的野蛮人怒不可遏时，野蛮人会联系到精神世界，并向这些守护者的灵魂求援。利用祖先守护者的野蛮人可以更好地战斗来保护他们的部落和盟友。为了巩固与祖先守护者的联系，走这条路的野蛮人会用精心制作的纹身来掩饰自己，以庆祝他们祖先的行为。这些纹身讲述了战胜可怕的怪物和其他可怕的对手的传奇故事。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"野蛮人等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Sew4Tj3ec9CwH53H","name":"精魂法器 Spiritual Focus","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/inv_ring_ardenweald_02_green.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你使用工具来与精魂沟通，无论这些精魂是历史上的人物，还是虚构的原型。以下物品可作为你施展吟游诗人法术的法器：一根蜡烛、一个水晶球、一个头骨、一个通灵板或者一副塔罗卡牌。</p>\n<p>从6级开始，当你通过精魂法器施放一个造成伤害或恢复生命的吟游诗人法术时，投一枚[[/r d6]]，你在该法术的一次伤害或治疗掷骰中获得等同于该d6掷骰结果的加值。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"VRGR","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d6","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"精魂学院等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"IQE6hAV3ygaTICtD":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.SoROktB6wHO25o9l"}}}
{"_id":"SiYzAyOLXUFow2lF","name":"恶毒言辞 Words of Terror","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_Harass.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         3级时，你学会了将险恶的魔法混入看似无害的语言中。一个听到你说话的生物可能会因此陷入恐惧或妄想。</p>\n<p>         若你单独的对一个类人生物说话至少1分钟，你可以尝试在其心灵中埋下多疑与恐惧的种子。在这次谈话的结束时，该目标必须通过一次感知豁免检定，对抗你的法术豁免DC，否则在接下来对你或者你指定的生物变得恐慌，直到1小时或直到下述事件发生时结束：他被攻击或伤害，他目击其盟友被攻击或伤害。</p>\n<p>         若一个目标在对抗此效果的豁免检定中成功，该目标对于你试图让他变得恐慌的行为没有任何察觉。</p>\n<p>         一旦你使用此特性，直到你完成了一次短休或长休前，你都不能再次使用它。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"minute","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"低语学院等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"SoBxbPGFyZbud8kM","name":"统一言说 Universal Speech","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Shaman_SpiritLink.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         3级起，你已经获得了让任何生物都能听懂你说话的能力。使用一个动作，选择你身边60尺内一个或多个生物，你最多可以选择与你魅力调整值相等数量的生物（至少一个生物）。不管你说哪种语言，被选择的生物都能在一小时内魔法般地理解你。一旦你使用了此特性，直到你完成一次长休，或者消耗一个法术位才能再次使用它。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MOT","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"雄辩学院等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"SoROktB6wHO25o9l","name":"造物表演 Performance Of Creation","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_SelflessHealer.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>以一个动作，你可以引导造物之歌的魔力来创造一个由你选择的非魔法物品，它会在你选择的距离你10尺内的一处未被占据的空间里生成。它必须要生成在一个可以支撑它的地方&mdash;&mdash;这可以是在也体内或者一个表面上。这件物品的价值不能超过你吟游诗人等级*20gp，它必须是中型或者更小的物品。这件物品会闪烁着柔和的微光。当一个生物触碰它的时候，会听到轻微的音乐。在被创造出等同于你的熟练加值数的小时之后，这件物品会消失。例如，玩家手册中的装备章节里的物品大多数都是可以通过此方法创造的。</p>\n<p>每当你用这一特性创造出一件物品后，直到下一次长休结束前你都不能再次使用这个能力。你可以消耗一个2环或者更高级的法术位去重制这个能力的使用次数。你同时只能保持一件以此法被创造出的物品。如果在你使用这个能力创造物品时已经有一件被创造出来的物品了，那么那个旧的物品会立刻消失不见。</p>\n<p>你创造的物品都大小限制会随着你的吟游诗人等级提高而增长。6级时你可以创造出大型物品，14级时你可以创造去巨型物品。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":2,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"space"},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"@classes.bard.levels*20","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"创造学院等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"T1rm8GritjZqmyJ2","name":"剑舞学院 College of Swords（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Warrior_WeaponMastery.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>剑舞学院的诗人被称作「刃锋」，他们通过杂耍武器以取乐。刃锋表演诸如吞剑，杂耍，飞刀和模拟格斗之类的特技。尽管他们用他们的武器来娱乐，他们同时也是自身有着高度训练和熟练技巧的战士。</p>\n<p>他们武器上的才能使得许多刃锋过着双重身份的生活。一个刃锋可能使用马戏团来掩盖他们的邪恶行为，比如暗杀，抢劫和勒索。其他刃锋则打击邪恶，伸张正义，反对强权和残暴。大多数剧团乐于接受刃锋把他们娱乐的才能加入到他们的表演上去，但是很少有艺人完全相信他们。</p>\n<p>放弃了艺人生活的刃锋通常都遇到了使其不能再维持秘密活动的麻烦。盗窃被抓或者从事义务警员的刃锋对大多数剧团来说都是个太大的负担。使用他们武器的技巧和魔法。这些刃锋开始成为盗贼公会的执行者或是像个冒险者一样开辟自己的道路。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"吟游诗人等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"T9Vw58RbZCKkEouT","name":"手稳就准Steady Aim","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Rogue_BladeTwisting.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>作为一个附赠动作，你在当前回合为你的下一次攻击提供优势。你只能在你本回合还没有移动的时候使用这个附赠动作，而且在你使用这个附赠动作后，你的速度在当前回合里归0.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游荡者等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"TI7ZZ9FmrvtlVlzi","name":"守魂者","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_DivineSpirit.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从十七级开始，你可以抓住游魂的一丝生命力来治愈生命。当你60尺内可见的敌人死亡，你或者你选择的60尺内的一个生物恢复等同于死亡敌人生命骰数量的生命。你只有不处于失能状态时才可使用此特性。当你使用了此特性，你下回合开始之后才可以再次使用它。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"坟墓领域等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"TfwQk0GrG4xIfY12","name":"幻想杀手 Spell Breaker","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Frost_ManaRecharge.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>    从6级起，每次你使用1环或者更高环数的法术恢复了一名盟友的生命值，你同时可以选择作用于此生物的一个法术终止。被终止的法术等级不能高于你用来施放恢复法术所占用的法术位。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奥秘领域等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ThMexbKa7IGupvI1","name":"引导神力：鼓舞一击 Channel Divinity：Inspiring Smite","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_HolyNova.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在你以@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.qV59DzEZQ58IAzfm]{至圣斩}造成一次伤害后，你可以用附赠动作消耗一次@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.3eyfqXMTJMG9AxYH]{引导神力}，给予你周围30尺任意个你选择的生物（包括你）临时生命。临时生命＝2d8+你的圣武士等级，你可以任意分配这些生命值。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MOT","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d8 + @class.paladin.levels","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"荣耀之誓等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"TieC6BcmIWTOYzQC","name":"魔能祈唤：护符牵绊Eldritch Invocation：Bond of the Talisman","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/violet_26.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>当别人佩戴你的护身符时，只要你们存在于同一位面，你可以用一个标准动作将你传送至靠近他们的空区域。佩戴该护身符的人也能做同样的事，用他们的动作来传送到你身边。该传送能力可使用的次数等于你的熟练加值，且所有已消耗的次数会在你完成一次长休之后完全恢复。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"存在于同一位面。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"2","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"邪术师等级 12，符之魔契","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"TvM1Mjyiud1qbcVY","name":"野兽道途 Path of The Beast（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_shadow_manafeed.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>踏上野兽道途的野蛮人点燃其灵魂深处熊熊燃烧的兽性火花以激活狂暴。其内心的野兽在嗥叫中被释放，在狂怒中爆发，并改变野蛮人的形态。这些野蛮人可能体内住着一只原初精魂，又或是某个化兽者的后人。请你为自己的野性之力选择一种起源，或在下方的“野兽起源表”随机选择。</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>[[/r D4]]</th>\n<th>野兽起源</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>你的生父或生母患有兽化症，你也遗传了这方面的一些诅咒。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>你是一位大德鲁伊的后人并且继承了变形部分躯体的能力。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>一只精类的精魂赐予你变换不同野兽形态的能力。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>一只上古野兽的精魂住在你的体内，为你打开选择此道途的大门。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"野蛮人等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"UHIZXCLTWbG6nDr4","name":"灵能天赋Psionic Power","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_mage_massinvisibility.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>　　你的内在潜藏着一个心灵异能的源泉，当你以各种形式引导它时，其能量会上下起伏。这一力量被表现为你的灵能骰，它的起始大小是[[/r d6]]。你拥有等同于你熟练加值两倍数量的灵能骰，并且他们供你发挥出你拥有的多种灵能力量，这些选项在后面列出。</p>\n<p>一些你的能力会消耗它们使用的灵能骰，如能力中确切描述的一样，而且你不能在你灵能骰全部用完的时候使用要求你使用灵能骰的能力。你在完成一次长休之后恢复所有的灵能骰。此外，作为一个附赠动作，你可以恢复一个你消耗的灵能骰，但是直到你完成一次短休或者长休之前，你都无法再次这样做。</p>\n<p>每当你在这个职业中达到特定等级，你的灵能骰会增大，5级达到[[/r d8]]。11级[[/r d10]]，17级为[[/r d12]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"2","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"d(floor((1+@classes.rogue.levels)/6)*2+6)","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魂刃等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"UcTb44qcFcpYkA0I","name":"生死流转 Strength Before Death","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/000411.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>          从18级开始，你的战斗意志可以延后死亡的支配。若你受到将你生命值归零但没有当场杀死你的伤害，你可以使用你的反应以延后陷入昏迷的时机，且你可以中断当前的回合并立刻进行一个额外的回合。</p>\n<p>          当你在这个额外回合期间的拥有0点生命值，受到伤害仍然会如往常一样导致一次失败的死亡豁免，且三次死亡豁免失败仍然会杀死你。当这个额外回合结束时，若你的生命值依旧为0点，你将陷入昏迷。</p>\n<p>          一旦你使用此能力，直到你完成一次长休之前你都不能再使用它。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"武士等级 18","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"name":"增强防御","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2>增强防御</h2>\n<p><em>物品：一套盔甲或一面盾牌</span></em><br></span>　　穿着该盔甲或挥舞该盾牌的生物在</span>AC</span>上获得</span>+1</span>加值。</span><br></span>　　当你拥有</span>10</span>个奇械师等级时，该加值变成</span>+2</span>。</span><br></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Defend.png","_id":"UgvGe7Lo9kDclj7I"}
{"_id":"UyTtD6D91W6EZLQt","name":"巫咒战士 Hex Warrior","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Priest_ShadowyApparition.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<h4>在1级时，你获得了有效的战斗训练。你得到对于中甲，盾牌，和军用武器的熟练。此外，你宗主的影响也让你得以通过一把特殊武器来魔法的引导你的意志。当你结束一次长休，你都能够触摸一把你已经熟练的、非双手武器，你可以在攻击和伤害检定中，使用你的魅力调整值，以代替力量或敏捷。这个好处保留到你再次完成长休。如果你在后续获得@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.MtURbXBBvh9LdJxf]{刃之魔契}，此好处将扩展到你用这个魔契召唤的每一把契约武器上，没有武器类型的限制。</h4>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"咒剑士等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"zucCzkJArfZFbnhb","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.armorProf.value","mode":2,"value":"med"},{"key":"data.traits.armorProf.value","mode":2,"value":"shl"},{"key":"data.traits.weaponProf.value","mode":2,"value":"mar"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Priest_ShadowyApparition.png","label":"获得中甲、盾牌、军用武器熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.UyTtD6D91W6EZLQt","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"V0GUfk7uwMz5sWiM","name":"星我觉醒 Awakened Astral Self","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_ardenweald_priest.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你与星我之间的连接趋近完美，你能够释放它的全部潜能。以一个附赠动作，你可以花费5点气召唤你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.Qctmiuim4M9SfU1E]{星我之臂}、@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.vimr3VI7xsnK1ydv]{星我之容}和@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.lG7lOXsvmj7RXhkk]{星我之躯}，这种星我觉醒状态持续10分钟，如果你失能或死亡，这种觉醒状态会提前结束。</p>\n<p>当你处于星我觉醒时，你将获得如下增益：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>灵魂盔甲</strong>。你的AC获得+2加值。</li>\n<li><strong>星之连击</strong>。当你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.WKQXfXbifuoCk1V1]{额外攻击}特性进行两次攻击时，可以改为三次攻击，所有的攻击必须都是星我之臂进行的。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":"5 点气。"},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"星我宗等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"uccizkzfb6kIK7L1","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.ac.bonus","mode":2,"value":"2"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":600},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_ardenweald_priest.jpg","label":"获得 2 AC","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.V0GUfk7uwMz5sWiM","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"V5YioLyAmcWLtZqm","name":"物品注法 Infuse Item","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Shaman_ImprovedStormstrike.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>     在第2级，你获得为普通物品注入魔法的能力。使用此特性创造的魔法物品是永久性魔法物品的原型。</p>\n<h3><strong>已知注法</strong></h3>\n<p>     当你获得这个特性时，从职业描述末尾的“@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.IrZuNJvar506SCUa]{奇械师注法}”列表中选择选择四个奇械师注法习得。当你提升奇械师等级时，还能够根据“@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-table.2A3nWtToOKL8Asu3]{奇械师职业表}”习得更多注法。</p>\n<p>     当你提升一个奇械师等级时，你能够习得一个新的奇械师注法来来替换一个原有的已知注法。</p>\n<h3><strong>为物品进行注法</strong></h3>\n<p>     每当你完成一个长休后，你可以触摸一个非魔法的物体，使用奇械师注法来把它变成一个魔法物品。注法只能作用于注法描述中写明的指定类型物品。如果该物品需要同调，你可以在为物品进行注法的那一刻同调到它，或者你可以放弃同调，以便其他人能够同调到该物品。如果你决定以后与这个物品进行同调，你必须进行通常的同调程序（参见《地下城主指南》第136页中的“同调”）。</p>\n<p>     你的注法持续时间无限，但当你死亡时，注法会在你智力调整值的天数后消失（至少1天）。如果你将某个注法从已知中替换掉，该注法的效果也将消失。</p>\n<p>     你能在一次长休后为复数物品进行注法；注法物品的最大数量请参见“@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-table.2A3nWtToOKL8Asu3]{奇械师职业表}”。你必须触摸每一个物体，且一种注法在同一时间内只能存在于一个物品上。如果你试图超过你的最大注法量，则最旧的注法立即结束，然后新的注法适用。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>奇械师等级</th>\n<th>已知注法</th>\n<th>注法物品数量上限</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>14</td>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>18</td>\n<td>12</td>\n<td>6</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奇械师等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effec