{"_id":"VBR3UzO0EwZ0pdHk","name":"神圣防御 Glorious Defense","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpcloud3steamusercontentcomugc842585423179194441F2AE2E830612ECF2FF3E7587BAA12C7B08E55602.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你可以防卫突然袭击。当一次攻击检定命中你或10尺内另一个你可见的生物时，你可以用反应来获得额外AC对抗该次攻击，这可能会导致它打失。加值等于你的魅力调整值(最小值1)。如果该次攻击失败，作为此反应的一部分，如果攻击者在你的触及内，你可以对攻击者进行一次武器攻击。</p>\n<p>         你能使用的次数等于魅力调整值（至少有一次），长休刷新。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MOT","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"max(@abilities.cha.mod,1)","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"荣耀之誓等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"VJHMkz9DNOnuIsQ8","name":"复原药剂 Restorative Reagents","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Mage_ConjureWater11.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从第9级起，你可以在你的一些作品中加入复原药剂：每当一个生物饮用一剂你制造的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.sGggioh8w6WTNUbD]{实验性灵药}时，该生物获得[[/r 2d6]]+你智力调整值的临时生命值。（至少1点临时生命点）。</p>\n<p>         此外，只要你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.EFBBAE8B63126638]{炼金工具}作为法器，就可以在不花费法术位的情况下施展@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.I1C2EQxwynPd7dOC]{次级复原术}。你能够这么做的次数等于你的智力调整值（最少1次），在你完成一次长休后，将恢复所有可用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"max(@abilities.int.mod,1)","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d6+@abilities.int.mod","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"炼金师等级 9","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"VQyAB5s30uowEgIU","name":"回音骑士 Echo Knight(EGtW)","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/1Ability_Rogue_CutToTheChase%20-%20.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>          Kryn王朝的一种神秘并且令人忌惮的前线斗士，回音骑士掌握并运用dunamis的技艺，召唤未能成为现实的众多时间线里的消逝之影，来在协助他们战斗。在自身力量的回音的围绕下，他们冲锋陷阵姿态宛如凶猛来袭的阴影集群。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EGtW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Vlx0VdQ9V61wHX9I","name":"先祖护卫 Ancestral Protectors","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Warrior_SwordandBoard.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从你在3级时选择此道途开始，精魂战士会在你@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.gLNFWGL05O0FUNTD]{狂暴}时出现。当你处于狂暴状态，你的回合内你攻击命中的第一个生物会成为战士的目标。直到你的下一个回合开始，目标对你以外的目标的攻击骰取劣势，若目标在一次攻击中击中了除你以外的生物，该生物对那次攻击有伤害抗性。若你的狂暴结束，此效果也随之提前结束。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"先祖守卫等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"VtoHZM9o8Oifvh4m","name":"快手投掷 Quick Toss","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/mech_6.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>以一个附赠动作，你能消耗一枚卓越骰一件具有投掷属性的武器进行一次远程攻击。在进行此攻击时，你能拔出一把投掷武器作为攻击的一部分。如果此次攻击命中，你能将消耗的卓越骰加入此次攻击的伤害检定中。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战斗大师等级 3，卓越技巧，战技专家","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"VyexnnQhqlP2YcrA","name":"骑兵 Cavalier","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_SealOfProtection.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这种泛型擅长乘骑作战。他们通常出身于贵族，成长在宫廷，骑兵往往在家族中领导骑兵队冲锋陷阵或在国家庆典中担任仪仗或守卫。他们学习如何在冲锋时保护他人不受伤害，经常以保护者的身份服务于他们的长官或者弱者。他们被强迫去惩奸除恶或取得荣耀，他们中的一些战士会为了在冒险中提升自己而离开了他们的安逸生活。</p>\n<p><strong>额外熟练：</strong></p>\n<p>当你在3级选择这个泛型时，你选择一下技能中的一个并获得其熟练：驯兽、历史、洞察、表演、游说。或者，你学会一门你选择的语言。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"W2lVMW9feaADwdH8","name":"雅臣 Elegant Courtier","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_Faction_LoreWalkers.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从7级开始，你的修养和对细节的专注让你得以在社交场合崭露头角。每当你进行一次魅力（说服）检定时，你将在该检定中获得等同于你感知调整值的加值。</p>\n<p>         你的自我控制能力同时也让你获得了感知豁免的熟练。若你已经拥有此熟练，则你可以改为获得智力豁免或魅力豁免的熟练（由你选择）。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"武士等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"MNbkZydsSbGSG0PS","changes":[{"key":"data.abilities.wis.proficient","mode":4,"value":"1"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_Faction_LoreWalkers.png","label":"获得感知熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.W2lVMW9feaADwdH8","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"W8IgV3zZSWduIjd0","name":"额外游侠法术 Additional Ranger Spells","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/arrow_04.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>下列法术是对玩家手册中的游侠法术列表的补充该表格以法术等级而非角色等级排序。除非该法术标有一个星号(说明该法术位于TCE第三章)，否则其他法术都来自玩家手册。萨娜珊的万事指南中提供了更多的法术。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>法术环位</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.NZ4JOGBMJzeCKT5O]{纠缠术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.73yB6CHxGk3Np5ME]{炽焰斩}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.hAL0Dxp9w7gvkfZm]{援助术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.SCmGEYM6V880rfaW]{强化属性}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.cGIrpk6h4Rf8QKV6]{造风术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.14a3v5NF5h5Lgm9J]{魔化武器}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.exBreA0aIOBCV2hi]{野兽召唤术*}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.srjt2KPpCAtQGe7W]{元素武器}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.pJ6hE8Vab5Ypuqm4]{融身入石}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.TkFsGmyAeHknESJ4]{回生术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.p12lhL5QyiAvgpTx]{精类召唤术*}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.xaSXewdCx3aWtczk]{支配野兽}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.9Yhs9yVaMLPnDlSC]{元素召唤术*}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.7dqplcsKNYQgRh2S]{高等复原术}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游侠等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"per