{"_id":"WYwc4UQBzV8IhvR6","name":"引导神力:控制亡灵 Control Undead","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Frost_FrostArmor.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         作为一个动作项，该圣骑士指定其身边 30尺内一个他能看见的不死生物。该目标必须进行一次感知豁免。豁免失败时，该目标必须在随后的 24小时里遵从该圣武士的命令，或者直至该圣武士在此使用该@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.3eyfqXMTJMG9AxYH]{引导神力}选项为止。挑战等级等于或高于该圣武士等级的不死生物免疫该效应。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":24,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"破誓者等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"WcnprPZgGMC8916q","name":"暴风魔法 Tempestuous Magic","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_StormReach.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从1级起，你与风元素魔法紧密联系起来。每当你在你自己的行动轮内施展一个并非戏法的法术时，你可以用附赠动作导致旋转的风元素飙风围绕着你。此时你可以飞行10尺，而不引起借机攻击。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"狂怒风暴等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"WmhbakjejSlngoD3","name":"意志壁垒 Bulwark","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_Win_Gilneas.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从15级起，你可以延展你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.H8gQ1Lf0OpePA3JP]{不屈}能力作用于你的盟友。每当你决定用不屈重投智力，感知或者魅力豁免并且你未处于失能状态，你可以选择一个在你60尺距离内对同样的效果豁免失败的盟友。如果他能看见你或者听见你的声音，他可以重投豁免骰。他必须采用新的结果。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"紫龙骑士等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"WrdYtYe9gaMhdkvq","name":"启悟传播 Infectious Inspiration","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/002615.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         14级起，当你成功地激励了某人，你的雄辩之力便可以传播到他人的身上。当你身边60尺内的一个生物将你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.FSr7TfaoWRPpUtkD]{诗人激励}骰加到其属性检定、攻击检定或豁免检定并且该掷骰成功时，你可以用你的反应去激励在你身边60尺内能听到你声音的一个其他生物（不能指定你自身），给予该生物一个诗人激励而不需要消耗你任何的诗人激励。</p>\n<p>         你能够使用该特性的次数等于你的魅力调整值（最低一次）。完成一次长休后，你将重获所有消耗掉的诗人激励次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MOT","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"max(@abilities.cha.mod,1)","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"雄辩学院等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"WsBRhWXSAk452GUy","name":"奥术偏斜 Arcane Deflection","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Shaman_AstralShift.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在2级时，你学会了编织魔法以更强韧的面对伤害。当你被一次攻击击中，或未通过一次豁免时，你可以使用你的反应来在对抗那次攻击的AC上获得+2加值，或在那次豁免检定中得到+4加值。</p>\n<p>当你使用此特性时，你不能施展戏法之外的法术，直到你下个回合结束。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战争法师等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"X9xPihIslNck5bCk","name":"夙敌 Favored Foe","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_SniperTraining.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<p>替换@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.FxSEAmMXMIcv4iWm]{宿敌}并能够对@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.V7VI6TXZ7LJzP8Fd]{屠灭众敌}起效。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>当你以一次攻击掷骰命中一个生物时，你可以呼唤你与自然的神秘羁连以将目标标记为你的夙敌，持续一分钟或直到你失去专注(如同你在专注一道法术)。</p>\n<p>你在你的回合内第一次命中你的夙敌并对其造成伤害，包括你标记它的时候，你可以造成额外的[[/r 1d4]]点伤害。你可以使用同等于你的熟练加值次该特性来标记你的夙敌，你在完成一次长休后恢复所有已使用的次数。这个特性的额外伤害在你达到特定等级时会增加：6级时[[/r 1d6]]，14级时[[/r 1d8]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"2","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["d(floor((2+@classes.ranger.levels)/8)*2+6)",""]],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"游侠等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"XDsHOwUjo6dJSK4b","name":"战斗风格：卓越技巧","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/weapon_29.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>        </strong>你从@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.Rv7ONO9srHsLqFuV]{战斗大师武术范型}的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.CRu7K83gIxlVL5sX]{战技}列表中习得一项战技。如果该战技需要豁免，则豁免DC为8+你的熟练加值+你的力量或敏捷调整值（由你选择）。</p>\n<p><strong>        </strong>你获得一个[[/r d6]]的卓越骰（此卓越骰与任何你能够其他方式获得的卓越骰累计）。此卓越骰可用于启动你的战技。卓越骰一经使用即消耗，并在完成一次短休或长休后恢复。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr","type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"战士等级 1，勇士等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"XLAACVfQbbmNrhQk","name":"命定毁伤 Inescapable Destruction","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_shadow_shadowfury.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         第6级起，该牧师引导负能量的能力更为有效。该角色的牧师法术与@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.BAYFDeCiaMYHQZRw]{引导神力}选项所造成的黯蚀伤害将无视对黯蚀伤害抗性。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"死亡领域等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"XjFLK1XZERDlvQua","name":"高爆炮台 Explosive Cannon","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Vehicle_SiegeEngineCannon.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从第9级起，你制造的每一门@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.yaiCR2TIRre4E5Yi]{奥能炮台}都将拥有更大的破坏力：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>所有炮台的伤害增加[[/r 1d8]]。</li>\n<li>如果你距离炮台不到60尺，你能以一个动作命令你的炮台自爆。这么做会摧毁炮台，并迫使每一个离它20尺以内的生物对你的法术豁免dc进行一次敏捷豁免检定，若豁免失败，将受到[[/r 3d8]]力场伤害，成功的豁免检定将使伤害减半。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":20,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"spec"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["3d8","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魔炮师等级 9","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Xr8uiPr41sHR1Uwt","name":"放逐箭 Banishing Arrow","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_AimedShot.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你尝试用你的防护魔法来暂时放逐你的目标到一片属于精灵沃野的无害区域。被这发箭击中的角色必须通过一个魅力豁免或者被放逐。当被这种方式放逐时，目标速度降为0，变为失能。在他的回合结束时，目标在他被放逐前的位置出现。如果该位置被占据，则他在最近的未被占据空间出现。</p>\n<p>         当你的战士等级到18级时，目标被箭击中时还会受到[[/r 2d6]]的力场伤害。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"cha","dc":null,"scaling":"int"},"requirements":"魔射手等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"XuddfP5pfKqJL4NP","name":"星图 Star Map","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003144.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>作为你天文学研究的一部分，你创造了一个星图。它是一个微型物体，可以作为你德鲁伊法术的法器。你通过在星图列表上掷骰或选择一个来确定它的形态。</p>\n<p>当你持握这件星图时，你获得这些好处：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你已知@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.QiU2ZZ09lBye0Iy4]{神导术}戏法</li>\n<li>你获得准备@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.PHYXwNkXSdJjDCSD]{曳光弹}。它对你来说视作德鲁伊法术，且不计入你的每日准备法术上限。</li>\n<li>你可以施放曳光弹而无需消耗法术位。你可以这样做的次数等同于你的熟练加值，且在你完成一次长休后会恢复所有已消耗使用次数。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果你丢失了星图，你可以举行一场为时一小时的仪式来使用魔法创造一个替代品。这一仪式可以在一场短休或长休时举行，并会摧毁先前的星图。</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>[[/r D6]]</th>\n<th>星图样式</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>一幅布满星座图列的卷轴。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>一块钻有细孔的石板</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>一张斑点枭熊皮，标有凸痕记号</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>一套黑檀木封皮地图集</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>一块遇光会投射出星辰轨迹的水晶</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>描绘星座排列的玻璃圆盘</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"d6","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"星辰结社等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"XvBRljAgLsoFFPF4","name":"强效治疗 Empowered Healing","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/SPELL_HOLY_PERSECUTION.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         6级起，你可以通过神圣之力增幅治疗法术。当你或你的盟友在你周围5尺内掷骰子来决定法术恢复生命值的时候，只要你没有失能 incapacitated，你便可以花费1个术法点，重扔其中任意数量的骰子。每轮只能使用一次该能力。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":1,"condition":"你或盟友在你周围5尺内掷骰决定法术恢复hp，你未失能；1术法点。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"神圣之魂等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"XvZtgLjExeMcMxrd","name":"孢子光晕 Halo of Spores","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_ElementalShields.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从2级起，你被无形的坏死的孢子包围着，直到你把他们释放到附近的生物上。当一个生物进入你的10尺内时，或在其中开始其回合时，你可以使用反应来激发孢子光晕特性。造成[[/r 1d4]]点暗蚀伤害，除非其通过一个等同于你法术DC的体质豁免。此伤害在6级时提高到[[/r 1d6]]，在10级时提高到[[/r 1d8]]，在14级时提高到[[/r 1d10]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GGR","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":10,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d(min((floor(@classes.druid.levels/4)*2+4),10))","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"孢子结社等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"YMVLurWdUfCApbPa","name":"卓越防守 Supernatural Defense","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Rogue_CheatDeath.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         7级时，对于你的猎物对你的身体和精神的攻击，你拥有额外韧性。无论何时你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.zJRRsdKNnidyjqQD]{狩猎开始}特性所指定的目标强迫你进行一次豁免检定，或每当你进行一次属性检定以尝试脱离该目标的擒抱，骰[[/r 1d6]]并将其加入你的掷骰结果中。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d6","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"怪物杀手等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"YMjgmId32dyhNhY3","name":"繁星形态 Starry Form","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_druid_swarm.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>作为一个附赠动作，你可以消耗一次@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.pORTgCToV9NLPWo1]{荒野形态}使用次数以呈现一个繁星形态，而不是变化为野兽形态。</p>\n<p>当处于繁星形态时，你保留你的游戏数据，但你的身体变得明亮；你的关节星光熠熠并有如星图一般由亮线连接。这一形态散发出 10 尺范围明亮光照以及其外 10 尺范围昏暗光照。这一形态持续 10 分钟。如果你解除它（无需动作），失能，死亡，或再次使用此特性，它就会提前结束。</p>\n<p>每当你化身繁星形态，选择以下哪个星座在你身上闪耀；你的选择为你在形态中获得特定好处：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.qCQtq2qCdWT5wduu]{圣杯座 Chalice}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.3c678QuDLdblTLXm]{射手座 Archer}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.aiNtDThsxYEkpNr9]{巨龙座 Dragon}</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":2,"max":2,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"星辰结社等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"YW2NTcJkg9hHYpCy","name":"收割者 Reaper","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_revendreth_rogue.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         第1级时，该牧师可以从任意法术列表中选择学习一个死灵戏法。该牧师施展一个通常指定一个生物为目标的死灵戏法时，则该法术现在可以指定施法距离内两个相互之间距离不超过5尺的生物。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"死亡领域等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"YZgLwcsl9vy77A3P","name":"额外戏法 Bonus Cantrips","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_Chastise.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在1级时，你学会了@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.rW5ZoeX4jjZw4hBO]{光亮术}和@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.yu8LatUOZ08ORwSU]{圣火术}两个戏法。它们对你而言是邪术士戏法，但并不计入到你的邪术士可知戏法总数中。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"天界宗主等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"YavkIboZpQRIX1nC","name":"秩序领域 Order Domain（GGR）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_BlindingLight.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         秩序领域代表着纪律，以及对一个社会或制度的忠诚和对其统治法律的严格服从。在拉尼卡，这个领域被俄佐立参议会和欧佐夫集团的牧师所青睐，前者用它维持和执行法律，而后者则利用法律与秩序牟取私利。在别的世界中，掌管这领域的神包括班恩Bane，提尔Tyr，马哲理Majere，厄拉西斯Erathis，佛尔图斯Pholtus，维婕斯Wee Jas，奥林Aureon，马格鲁比耶Maglubiyet，努阿达Nuada，雅典娜Athena，阿努比斯Anubis，凡塞提Forseti以及阿斯摩蒂尔斯Asmodeus。</p>\n<p>         理想中的秩序便是对法律的服从高于一切，而不是对某个人，情感的暂时影响或是民治的服从。与其关心结果是否公正合理，秩序牧师们通常会关心于过程。遵循法律与法令至关重要，尤其是当其对这些牧师和他们侍奉的公会或神有益的时候。</p>\n<p>         法律建立阶级。凡是被法律选中去领导的，都必须被服从。而服从命令的人必须尽力而为。以这种方式，法律创造了错综复杂的责任之网并允许社会在混沌的多重宇宙之中塑造安全与秩序。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>牧师等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>1st</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Ja6HpsLeGA9MQ0Rm]{命令术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.eatsvLyUqyzEFzCv]{英雄气概}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>3rd</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.syHHJlRPS4rVwCQA]{人类定身术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.T4zFq0zTHnzZeO9t]{诚实之域}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>5th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.6PTF3SN0jxkEqv6W]{群体治愈真言}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.2AgiR8EQ7IglGbci]{缓慢术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>7th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.RpBbOYseLZCFXaFY]{强迫术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Fw3U8sQwWSPVoisW]{物件定位术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>9th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.7tphgwQJI7dKIyfE]{通神术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.JudswpO6E5GBlyfQ]{支配人类}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>附赠熟练项Bonus Proficiencies</strong></p>\n<p>         当你在1级选择此领域时，你获得重甲的熟练项。你还获得由你选择的威吓或游说的熟练项。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GGR","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"牧师等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"dXYczXl9HTZsmu7o","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.armorProf.value","mode":2,"value":"hvy"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_BlindingLight.png","label":"获得重甲熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.YavkIboZpQRIX1nC","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Ywzw8xNcbYKybJ5w","name":"重力魔法 Graviturgy Magic（EGtW）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003123.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         理解并掌控着将物体的物质聚合或分离的力量，重力奥术传承的学生们通过学习来更进一步掌控扭曲并操纵重力的狂暴能量来增益自己，或是为他们的敌人带来恐怖的伤害。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EGtW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"法师等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"YzNkv97GG9DyVg7F","name":"扭曲爆裂 Warping Implosion","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_priest_void-blast.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>18级起，你能够解放你异质的力量，从而制造扭曲空间的异常现象。以一个动作，你可以传送到120尺内你可见的一个未被占据的位置，然后你消失位置30尺内的生物必须进行一次力量豁免，失败受[[/r 3d10]]力场伤害并被立即拉向你原本的位置或最近的一个未被占据的位置，成功半伤且不受拉扯。</p>\n<p>一旦你使用了此能力，你在完成一次长休之前必须消耗5术法点以再次使用此能力。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":120,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["3d10","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"str","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"畸变心智等级 18","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Z3Jkvy9YLoHmo88I","name":"长眠触 Touch of The Long Death","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Monk_TouchofDeath.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从17级起，你可以将死亡的能量传入生物的体内。</p>\n<p>        以一个动作，你触碰一个5尺内的生物，同时花费1到10点气。目标必须进行一次体质豁免，若失败将受到每点被耗费的气[[/r 2d10]]的黯蚀伤害。成功通过豁免可以使这个伤害降低到一半。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"1 到 10 点气。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"touch","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"con","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d10","necrotic"]],"versatile":"2d10"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"wis"},"requirements":"永亡宗等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Z6odF8yvJWuJHaw3","name":"永恒生命 Indestructible Life","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_deathwing_bloodcorruption_earth.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从14级起，你从你的宗主处窥探到一些有关于永恒的奥秘。在你的回合，你可以使用一个附赠动作恢复[[/r 1d8]]+邪术士等级的生命值。此外，如果你在使用这个能力的同时把自己一部分被切断的躯体放置在断口处，那部分伤口将会愈合。<br />        一旦你使用了这个能力，直到一次长/短休之前你不能再次使用。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+@classes.warlock.levels","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"不朽者等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Z8Rs95GtdznfMCrf","name":"重整姿态 Rallying Cry","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_BG_KillFlagCarriers_grabFlag_CapIt.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从3级起，你学会了如何激励你的盟友来对抗伤害。当你使用你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.AQ0X21tf5cmjRmGT]{回气}能力，你可以选择在你60尺范围内最多3个盟友，他们每个人都恢复等同于你的战士等级的生命值。他们必须要能看到或者听到你的声音才能获得这个好处。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":"使用回气。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":3,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["@classes.fighter.levels","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"紫龙骑士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZEEnUo1rdVKhwi4r","name":"星辰结社 Circle of Stars（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_unused2.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>星辰结社历史悠久，其德鲁伊可驱使星光的能量。这些德鲁伊自远古时期便开始记载星象并探索星座中隐藏的秘密。通过揭示并理解群星之奥妙，属于星辰结社的德鲁伊们渴望驾驭宇宙之力。</p>\n<p>此结社的诸多德鲁伊对群星与其对世界的影响保留有详细记载，其中一些则被记载并保存于作为深奥知识的宝库的巨型石制场地中。这些知识保存处形态多样，从巨石阵，金字塔，岩刻再到地下神殿——乃至于任何足以在一场大灾变中幸存下来并保护这此结社的珍贵知识的坚固结构。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"德鲁伊等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZMsWAAnCbFFgih3H","name":"巨人之力  Giant’s Might","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Warrior_TitansGrip.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从3级起，你已经学会了如何使用巨人之力灌注自身。你可以使用一个附赠动作，魔法性地获得以下能力，持续一分钟。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>如果你的体型小于大型，你和你所穿戴的所有物品一起变为大型。如果你缺少变为大型的空间，则你的体型无法发生变化。</li>\n<li>你在力量检定和力量豁免检定上获得优势。</li>\n<li>你的每回合内一次，你的武器攻击或徒手打击可以在击中后对目标造成额外[[/r 1d6]]的伤害。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>该特性的可使用次数等于你的熟练加值，且你可以在完成一次长休之后恢复所有已使用的次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"2","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d6","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"符文骑士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZRXJv8SMKCUK53Xu","name":"哨卫灵光 Aura Of The Sentinel","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Paladin_Clarityofpurpose.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>7级起，若你未失能，你散发出一道令人保持警觉的灵光。当你和你10尺内由你选择的生物进行一次先攻检定时，获得等同于你熟练加值的加值。</p>\n<p>18级起，灵光的范围增长至30尺。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"perm"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"守望之誓等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Zm7oGfXl3kxVN3EZ","name":"终焉之力 Strength of the Grave","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpcloud3steamusercontentcomugc842585341025537431C8D829D636A4FF883DA7B75CB91A77B63ECEA582.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>1级起，存在于生和死的朦胧状态中使得你难以被击败。当生命值被降至0点时，你可以通过一个DC=该次所受伤害+5的魅力豁免。若豁免成功，作为代替你的生命值被降至1点。若该次伤害为光耀或重击时你不可使用此能力。</p>\n<p>         当你通过豁免后直到下一次长休前不能再使用此能力。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"幽影魔法等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Zr1KSmDIoSq0BPSe","name":"引导神力：奥秘阻绝 Channel Divinity: Arcane Abjuration","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Arcane_ArcaneResilience.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从2级起，你可以使用你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.WPevnsjK8Cjd9Fcl]{引导神力}来抵御外世界生物。</p>\n<p>以一个动作，你可以展示你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.TJi1q6Bm8IGoJJVL]{圣徽}，同时你选择一个30尺内能看见或者听见你声音的天界，元素，精类或者邪魔类生物进行一次感知豁免。如果他未通过，他在1分钟之内被驱散直到他受到任何伤害。</p>\n<p>        一个被驱散的生物必须使用他的回合尽力远离你，并且无法主动靠近你30尺以内。同时他们无法使用反应。在他们行动中，只能使用疾走或者从任何妨碍他们移动的效果中挣脱出来。如果没有任何地方移动，该生物使用闪避动作。</p>\n<p>        从5级起，如果一个挑战等级小于等于表内数值且不是这个位面原住民的生物在对抗你的奥秘阻绝能力时豁免失败，他将在1分钟之内被放逐（如同@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.lopw7wVkPoE7gbNu]{放逐术}，但不需要专注）。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>牧师等级</th>\n<th>被放逐的生物CR</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>1/2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8th</td>\n<td>1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11th</td>\n<td>2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>14th</td>\n<td>3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17th</td>\n<td>4</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"wis","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奥秘领域等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZyhSlbXVK3UETRBb","name":"战斗风格：德鲁伊教战士","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/green_10.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你学会两个来自@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.spell-table.owJ94hrYlzU4BsBd]{德鲁伊法术列表}的你自选的戏法。它们对你视作游侠法术，感知是你施展他们的施法关键属性。当你升级时，你可以将其中一个戏法替换为德鲁伊法术列表中的另一个戏法。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":"","long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"游侠等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"a1JCKCXb7pCgs9wT","name":"魔能祈唤：链主赋能Eldritch Invocation：Investment of the Chain Master","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/red_06.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你使用获得魔宠时，你将一定程度的魔能力量灌注给被召唤的魔宠，给予这个生物以下的能力：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>该魔宠获得40尺飞行速度或游泳速度（由你选择）。</li>\n<li>你可以使用一个附赠动作指挥你的魔宠进行一次攻击动作。</li>\n<li>该魔宠的武器攻击被认为是魔法武器攻击，旨在克服对于非魔法攻击的免疫和抗性。</li>\n<li>如果该魔宠强迫一个生物进行豁免检定，它使用你的法术豁免DC。</li>\n<li>当你的魔宠受到伤害时，你可以使用你的反应动作给予它对于该伤害的抗性。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"邪术师等级 2，链之魔契","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"a5aIsWVx11LjqlS4","name":"轻蔑呵斥 Scornful Rebuke","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_Polymorph.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从15级起，那些胆敢击中你的人，将在心灵上因为无礼而受到惩罚。当一个生物以一次攻击击中你时，若你并未失能，该生物受到等于你魅力调整值（最小为1）的心灵伤害。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["max(@abilities.cha.mod,1)","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"征服之誓等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"aI6Gc7MU4uZ621kr","name":"守护之魂 Protective Spirit","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_HolyGuidance.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从15级起，神圣的实体在战斗中为你治疗伤口。若你在战斗中结束你的回合时，剩余的生命值少于一半，且你未处于失能状态，则你恢复等于[[/r 1d6]]+你圣武士等级一半的生命值。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d6+floor(@class.paladin.levels/2)","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"救赎之誓等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"aIY9BRADsHisG9TJ","name":"愤怒风暴 Storm of Fury","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_ElementalPrecision_2.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你在3级选择此道途时，当处于狂暴时，你散发出一个10英尺半径的灵光，但无法穿透全掩护。你的灵光效果拥有一个由你进入狂暴时所激活的效果，你在每个自己的回合也可以用一个附赠动作来激活该效果。从下述选项中选择一个：沙漠，海洋，或冻原，此灵光的效果基于你选择的环境类型。每当你在此职业中获得级别提升时，你可以改变所选环境。如果你的光环效果需要进行豁免，DC等于8+你的熟练加值+你的体质调整值。</p>\n<p><strong>沙漠desert</strong>：当这个效果被激活时，你的灵光中所有其他生物都会受到2点火焰伤害。当你在这个职业达到一定等级时，伤害增加——在5级时增加到3，10级时增加到4，15级时增加到5，20级时增加到6。</p>\n<p><strong>海洋sea</strong>：当这个效果被激活时，你可以选择一个处于灵光中且你能看到的其他生物。目标必须通过一个敏捷豁免，否则受到[[/r 1d6]]闪电伤害，豁免成功则伤害减半。当你在这个职业达到一定等级时，伤害增加——10级增加到[[/r 2d6]]，15级时[[/r 3d6]]，和20级时[[/r 4d6]]。</p>\n<p><strong>冻原tundra</strong>：当这个效果被激活时，灵光中每个你选择的生物获得2点临时生命值。当你在这个职业达到一定等级时，临时生命值增加——在5级时增加到3，10级时增加到4，15级时增加到5，20级时增加到6。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"风暴先驱等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"aJhiEEOneWfQG6Ge","name":"擒握触手 Grasping Tentacles","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_priest_voidtendrils.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你获得法术@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.JMAmXdzvxTU27pP2]{艾伐黑触手}。它对你来说是一个邪术师法术，但是它并不算作你已知的法术数量。你可以在不消耗法术位的情况下使用该法术一次，且该能力于你完成一次长休后恢复。</p>\n<p>每当你使用这个法术，祂的魔力鼓舞着你，并且赐予你和你邪术师等级一致的临时生命值。此外，对你的伤害并不会破坏你对于该法术的专注。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["@classes.warlock.levels","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"深海意志等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"aLEYUnmaQ9DDdcv4","name":"隐匿通途 Hidden Paths","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_FarSight.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>          10级起，你可以使用那些被隐藏起来的、无法预测的魔法道路，像妖精一样在眨眼之间穿越空间。在你的回合，你可以以一个附赠动作传送到60尺内一处未被占据的可见区域。或者，你也可以用你的动作来接触一个自愿生物将它传送至30尺内一处未被占据的你可见的空间。</p>\n<p>          你可以使用这个能力的次数等同于你的感知调整值（至少1次），当你结束一次长休之后，你恢复所有使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"max(@abilities.wis.mod,1)","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"梦境之环等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"aZJhapP7lW0esvNh","name":"法力变换Sorcerous Versatility","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_warlock_MortalCoil.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>　　每当你通过提升术士等级获得属性值提升时，你可以进行以下一种行为，代表着你内在的法力流向了新的途径：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>用另一个你能够选择的超魔法选项替换你当前的一个超魔法选项。</li>\n<li>用另一个你能够从术士法术列表中选择的戏法替换你当前已知的一个术士戏法。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"术士等级 5","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"aiNtDThsxYEkpNr9","name":"巨龙座 Dragon","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/inv_celestialserpentmount.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>一条智慧而又古老的巨龙形态的星座于你身上浮现。当你进行一次智力或感知检定，或是进行一次体质豁免来维持专注时，你可以将[[/r d20]]中9或以下的骰值视为10。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"星辰结社等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"atBpuvOh93dgBvlf","name":"符文主宰 Runic Juggernaut","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_demonhunter_sigilblue.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从18级起，你学会增强你对于符文力量的转换。因此，你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.ZMsWAAnCbFFgih3H]{巨人之力}特性造成的额外伤害提高至[[/r 1d10]]。此外，当你使用该特性时，你的体型变为巨型，且当你保持该尺寸时，你的触及提高5尺。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d10","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"符文骑士等级 18","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"b7YOoleApdPyVYfG","name":"振奋魔法 Bolstering Magic","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_HolyGuidance.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以控制你的狂野魔法并用于振奋自己或者一个同伴。以一个动作，你触碰一个生物（也可以是你自己）并且为该生物提供以下增益中你所选择的一种：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>持续10分钟，该生物在掷攻击骰或者属性检定时可以额外掷一个[[/r d3]]的骰子，将其加到所扔的[[/r d20]]中。</li>\n<li>掷一个[[/r d3]]骰子。这个生物将恢复一个法术位，其环数必须小于等于所掷出骰子的结果（由这个生物决定）。当一个生物享受了这一增益后，直到下一次长休结束前都不能再次从此获益。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>你每天可以使用该能力的次数等于你的熟练加值。每完成一次长休之后你补充齐所有已消耗的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":3,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"d3","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"狂野魔法道途等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"b8wxFUmXnMXyC6TK","name":"紫龙骑士 Purple Dragon Knight（SCAG）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_BG_KillXEnemies_GeneralsRoom.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<h3><strong>限制：限定骑士</strong></h3>\n<p>紫龙骑士是一个特殊的、与科米尔地区的骑士绑定的范型。</p>\n<p><strong>爵位</strong> 如果你想把它用在其他的战役模组或者是除了紫龙骑士团以外的军阀模型中，把爵位当做是这些范型的通用限制。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>        紫龙骑士是来自科米尔王国的战士。他们承诺守护王国的传承，对抗王国领土内的邪恶。他们的任务是作为漫游骑士巡游祖国的土地，他们依靠判断力、英勇无畏、对骑士精神的忠贞来指引他们击败邪恶势力。</p>\n<p>        一名紫龙骑士通过在战斗中的英勇表现激发其他人的战力。在一个小村庄内仅有一名骑士也足以让一些兽人们和土匪们不随便打这个村子的主意。一名孤独的骑士是一名技艺娴熟的战士，但是如果一名骑士领导着一队盟友，即使是装备最差的民兵也会转变成一个激昂的战斗团队。</p>\n<p>        紫龙骑士们用行动而非言语证明自己。他们永远作为先头部队冲锋在队伍的最前方，用他们无畏的战斗唤醒友军的勇气和信念，正如他们自己所一直拥有的那样。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bCzTP0sFVSM7nsNl","name":"替换武术Martial Versatility","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/blue_23.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你的职业等级抵达能让你获得属性值提示职业特性时，你能进行以下一项改变。这种变化代表着你改变了武术训练和练习的重点</p>\n<ul>\n<li>用一个本职业可用的战斗风格替换原有的一个战斗风格。</li>\n<li>如果你通过@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.Rv7ONO9srHsLqFuV]{战斗大师范型}掌握了战技，你可以将你的一个已知战技替换为一个不同的战技。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战士、游侠等级 4","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bDYWBvMmi2yL8YEa","name":"灵界漫步 Ethereal Step","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/000111.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在7级时，你学会如何进入灵界位面。以一个附赠动作，你能够以这个特性不消耗法术位施放@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.2dKpsNn8QZWECFtd]{同游灵界 Etherealness}，但是这个法术在当前回合结束时结束，你使用该特性后，你无法再次使用直到你进行完一次短休或长休。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"边界行者等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bEnlLdzvGIIswywA","name":"剑咏者 Bladesinging（SCAG）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/INV_Weapon_Shortblade_99.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<h3>限制：限定精灵</h3>\n<p>只有精灵与半精灵可以选择剑咏者奥术传承。在费伦世界，精灵严密保管着剑歌之术的奥秘。<br />你的DM可以调整这一限制，使之更符合战役。这一限制反映着被遗忘的国度中剑咏者的故事，不过这也许不适合你DM的设定，或者他那个版本的国度。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>剑咏者一开始是作为一个剑术和魔法相结合的艺术，一把剑，更具体来说长剑是剑咏者的基础。然而经过一代又一代的学习与发展，各种各样的基于近战武器发展出的剑歌风格出现了。这些不同风格的知识在各种不同的小学校中由导师一代一代传承给学徒们。即使最新创造出的风格也有着上百年的历史，但是由于精灵们拥有着漫长的生命，最初的创造者仍可以亲自传承他们所创造的风格。大部分剑咏者的学校坐落在永聚岛或者埃弗拉斯卡。曾经有一所学校坐落在密斯卓诺，但是由于城市的毁灭，那些幸存下来的学徒们已经走失分散在世界各地。</p>\n<p>剑歌的风格种类基于武器运用的类型以及分别对应的动物类型来分别。这些特定的风格类型通过偏爱法术类型的运用，导师技艺的风格和特殊武器的运用来用特定的动物类型进行命名。剑咏者学徒们通常会得到一个他们所选择导师风格的动物纹身。一些剑咏者会学习多种剑歌风格，并获得许多的纹身，通过他们皮肤上的纹身警告那些不怀好意的人，他们拥有着致命的技艺。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"法师等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bOFe0xoSUxAi6tVB","name":"突袭大师 Ambush Master","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_AspectoftheIronHawk.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从13级起，你精通于引领突袭，在战斗中首先行动。</p>\n<p>         你在先攻检定时具有优势。此外，在第一轮战斗中你所命中的第一个生物对你和其他人而言会变得更容易打击；直到你下一回合开始之前，所有对它进行的攻击检定具有优势。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"斥候等级 13","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bSAdOpitFQ7qM60V","name":"振奋之潮 Inspiring Surge","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_BG_winWSG_3-0.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从10级起，每当你使用你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.YdtxSgV9hbHLx416]{动作如潮}能力时，你可以选择一个在你周围60尺内的盟友，他可以立刻用他的反应进行一次近战或者远程武器攻击。他必须要能看见或者听见你的声音才能获得这个好处。</p>\n<p>        从18级起，你可以选择两个盟友。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":"使用动作如潮。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"紫龙骑士等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bSCZVMQSSZKxYCPP","name":"神圣誓忠 Divine Allegiance","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_RighteousVengeance.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从7级起，如果一个在你周围5尺内的生物受到伤害，你可以使用你的反应魔法地代替目标生物承受这一次伤害，使目标不再受伤。你不能用任何方式减少或者阻止这个伤害。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"王冠之誓等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bag3ib2jXUYCe535","name":"活着的神话  Living Legend","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_AuraMastery.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         现在，你可以用壮举的传奇包装自己无论是真实的还是夸张的。以一个附赠动作，你可以在1分钟内获得以下好处</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你被赋予超凡脱俗的表征，在所有魅力属性检定中获得优势。</li>\n<li>在你的每回合中，当你进行武器攻击而未命中时，你可以将该次攻击改为命中。每回合你只能使用一次此能力。</li>\n<li>如果你的豁免失败了，你可以用反应重骰，你必须使用新的骰值。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>         一旦你使用了这个特性，直到你完成一次长休，或者消耗一个五环法术位来刷新，你都不能再使用。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MOT","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"荣耀之誓等级 20","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"beHICAkM6dJJZi1X","name":"宇宙预兆 Cosmic Omen","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003550.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你学会使用你的星图来占卜宇宙的意志。每当你完成一次长休，骰一次[[/r d6]]。根据你[[/r d6]]骰值是奇数还是偶数，你获得以下的一个预兆。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>吉兆（奇数）</strong>：每当你 30 尺内可见的一个生物进行一次攻击检定，豁免检定或属性检定，你可以使用你的反应来骰一个[[/r d6]]并将骰值加到检定结果中。</li>\n<li><strong>凶兆（偶数）</strong>：每当你 30 尺内可见的一个生物进行一次攻击检定，豁免检定或属性检定，你可以使用你的反应来骰一个[[/r d6]]并将骰值从检定结果中减去。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>你可以使用此反应的次数等同于你的感知调整值，且当你结束一次长休时恢复所有已使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"@abilities.wis.mod","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"d6","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"星辰结社等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bg7iCbCILIfQ0Thu","name":"阴谋大师 Master of Intrigue","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpsvignettewikianocookienetwowimages999Spellmiscemotionhappypngrevisionlatestcb20090317211041pathprefixru.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从3级起，你可以得到@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.26A1CCA4D4FC200D]{易容工具}、@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.5777EBC9E403D996]{文书伪造工具}和一种自选@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.193CC07CA8D6FDDF]{赌具}的熟练。你同时可以学会两种自选语言。</p>\n<p>         此外，如果你听到一个生物讲话长于1分钟，你可以确切无误地模仿他的语气和口音。这允许你模仿来自某个特殊地区的特别口音，只要你知晓这种语言。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"minute","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"策士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"blzFbMN0WrOEGDXX","name":"元素赐福 Elemental Gift","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_frostfire-orb.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你逐渐显露出你的巨灵宗主的特质。你对由你的宗主类型决定的一种伤害类型具有抗性：钝击（土巨灵），雷鸣（气巨灵），火焰（火巨灵），冷冻（水巨灵）。 同时，以一个附赠动作，你可以获得一个持续10分钟的30尺飞行速度，并且在飞行时你可以悬浮。你可以使用此附赠动作的次数等同于你的熟练加值，并在完成一次长休后恢复所有使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":3,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"巨灵宗主等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"b8jOgHndeuTasjp7","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.movement.fly","mode":4,"value":"30"},{"key":"data.attributes.movement.hover","mode":5,"value":"true"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":600},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_frostfire-orb.png","label":"获得 30 尺飞行速度","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.blzFbMN0WrOEGDXX","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bm2e5C25S0klCPH7","name":"酒疯沉醉 Intoxicated Frenzy","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_monk_dpsstance.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你17级时，你能对一大群敌人进行超量次数的乱舞打击。每当你使用你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.vLuoFN1x3tRWTPdm]{疾风连击}时，你可以用它进行最多三次的额外攻击（疾风连击最多可以进行五次攻击），前提是每一次疾风连击都能在本回合中取一个不同生物作为攻击目标。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"醉拳宗等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bolUalIQ1Ad2I6Mg","name":"夺命之手Hand of Harm","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Monk_TouchOfDeath.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你能用气来造成伤害。当你用徒手攻击命中一个生物时，可以花费1点气来额外造成等于1个你的武艺骰+感知调整值的黯蚀伤害。每回合你能使用该特性一次。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":"用徒手攻击命中一个生物；1 点气。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["d(ceil(((@classes.monk.levels)+2)/6)*2+2) + @abilities.wis.mod","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"命流宗等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bxUXWvE9SbYEdjqL","name":"天界宗主 Celestial（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Priest_Archangel.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你的宗主是上层位面的强大存在。你和一位古老的至高天、@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.lOYt73eaJojBDxAV]{炽天神侍}、麒麟、@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.G9PENY6nw0xRxCJW]{独角兽}，或其他居住于那些永享极乐的位面中的存在立下了契约。你与它们的契约让你体会到裸身沐浴在照亮多元宇宙的圣光中的独特体验。</p>\n<p>沐浴在如此力量中，会改变你的行为和信念。你可能发现自己投身于消灭不死生物、抵御魔族、保护无辜者的事业当中。不时地，你的心中会充斥着对你宗主拥有的天国的渴望，期冀于在你的余生中享有的天堂美景。但你知道你现在的任务是栖身于凡世之中，并给世界的黑暗角落带去光明。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">扩展法术列表</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.a5wqDP53A5UvGvSK]{疗伤术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.PHYXwNkXSdJjDCSD]{曳光弹}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.TEZY0aYJtnuU4FlW]{炽焰法球}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.I1C2EQxwynPd7dOC]{次级复原术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.uRF0L8no150cYca4]{昼明术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.TkFsGmyAeHknESJ4]{回生术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.LPXdi1HhVx8kJWYy]{信仰守卫}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.agTzLRmgNSVghaGk]{火墙术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Q8XNvy4kwTSQVizo]{焰击术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.7dqplcsKNYQgRh2S]{高等复原术}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"邪术师等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bxVV4yAmk5OhBemN","name":"策士 Mastermind（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Rogue_Disguise.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         策士专注于对人们施加影响和知晓他们的秘密。许多间谍，朝臣和阴谋家会追随这个范型，在密谋中渡过他们全部的生命。言语像你的匕首和毒药一般作为你的武器，通过它们你得到你最喜欢的宝藏——人们的要害所在以及他们言不由衷的支持。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游荡者等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"c0gGX4Cu8ZXvxR8f","name":"灼光复仇 Searing Vengeance","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_DivineProvidence.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从14级开始，你引导的光耀能量能让你抵抗死亡。当你在回合开始需要进行一次死亡豁免检定时，你可以选择在一次光耀能量的爆发中一跃而起。你恢复等于你最大生命值一半的生命值，如果你愿意的话可以选择处于站立状态。距你30尺以内的、你所选择的所有生物受到[[/r 2d8]]+你的魅力调整值的光耀伤害，并且目盲到你当前回合结束。</p>\n<p>当你使用这个职业特性后，在你完成一次长休前你无法再次使用此能力。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":"回合开始需要进行一次死亡豁免检定。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"cha","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d8+@abilities.cha.mod","radiant"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"floor(@attributes.hp.max/2)","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"天界宗主等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"c9cngYUCPCjGvMOi","name":"天界韧性 Celestial Resilience","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_DivineSpirit.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从10级开始，当你完成一次长休或短休后，你会得到临时生命值。得到的临时生命值等于你的邪术士等级+你的魅力调整值。另外，在你完成休息时，你可以选择最多五个视线中的生物。这些生物各自获得等于你的邪术士等级的一半+你的魅力调整值的临时生命值。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"cha","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["@classes.warlock.levels +@abilities.cha.mod","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"floor(@classes.warlock.levels /2)+@abilities.cha.mod","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"天界宗主等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"cbcMje3zSLozblAJ","name":"有限许愿术Limited Wish","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/002658.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你祈求你的宗主，并实现你的小小愿望。以一个动作，你可以向你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.94prCWbgDDsOtodq]{巨灵器皿}说出你的愿望，并请求实现一个6环或更低环阶的，且施法时间为1动作的法术效应。这一法术可以来自任何职业的法术列表，且你不需要满足法术材料需求，法术仅仅是作为此动作的一部分生效。</p>\n<p>你使用此特性后，你直到完成[[/r 1d4]]次长休后才能再次使用它。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d4","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"巨灵宗主等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"cjlVWsuWqlf4BBOH","name":"神圣之魂 Divine Soul（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_WrathV2.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>有时，支持着术士的魔力火花来自他灵魂中闪耀着的一点神力。拥有这样一种神迹的灵魂，表明你内在的魔法可能来自于一个遥远而强大的家族与某种神圣的存在之间有所联系。也许你的神是一个天使，变成了一个凡人，奉神的名义来战斗。或者你的出生可能与一个古老的预言相符，昭示着你是神的仆人，或者是神圣魔法的容器。</p>\n<p>一个具有自然魅力的神圣灵魂，被一些教派视为威胁。作为一个指挥着神圣的力量的局外人，一个神圣的灵魂可以通过声称与神的直接联系，来破坏一个现有的秩序。</p>\n<p>在某些文化中，只有那些具备神圣灵魂之力的人，才能统御宗教势力。在这些国度，教会的权利由几条血脉支配着，代代相传。</p>\n<p><strong>神圣魔法DIVINE MAGIC</strong></p>\n<p>你对于神力的联系允许你学习通常与牧师职业相关的法术。当你的施法特性让你学会一个术士戏法或一个1级或更高级的术士法术时，在术士法术列表之外，你可以从牧师法术列表中选择新法术。除此之外，你必须满足选择该法术的所有限制，而它对你而言成为一个术士法术。</p>\n<p>此外，选择一种对你神力来源的亲和力：善、恶、守序、混乱或中立。你可以根据这个关联，学习一个额外的法术，如下所示。这对你来说是一个术士法术，但它不与你术士法术的数量有关。如果你以后替换了这个法术，你必须用牧师的法术列表来替换它。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>亲和力Affinity</th>\n<th>法术Spell</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>善 </strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.a5wqDP53A5UvGvSK]{疗伤术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>恶</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Fl4lOWHo82WLp3g7]{致伤术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>秩序</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.U1GNY4potyr0c6mq]{祝福术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>混乱</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.XT4GwLQNAuPvtnrF]{灾祸术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>中立</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.IuzXxwP3EhWGhtXC]{防护善恶}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"术士等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"csxVkdUoKkeiFOjN","name":"呢喃指引 Guiding Whispers","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_ardenweald_hunter.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以通过与精魂沟通来引导你和其他人。你习得@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.QiU2ZZ09lBye0Iy4]{神导术 Guidance}戏法，且不计入你已习得的吟游诗人戏法数量。对你来说，当你施展@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.QiU2ZZ09lBye0Iy4]{神导术 Guidance}时，其施法距离为60尺。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"VRGR","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d4","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"精魂学院等级3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"IQE6hAV3ygaTICtD":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.SoROktB6wHO25o9l"}}}
{"_id":"d1FlrNgFQiucJHbz","name":"受祝击 Blessed Strikes","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_HolyBolt.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<p>8级牧师特性，替代@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.twDzAZCJeSqZnLTW]{神圣打击}或@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.lTR0ojCE1yFRvIjT]{强力施法}。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>在战斗中，你受到神力的祝福。当你通过戏法或武器攻击来伤害一个生物时，你能够对该生物造成额外[[/r 1d8]]光耀伤害。当你造成一次此伤害后，你直到自己的下一个回合开始前无法再次使用此特性。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d8","radiant"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"牧师等级 8","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"d9aVIFjiqL09iK7k","name":"燕返 Rapid Strike","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003080.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从15级起，你学会如何将精准转化为迅捷。如果你在这回合进行攻击动作且对目标的一个攻击骰有优势，你可以放弃那个优势骰转而对目标进行一次额外的武器攻击，作为同一个动作的一部分。每个回合你都只能使用一次该特性。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"武士等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dCcWJgyAQOMqZE6G","name":"奇械之魂 Soul Of Artifice","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_ImpHolyConcentration.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在20级时，你与你的魔法物品建立了一种神秘的联系，你可以利用它来保护自己。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你当前每有一件同调中的魔法物品，你就在所有豁免检定中得到+1加值。</li>\n<li>如果你的生命值降低到0，但没有立即死亡，你能以一个反应解除一个注法，使你的生命值降低到1而不是0。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奇械师等级 20","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dDtkcy3Nx0OGUR2d","name":"不朽者 The Undying（SCAG）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Shadow_DevouringPlague.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你的宗主早已破译了有关无穷生命的奥秘，死亡对于他而言不再有任何威胁。他不介意和一个凡人——在他看来寿命有如四季般更替、有如昼夜般闪烁的凡人分享他的力量，作为服务于他的一点奖赏。</p>\n<p>这类存在包括万隐万秘之主宰维克那，邪恶者伊乌兹，不朽殿的艾伦诺，吉斯洋基人的君王维拉基斯，还有不死的黑袍巫师费斯坦但提勒斯。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">扩展法术列表</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.DEl8kc5vGwLCNYpR]{虚假生命}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.PZQqlG5R6G24aWtm]{致病射线}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.5GWYJBfc1aZ6415M]{目盲/耳聋术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.K8KLs8zFHqBZittr]{沉默术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.ahDUyok3DMRcYLnS]{假死术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.o9GQEt4fYw6WjpB0]{死者交谈}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.9WDd3gopYOGyYnrT]{生命灵光}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.4gLdaCM7rxoNhj8d]{防死结界}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.gbHBG4jYU3I06JQO]{疫病术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.YJI4AeSEGPKf169b]{通晓传奇}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"邪术师等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dJAbTGhVw9DFET4M","name":"深海意志 The Fathomless（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_maldraxxus_deathknight1.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你已经浸没于和深渊的契约。你现在可以汲取整个大洋，水元素位面或者其他的异界海洋的无尽力量。你的宗主仅仅是想利用你去了解陆地，或者它希望你打开深海的阀门去淹没整个世界？</p>\n<p>也许你生为祂的信徒，你的家族世代崇拜深海宗主和祂眷族。或者你曾经遭遇海难，在溺死的边缘被你的宗主所拯救，祂给了你生存的机会。不管你为何和祂缔结契约，大海和它那未知的深渊听从你的召唤。</p>\n<p>能够赋予邪术师力量的深渊存在包括@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.kVg37NlPcACAzjCT]{克拉肯}们（泛指神话中的海妖），古老的元素生物，寇涛鱼人神话幻想中的存在，@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.KUpbXdn1XmHEeOPk]{人鱼}半神和@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.OQqybZoMeDFn5AFD]{海鬼婆}集会。</p>\n<h3><strong>海洋馈赠 Gift of the Sea</strong></h3>\n<p>你游泳速度为40尺，且可以在水下呼吸。</p>\n<h3><strong>扩展法术列表 Expanded Spell List</strong></h3>\n<p>当你学习一个邪术师法术时，你的深海宗主赐予你将以下法术加入邪术师法术列表进行选择的权力。</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>法术环位</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.V843ppI7fUmc5Gd6]{造水/枯水术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.8GM6YBgYFPIcFXKg]{雷鸣波}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.cGIrpk6h4Rf8QKV6]{造风术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.K8KLs8zFHqBZittr]{沉默术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.dHg72reVMXYFu4lR]{闪电束}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.InxRn0MsZsH5wslj]{雪雨暴}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.9zy4xObdmQFW9VP7]{操控水体}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.9Yhs9yVaMLPnDlSC]{元素召唤术（仅限水元素）}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.naXxMtlZiJr9JYdU]{毕格比之手（以触手的形式出现）}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.z9HXB89B3uO5NHW8]{寒冰锥}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"邪术师等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"l6mEoOrtONBoXCuy","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.movement.swim","mode":4,"value":"40"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_maldraxxus_deathknight1.png","label":"获得 40 尺游泳速度","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.dJAbTGhVw9DFET4M","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"daUkOPLMsi9wXl0C","name":"战歌训练  Traning in Sword and Song(TCE)","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_DeathKnight_SpellDeflection.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>你获得轻甲的熟练项，并获得一种自选的单手近战武器熟练项。<br />如果你尚未熟练表演技能，则还可以获得表演技能的熟练项。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"剑咏者等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"zWgM4eZOp0UEduvH","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.armorProf.value","mode":2,"value":"lgt"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_DeathKnight_SpellDeflection.png","label":"获得简易护甲熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.daUkOPLMsi9wXl0C","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null},{"_id":"vgkYx93TA1zgt66e","changes":[{"key":"data.skills.prf.value","mode":4,"value":"1"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_DeathKnight_SpellDeflection.png","label":"获得表演熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.daUkOPLMsi9wXl0C","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ddR4tv41KTeUD0Gg","name":"锻造之魂 Soul of the Forge","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_PowerWordShield.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从6级开始，你对锻造的掌控给你带来额外的好处。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你对火焰伤害有抗性。</li>\n<li>当你穿着重甲，你的AC获得+1加值。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"锻造领域等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"YeZo6c1WrzR4BDpc","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"fire"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_PowerWordShield.png","label":"获得火焰抗性","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.ddR4tv41KTeUD0Gg","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"djEK3U7fIVbhFpsx","name":"书士宗师 Master Scrivener","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/INV_Fabric_MoonRag_02.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>每当你完成一次长休，你可以令你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.mWchknyJMnozqbPO]{法师之笔}触碰一张空白的纸张或是羊皮纸，以将你@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.N1XJB0t4e9GM93tI]{觉醒魔典}中的一个法术并复制到这张纸上、并制造一个魔法卷轴。你制造卷轴时，魔典必须在你5尺之内。</p>\n<p>被复制的法术必须是1环或2环法术，且施法时间必须为1个动作。卷轴将增强法术的力量，令其视为比平常高1环阶的法术。你可以以一个动作阅读卷轴来施展其中的法术。卷轴对其他任何人都不可理解，且当你施展其中法术、或是完成下次长休后，卷轴上记载的法术将会消失。</p>\n<p>你同样熟练于制造城主指南第七章中所描述的法术卷轴。若你使用你的法术笔制造卷轴，所需要花费的金币和时间减半。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"书士会等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dkpQJsciaVomruu7","name":"念力突刺 Telekinetic Thrust","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-weapon-polearm-ice-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.uaPefnuz8mYlc7Th]{灵能击打}对一个目标造成伤害时，你可以使目标进行一次力量豁免来对抗DC等于8+你的熟练加值+你的智力调整值。如果豁免失败，你可以击倒目标或者将其在任意方向水平移动至多10尺。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"str","dc":null,"scaling":"int"},"requirements":"灵能武士等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dnHKTpzYGpMYiEvW","name":"引导神力:往墓之途","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_DeathKnight_Strangulate.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从你二级开始，你可以使用此能力来消亡敌人的生命力。</p>\n<p>         作为一个动作，直到你下回合结束，你诅咒30尺内的一个可视生物。当被诅咒的生物下一次被你或你的盟友的攻击命中，他对此次攻击的所有伤害具有易伤，之后诅咒终止。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"坟墓领域等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dpOHLoQUpFbxl3Nj","name":"彼岸故事 Tales from Beyond","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/sanctum_features_animadiversion.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你与那些借由你来讲述自己故事的精魂沟通。当你持握你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.Sew4Tj3ec9CwH53H]{精魂法器}时，你可以使用一个附赠动作，消耗一次你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.FSr7TfaoWRPpUtkD]{诗人激励}来投掷一次精魂故事表。诗人激励骰的掷骰结果将决定精魂们引导你说出何种故事。这个故事将保存在你脑海中，直到你用掉该故事的效果，或者完成一次短休或长休。</p>\n<p>你可以使用一个动作选择30尺内一个你能够看到的生物（可以是你自身）作为故事效果所影响的目标。一旦这样做之后，在下一次投掷故事表以前，你都无法再次使用此故事的效果。</p>\n<p>你的脑海中一次只能保存一种故事，再次投掷精魂故事表将立刻结束之前一个故事的效果。</p>\n<p>如果故事的效果需要进行豁免，其DC为你的法术豁免DC。</p>\n<table><caption>精魂故事表</caption>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>[[/r D12]]</th>\n<th>通过你讲述的故事</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td><strong>聪慧的动物的故事Tale of the Clever Animal</strong><br />接下来的10分钟内，每当目标进行一次智力、感知或魅力检定时，目标可以在投掷[[/r d20]]后额外立刻投掷一个额外的骰子，并将数值加到检定结果之中。额外骰的面数和你的诗人激励骰相同。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td><strong>著名决斗家的故事Tale of the Renowned Duelist</strong><br />你对目标进行一次近战法术攻击。若命中，则目标受到等同于2个你的诗人激励骰的掷骰结果+你的魅力调整值的力场伤害。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td><strong>挚友们的故事 Tale of the Beloved Friends</strong><br />目标和其所选的另一个在其5尺内且其可见的生物获得临时生命值，数值等于1个你的诗人激励骰的掷骰结果+你的魅力调整值。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td><strong>逃亡的故事Tale of the Runaway</strong><br />目标可以立即使用其反应来传送至多30尺，到一处其可见且未被占据的空间。当目标传送时，其能选择至多相当于你的魅力调整值（最少为0）数量的、在其30尺内的可见生物立即执行相同的反应。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td><strong>复仇者的故事 Tale of the Avenger</strong><br />在1分钟里，任何使用近战攻击命中目标的生物会受到相当于1个你的诗人激励骰的掷骰结果的力场伤害。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td><strong>旅行者的故事 Tale of theTraveler</strong><br />目标获得临时生命值，数值为一个你的诗人激励骰的掷骰结果+你的诗人等级。当其拥有这些临时生命值时，其移动速度增加10尺，并在其AC上获得+1加值。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td><strong>欺诈者的故事 Tale of the Beguiler</strong><br />目标进行一次感知豁免，失败则受到数值等同于2个你的诗人激励骰的掷骰结果的心灵伤害，并陷入失能incapacitated直到其下一个回合结束。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td><strong>鬼魅的故事Tale of the Phantom</strong><br />目标变为隐形invisible，直到其下一个回合结束，或以攻击命中一个生物。如果目标在这次隐形期间攻击命中了一个生物，被攻击的生物受到暗蚀伤害，数值等同于1个你的诗人激励骰的掷骰结果，并陷入对目标的恐慌frightened之中，持续到该生物的下一个回合结束。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9</td>\n<td><strong>凶蛮恶汉的故事 Tale of the Brute</strong><br />目标所选择的30尺内其可见的每个生物都必须进行一次力量豁免。若豁免失败，该生物受到3个你的诗人激励骰的掷骰结果的雷鸣伤害，并倒地prone。若豁免成功，该生物受到的伤害减半，并且不会倒地prone。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10</td>\n<td><strong>巨龙的故事 Tale of the Dragon</strong><br />目标从口中喷出30尺锥形的火焰。在范围内的每个生物都必须进行一次敏捷豁免，若豁免失败则受到4个你的诗人激励骰的掷骰结果的火焰伤害，若豁免则成功伤害减半。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11</td>\n<td><strong>天使的故事 Tale of the Angel</strong><br />目标恢复相当于2个你的诗人激励骰的掷骰结果+你的魅力调整值的生命值，并且你结束目标身上正起作用的状态中的一个，可结束的状态如下：目盲blinded，耳聋deafened，麻痹paralyzed，石化petrified或中毒poisoned。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>12</td>\n<td><strong>夺魂故事 Tale of the Mind-Bender</strong><br />你从某个超凡的存在那里唤起了一则超越人的理解能力的寓言。目标必须成功通过一次智力豁免，否则受到相当于3个你的诗人激励骰的掷骰结果的心灵伤害，并被震慑stunned直到其下一个回合结束。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"VRGR","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d12","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"精魂学院等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"IQE6hAV3ygaTICtD":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.QDdiLinrHSTLMFya"}}}
