{"_id":"eDwmwZd0yMESrMjf","name":"征服光环 Aura of Conquest","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_ArtofWar.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从7级起，只要你并未失能，你便弥漫出一阵威吓的灵光。光环包括你的格子，从你向各个方向延伸10尺，它会被全掩蔽所阻挡。</p>\n<p>         若一个生物恐慌于你，当其处于此光环内，其速度降为0，若其在光环内开始其回合，则受到等于你圣武士等级一半的心灵伤害。</p>\n<p>         从18级，此光环的距离增加到30尺。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["floor(@class.paladin.levels/2)","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"征服之誓等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"eGdmFkl676r4Nhd3","name":"忠诚呼唤 Faithful Summons","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/000526.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从14级开始，你通联的自然精魂会在你最为无助的时候保护你。若你的生命值降到0，或非自愿地变得失能，你可以立即获得@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.JTNL68CjsZelE8b5]{召唤动物}法术的好处，如同它是以一个9级法术位施展的那样。它召唤出四只由你选择的、挑战等级2或更低的野兽。被召唤的野兽出现在你周围20英尺内。如它们没有从你那里获得命令，它们会保护你免受伤害并攻击你的敌人。此法术持续1小时，无需专注，或直到你解消它（无需动作）。</p>\n<p>         一旦你使用了此特性，你无法再次使用它，直到你完成了一次长休为止。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":"生命值降到0，或非自愿地失能。"},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":20,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"牧人之环等级14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"eKQ66ycgCtYjnWYv","name":"死灵宗主The Undead（VRGR）","type":"subclass","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/achievement_dungeon_hallsofattonement_lordchamberlain.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你与不死的存在结下契约，这些生物藐视生与死的循环，抛弃凡躯，永恒地追求无尽的野心。对于这些存在来说，时间和道德都是转瞬即逝的东西，只有生命的沙漏匆匆流逝的人才会在意。这些古老的不死之身曾是凡人，对于如何实现野心，跨过死亡之门有着切身体会。他们迫切地与在生灵间履行他们意志的侍从，分享亵渎生命的知识和秘密。</p>\n<p>这般存在有：半巫妖阿瑟瑞拉克demilich Acererak，吸血鬼暴君血手凯斯the vampire tyrant Kas the Bloody-Handed，吉斯洋基巫妖女王维拉基斯the githyanki lich-queen Vlaakith，龙巫妖卓公煞the dracolich Dragotha，不死法老安卡特珀特the undead pharaoh Ankhtepot，以及逃离的黑暗领主亚扎林·雷克斯the elusive Darklord, Azalin Rex。</p>\n<p><strong>扩展法术列表Expanded Spell List</strong></p>\n<p>死灵宗主让你在学习邪术师法术时，可以从扩大的法术列表中选择，将以下法术为你添加到邪术师法术列表中。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">扩展法术列表</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.XT4GwLQNAuPvtnrF]{灾祸术 Bane}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.DEl8kc5vGwLCNYpR]{虚假生命 False Life}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.5GWYJBfc1aZ6415M]{目盲/耳聋术 Blindness/Deafness}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.ScqNvMCUNcvTs5rG]{魅影之力 phantasmal force}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.94pGYJy85jxFKHi8]{魅影驹 Phantom Steed}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.o9GQEt4fYw6WjpB0]{死者交谈 Speak with Dead}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.4gLdaCM7rxoNhj8d]{防死结界 Death Ward}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Au584WRiGch84PXI]{高等隐形术 Greater Invisibility}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.XK3IvcqPquyj1W3P]{防活物护罩 Antilife Shell}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.T39k39dbE2poIFc5]{死云术 Cloudkill}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"VRGR","identifier":"the-undead","classIdentifier":"warlock","advancement":[{"_id":"zf1dkhumwcl5ybs7","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.39YlsyoJXTtDSGf4"],"optional":true},"value":{},"level":1,"title":"职业特性","icon":""},{"_id":"e28dbaq7tfbn37s7","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.i3weCx7bGsnIbg8s"],"optional":false},"value":{},"level":6,"title":"职业特性","icon":""},{"_id":"0a759filpxqij4rs","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.NeBFoq8gg0253mfG"],"optional":false},"value":{},"level":10,"title":"职业特性","icon":""},{"_id":"93x3vottt2aglayt","type":"ItemGrant","configuration":{"items":["Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.zWcXri77krJizuaE"],"optional":false},"value":{},"level":14,"title":"职业特性","icon":""}],"spellcasting":{"progression":"none","ability":""},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"IQE6hAV3ygaTICtD":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.subclass.K8769YOGYqLIB904"}}}
{"_id":"eS7Ex4p5Yh3jDtSb","name":"决斗大师 Master Duelist","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/002503.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         第 17 级起，你对剑术的精通使你得以扭转战斗胜负。如果你的一次攻击检定未命中，则你可以选择带优势再进行一次攻击检定。使用该特性后，你直到完成一次短休或长休前都不能再次启用它。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游荡剑客等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"eSkokko4kmkFhvbR","name":"战斗变通 Martial Versatility","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/red_05.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>每当你通过提升圣武士等级获得属性值提升时，你可以用另一个圣武士能够选择的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.0LbuXQnP6LC0gn3H]{战斗风格}替换你当前的战斗风格。这一变化代表着你在战斗训练上重心的转移。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"圣武士等级 4","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"eXk4FM2eHvy3WS67","name":"逝者遗物Tokens Of The Departed","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Warlock_Haunt.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当生命终结于你的眼前，你可从离去的灵魂中抓取出一小片其生命精华的具现化象征：当你30尺内一个可见生物死亡时，你可以以一个反应张开一只空手，使得一个微型的饰物——一个魂器——出现在你的掌心。DM决定魂器的外观或者让你骰玩家手册中的饰品表来决定。你最多可以同时持有魂器的数目等同于你熟练加值的魂器且当你所持魂器数目达到上限时你不再能制造新的魂器。</p>\n<p>你能以下列方式使用魂器：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>当你随身携带着魂器时，由于你的生命力受到了魂器内蕴藏的生命精华的强化，你在死亡豁免检定和体质豁免检定上具有优势。</li>\n<li>当你在你的回合里造成偷袭伤害时，你可以销毁你的一个魂器，在不消耗能力使用次数的情况下，瞬间使用墓穴惊嚎。</li>\n<li>以一个动作，你可以销毁一个你的魂器，无论它在哪里。若你如此做，你可以向与魂器相关的灵体一个问题。灵体将出现在你面前并以它生前所知的一种语言回答。它并无义务对你诚实，并由于其对自由的渴望将回答地尽量简略。DM应当决定在这个灵体只知道他生前所知。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"2","per":"charges"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"鬼魅等级 9","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"eZMKbK1TDBqqB70K","name":"海渊传送 Fathomless plunge","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_monk_chiexplosion1.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以魔法性地打开一个前往水域目的地的临时通道。你可以使用一个标准动作传送自己和最多五个自愿、且在30尺可视范围内的生物。在一团触须的漩涡中，你们全部消失，然后在至多1里以内的你曾见过的水域（至少为池塘大小）或者它的30尺范围内。你们当中的每一个人都出现在距离其他人30尺以内的一个空的空间内。</p>\n<p>一旦你使用了这一特性，你不能再次使用它直到你完成一次短休或长休。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":5,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"深海意志等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"eZWU8IrHPcNXuu0w","name":"突袭 Ambush","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/weapon_08.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你进行一次敏捷（隐匿）检定或先攻检定时，你能够消耗一枚卓越骰，并将消耗的卓越骰加入检定中。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战斗大师等级 3，卓越技巧，战技专家","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"elgZeXSAplLNQhD1","name":"剑舞大师 Master's Flourish","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_SheathofLight.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>14级时，当你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.6phT9JzgLIAgIu4Y]{剑舞}选项时，你可以投掷一枚[[/r D6]]来代替吟游激励的消耗。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"d6","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"剑舞学院等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"enRJaReImW7ZVMDY","name":"施法（奇械师） Spellcasting","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003005.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你已经学习了魔法的工作原理，知道如何引导魔法进入物体，以及如何唤醒魔法。因此，你获得了有限的施法能力。在旁观者看来，你不会用传统的方式施法——你看起来好像在通过各种物品创造奇迹。</p>\n<h3><strong>必备工具</strong></h3>\n<p>         你通过你的工具产生你的奇械师法术效果。当你使用施法特性来施展法术时，必须手持一个法器——通常是@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.F8C51FA868C3F758]{盗贼工具}或工匠工具。你必须熟练这一工具才能将它作为法器使用。</p>\n<p>         当你在第二级获得物品注法特性后，你也能使用任何你注入魔法的物品来作为法器使用。</p>\n<h3><strong>戏法</strong></h3>\n<p>         根据    “@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-table.2A3nWtToOKL8Asu3]{奇械师职业表}”在第1级，你从奇械师法术列表中习得两个戏法。在更高的等级，你能够习得更多戏法。</p>\n<p>         当你提升一个奇械师等级时，你能够从奇械师法术列表中习得一个新的戏法来替换一个原有的已知戏法。</p>\n<h3><strong>法术的准备和施展</strong></h3>\n<p>         奇械师职业表”显示出你有多少能用于施法的法术位。施展某个奇械师法术时，你必须同时消耗其对应环阶的法术位。而已消耗的法术位则可以通过完成一次长休进行恢复。</p>\n<p>         你需要从奇械师法术列表中选择想要准备的法术，你能选择的准备法术总数等于你的智力调整值＋你奇械师职业等级的一半（向下取整）（最少为1）。你只能准备已经获得相应环阶法术位的法术。</p>\n<p>         例如，作为一名5级奇械师时，你拥有四枚1环法术位和两枚2环法术位。假如你的智力为14，则你的准备法术列表可以囊括总共四个1环或2环法术的组合。如果你准备了1环法术@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.a5wqDP53A5UvGvSK]{疗伤术}，则你可以使用1环或者2环的法术位来施展它。另外，已施展的法术并不会从你的准备列表中移除。</p>\n<p>         你可以在完成长休后改变你的准备法术列表。如需准备新的奇械师法术，你需要花时间来调整你的法器：每个法术要花费至少1分钟的时间。</p>\n<h3><strong>施法关键属性</strong></h3>\n<p>         你对魔法理论的理解使你能够以更高超的技法来使用这些法术，因此智力是你的施法关键属性。每当你的法术需要施法关键属性时均指向你的智力值。而你奇械师法术的豁免DC和攻击检定，也使用你的智力调整值。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>法术豁免DC</strong>＝8＋你的熟练加值＋你的智力调整值<br /><strong>法术攻击调整值</strong>＝你的熟练加值＋你的智力调整值</p>\n<h3><strong>仪式施法</strong></h3>\n<p>         如果你准备了带有仪式标签的法术，则你可以用这些法术进行仪式施法。</p>\n<h3><strong>技艺的魔法</strong></h3>\n<p>         身为一名奇械师，你在施法时使用工具。当描述你的施法时，请想想你是如何使用一个工具来执行这个法术效果的。如果你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.EFBBAE8B63126638]{炼金工具}来施展疗伤术，你可以很快的制造出药膏。如果你用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.E20CE7D30DE58B23]{修理工具}来施展，你可能会拿出一个微型机械蜘蛛来缝合伤口。当你施放@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.odeHix5Pr59Dvg1n]{毒气喷溅}时，你可以喷射出有毒的化学物质，或者使用一根喷射毒液的魔杖。法术的效果和其他的施法者职业是一样，但是你的施法方法是特殊的。</p>\n<p>         同样的原则也适用于你准备法术的时候。作为一名奇械师，你不需要学习魔法书，也不需要祈祷去准备你的魔法。你需要使用工具来制造用于产生效果的特定物品。如果你用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.0kzjiCnyoMHwijsp]{电爪}替换疗伤术，你可能会破坏你用来治疗的设备，并用它的部件制造一个攻击性的物品—— 这可能是一只能够让你引导冲击性能量的长手套。</p>\n<p>         这些细节不会以任何方式限制你，也不会给你带来任何好处。你不需要证明你是如何使用工具来施展法术的。但是创造性地描述你的施法是一种能够让你从其他施法者中脱颖而出的有趣方法。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奇械师等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"esOkyryLICY1Aew7","name":"真菌感染 Fungal Infestation","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Deathknight_UnholyPresence.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>       在</span>6级时，你的孢子获得了感染并活化遗体的能力。<br />       如果一个小型或中型的野兽或类人生物在你十尺内死亡，你可以以一个反应动作活化它，令它站起并具有1点生命值。该生物使用MM中@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.NAISFPoNNgUCsEyW]{僵尸}的属性，它将持续活化状态1小时，之后会倒下死去。<br />       在战斗中，它的回合紧接着你的。它遵从你的精神指令，而它只能进行攻击动作，进行一次近战攻击。<br />       该特性的可用次数等于你的感知调整值（至少一次）。而已消耗的特性使用次数则可以通过完成一次长休进行恢复。</p>\n<p> </span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GGR","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"max(@abilities.wis.mod,1)","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"孢子结社等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"etRpMB1H2VnYDWTU","name":"巫咒盔甲 Armor of Hexes","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Priest_Halo_Shadow.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在10级时，你的巫咒变得更加强大。若你以@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.JRyFQmsWflAFkBgN]{咒剑诅咒}所指定的目标以一次攻击检定击中你，你可以用你的反应投一次[[/r d6]]。在4或更高的结果下，这次攻击改为对你失手，不论骰值是多少。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"d6","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"咒剑士等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"f8UFvQ4UEQH5959m","name":"巫咒大师 Master of Hexes","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_DeathKnight_AoeDeathGrip.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从14级起，你可以转移你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.JRyFQmsWflAFkBgN]{咒剑诅咒}，从一个被杀的生物转移到另一个生物。当被你的咒剑诅咒所指定的生物死亡时，假如你并未失能，你可以将诅咒转移到一个距离你30尺内你能看到的其他生物身上。当你以此法转移诅咒，你不再从先前目标的死亡中获得生命值回复。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"咒剑士等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fIq6d2zbCjD9v7DH","name":"战术思维 Tactical Wit","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_SpiritualGuidence.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从2级起，你对于战略格局的急速把控让你能在战斗中快速的反应。你在先攻检定中获得等于你智力调整值的加值。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战争法师等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fKWRSpVdUaeIR8Kx","name":"器皿庇护所 Sanctuary Vessel","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Monk_JasmineForceTea1.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.G2j6gL7q6TmZHs2B]{瓶中小憩}特性进入你的巨灵器皿时，你可以选择30尺内最多5个可见自愿生物与你一同进入器皿。</p>\n<p>以一个附赠动作，你可以将任意数目的生物从器皿中逐出，且如果你离开器皿或是其被摧毁，所有生物都将被逐出。</p>\n<p>同时，在器皿中停留至少10分钟的任何生物（包括你自己）可视为完成了一次短休，且使用生命骰恢复生命值时的恢复量可以加上你的熟练加值。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"巨灵宗主等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fP9l4SdYuSPi0ofQ","name":"增强联结 Expansive Bond","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_AuraMastery.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.39vgDk1ARYUxfuoE]{勇气联结}和@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.viW2PkM3OfKDK0o9]{保护联结}的生效范围变为联结生物在彼此60尺内。此外，当生物使用保护联结来为其他人承受伤害时，该生物对那次伤害具有抗性。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"和平领域等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"g473FXNMREvpFY5E","name":"锻造祝福 Blessing of The Forge","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_GaurdedbytheLight.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从1级起，你获得将魔法灌输到武器或护甲中的能力。在长休的结束，你可以触摸一件非魔法护甲或者简易或军用武器，直到你下一次长休或者你死亡，若是护甲，其AC获得+1加值；若是武器，其攻击骰和伤害骰获得+1加值。</p>\n<p>一旦你使用过此特性，直到你完成一次长休，你无法再次使用它。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"锻造领域等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
