{"_id":"g7PSjAUIkd11YW3I","name":"生存专家 Survivalist","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpcloud3steamusercontentcomugc842586004367121393DCD7AFDB511D291B44480E4688A71887EBC98AB6.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         当你在3级时选择此范型时，你得到对于自然和生存技能的熟练。当使用上述熟练进行的任何属性检定中，你的熟练加值加倍。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"斥候等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"tAaH1N9Er0IgLijR","changes":[{"key":"data.skills.sur.value","mode":4,"value":"1"},{"key":"data.skills.nat.value","mode":4,"value":"1"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpcloud3steamusercontentcomugc842586004367121393DCD7AFDB511D291B44480E4688A71887EBC98AB6.jpg","label":"获得自然、生存熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.g7PSjAUIkd11YW3I","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"gDsqXKtRpltzhHLP","name":"命极之手Hand of Ultimate Mercy","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_monk_serenity.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你对生命能量的掌握打开了通往命流奥义的大门，以一个动作，你可以接触一个在过去24小时内死亡生物的尸体并消耗5点气，该生物则会复活，恢复相当于[[/r 4D10]]+你的感知调整值的生命值。如果该生物是在以下这些状态时死亡，它会在移除这些状态后复活：目盲、耳聋、麻痹、中毒和震慑。</p>\n<p>一旦你使用了这个特性，你就不能再使用它，直至你完成一次长休。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"5 点气。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":"object"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["4D10 + @abilities.wis.mod","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"命流宗等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"gQZB2uObJD1G15TX","name":"剑圣宗 Way of the Kensei（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/002518.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>研习剑圣之道的武僧沉浸于器械训练，达到了“武器就是身体的延伸”这一境界。在研习剑术的基础上，这一流派也同时涉猎诸多不同的武器。</p>\n<p>器械之于剑圣，就如同画笔之于画家、笔墨之于文人。剑圣将其视为用来展现武道之美丽优雅的工具。这一信条使得剑圣成为了盖世无双的武者，但与此同时也受缚于热情奉献和刻苦专研。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"武僧等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"gRkU4RaaZC8IY85b","name":"精妙剑法 Unerring Accuracy","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Rogue_SliceDice.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>第17级起，你对武器的运用更为精妙。如果你使用武僧武器进行的攻击检定失败了，你可以重新掷骰。该特性你每回合只能使用一次。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":null,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"剑圣宗等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"gTWRbBcc3Ecf7grG","name":"灵魂骗手 Soul of Deceit","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Mage_PotentSpirit.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从17级起，除非你允许，否则你的思想不能被心灵感应或者其他能力阅读。如果你使用魅力（欺瞒）检定并在与思想阅读者的感知（洞悉）检定的对抗之中胜出，你还可以伪造思想使对方信以为真。</p>\n<p>         此外，不管你说什么，你总是可以选择让魔法判定你在说真话并显现出相应的迹象。你也不会因为魔法效应的影响而被强迫说出真话。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"策士等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"gUogqXt5i3DjyA2j","name":"意念守护 Guarded Mind","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_siege_engineer_pattern_recognition.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>被灵能力量沐浴的你，意念得到增强。你对于心灵伤害有抗性。此外，如果你在你的回合开始时处于魅惑或者恐慌的状态，你可以消耗一个灵能骰并结束这些状态对你的影响。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"灵能武士等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"MD0I78qdXlo1vefM","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"psychic"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_siege_engineer_pattern_recognition.png","label":"获得心灵抗性","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.gUogqXt5i3DjyA2j","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"h5qHOk6IYIB73din","name":"闪耀星座 Twinkling Constellations","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003142.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>你的星耀形态星座增强了。射手座和圣杯座的[[/r 1d8]]变成了[[/r 2d8]]，而且在巨龙座激活时，你获得 20 尺飞行速度并且可以悬浮。</p>\n<p>此外，在星耀形态下的每回合开始时，你可以改变身上闪耀的星座。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"星辰结社等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"hFo41NKugH2WXnZ7","name":"书士会 Order of Scribes（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/inv_misc_book_07.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>许多人将法师魔法称为&ldquo;书之魔法&rdquo;，想想法师为研读卷宗与书写魔法理论花费了多少时间，这称呼也是名副其实。旅行中的法师包里，总是撑满书本卷宗；若能一探远古知识，法师愿意赴汤蹈火。</p>\n<p>书士会是法师之间与书卷的联系最为紧密的群体。尽管书士会在不同的世界之间有着不同的形态，但无论位于何处，其主要任务都是同一的：将魔法上的发现记载下来，令法师魔法繁荣昌盛。尽管所有法师都将法术书视为珍宝，书士会的法师却能用魔法唤醒他们的法术书，将其变为值得信赖的伙伴；所有法师都会研习书本，但书士却能与书本对话！</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"法师等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"hGJnoKdbKBe2vrDU","name":"巨灵宗主 The Genie（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_sandelemental.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你与巨灵中的稀有群体，巨灵贵族缔结了契约。巨灵贵族乃是广阔的元素位面的统治者，并对其他次等巨灵与次等元素生物具有莫大的影响力。巨灵贵族们的动机各不相同，但都傲慢自大且有着匹敌次等神明的强大伟力。他们喜好让热衷于缚誓巨灵的凡人们反过来服侍他们，并对于缔结能扩张他们在多元宇宙中势力的契约有着巨大的热情。</p>\n<p>你可以选择你宗主是哪种巨灵也可以通过巨灵种类表让骰子决定。如表所示，每种巨灵都与一种元素相对应。</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>[[/r d4]]</th>\n<th>种类</th>\n<th>对应元素</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>土巨灵</td>\n<td>土</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.5P1VGAZQwOilwZQf]{气巨灵}</td>\n<td>气</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.LTomFUTBrkRi0Pj5]{火巨灵}</td>\n<td>火</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>水巨灵</td>\n<td>水</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>当你学习一个邪术师法术时，你的巨灵宗主扩宽了你的可学习法术范围。巨灵扩展法术表包含加入到了邪术师法术列表中的巨灵法术和与你的巨灵宗主类型相关的法术。</p>\n<h3><strong>巨灵宗主扩展法术 Genie Expanded Spells</strong></h3>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td> </td>\n<th>全巨灵</th>\n<th>土巨灵</th>\n<th>气巨灵</th>\n<th>火巨灵</th>\n<th>水巨灵</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>一环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.zeN5fxXLn4QE2YDa]{侦测善恶}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.FbxdKcDpSPWuGTLA]{庇护术}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.8GM6YBgYFPIcFXKg]{雷鸣波}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.CB9z74KJLWMplGuz]{燃烧之手}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.rKLSWNBCS8eqGUll]{云雾术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>二环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.ScqNvMCUNcvTs5rG]{魅影之力}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.1oL8DBOVZMuhaKpw]{荆棘丛生}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.cGIrpk6h4Rf8QKV6]{造风术}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.IkgKSSiBuGa5TPLB]{灼热射线}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.2XwLnziQi0Iv7GQT]{朦胧术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>三环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.1wNlI6I8gtlQlm3q]{造粮术}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.pJ6hE8Vab5Ypuqm4]{融身入石}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_clas