{"_id":"hOJZRR0bgcBGsTgT","name":"察觉魔法 Magic Awareness","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Mage_StudentOfTheMind.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>以一个动作，你让你的感官对聚集的魔力的存在保持警觉。知道你的下一个回合结束前，你可以知晓你60尺内任何法术或者魔法物品的位置，除非它们对你有完全掩护。当你察觉到一个法术的存在时，你还能判断这个法术属于哪一个学派。</p>\n<p>你每天可以使用该能力的次数等于你的熟练加值。每完成一次长休之后你补充齐所有已消耗的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":60,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"2","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"狂野魔法道途等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"hhdcnaUYZaV2iWIl","name":"护卫光环 Aura of the Guardian","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/000151.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从7级起，你可以以自己的健康为代价保护盟友免受伤害。当一个处于你10尺内的生物受到伤害时，你可以用一个反应动作，魔法性地使你代替该生物承受此伤害。此特性不会传递任何该伤害可能附带的效果，该伤害也无法被任何方式减少。</p>\n<p>         在18级，此光环的距离增加到30尺。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"救赎之誓等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"hpaOlH1qrWKtRwaY","name":"精通收割者 Improved Reaper","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_revendreth_deathknight.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         第17级起，该牧师施展一个1至5环的死灵法术时，若该法术只指定一个生物为目标，则将其改为指定施法距离内相互之间距离不超过5尺的两个生物。如果该法术消耗其材料构材，则该牧师必须为每个目标提供一份耗材。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"死亡领域等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"i3YthtU7oYjfnZgB","name":"追踪箭 Seeking Arrow","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_Misdirection.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         使用预言魔法，你赋予你的箭自寻目标的能力。当你使用该选项时，你不用为该次攻击投攻击骰，取而代之，选择一名在过去的1分钟里你见过的角色。如果需要的话，这只箭会立刻掉头飞向那名角色，且忽视四分之三和半遮蔽。如果目标在箭的射程范围内且中间路程适合箭飞行至目标，目标必须做一个敏捷豁免。如果豁免失败，角色会受到如同被这只箭击中的伤害和额外[[/r 1d6]]的穿刺伤害，而且你得知目标的确切位置。如果成功，伤害减半且你无法得知其方位。如果目标不在范围内，箭会在飞行到最大距离后消失。</p>\n<p>         当你的战士等级到18级时该穿刺伤害增加到[[/r 2d6]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(ceil(@classes.fighter.levels/17))d6","piercing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"int"},"requirements":"魔射手等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"i3weCx7bGsnIbg8s","name":"坟冢之触 Grave Touched","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_animarevendreth_missile.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你宗主的力量对你的身体和魔法产生了深远的影响。你不需要吃、喝、呼吸。</p>\n<p>此外，每你的回合一次，当你用攻击检定命中一个生物并对该生物投掷伤害骰时，你可以将伤害类型替换为暗蚀伤害。当你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.39YlsyoJXTtDSGf4]{战栗形态}时，你可以在确定目标受到该暗蚀伤害的数值时，额外投掷一枚伤害骰。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"VRGR","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"死灵宗主等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"IQE6hAV3ygaTICtD":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.QDdiLinrHSTLMFya"}}}
{"_id":"i7WUteJZQLyoN9Jn","name":"炼金术掌握 Alchemical Savant","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Shaman_RepulsionTotem.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在第5级，你对魔法化学物质的掌握变得非常熟练，这将提高你通过炼金物质造成的治疗和伤害效果。当你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.EFBBAE8B63126638]{炼金工具}作为法器施法时，你在法术的一次掷骰中获得加值。该掷骰必须恢复生命值或是造成强酸、火焰、黯蚀或毒素伤害，获得的加值等于你的智力调整值（最低+1）。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"炼金师等级 5","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"i8fpZzA2N0hL3Irs","name":"低语光环 Mantle of Whispers","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_deathknight_hemorrhagicfever.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         6级时，你得到了吸取类人生物的人格的能力。当一个类人生物在你周围30尺内死去时，你可以使用你的反应，通过魔法能力捕获其影。你能保持这个影子直到你完成了一次长休。</p>\n<p>         你能以一个动作使用影子，当你这么做时，影子消失，魔法改变了你的外表。你看起来就像那个死去的人物，除了你还健康的活着。伪装持续1小时，或直到你以一个附赠动作结束此效果。</p>\n<p>         当你处于伪装中，你会获得所有该生物会与泛泛之交分享的信息。这包括了其背景和人生的一般细节，但不包括秘密。这些信息足够你借用它的记忆来伪装成该生物。</p>\n<p>         其他生物可以通过进行一次感知（洞察）检定，对抗你的魅力（欺瞒）检定，来看穿此伪装，你在你的检定中获得+5加值。</p>\n<p>         一旦你使用此特性捕捉了一道影子，直到你完成了一次短休或长休前，你都不能再次使用它。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"低语学院等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"iWd81TlNiudP2qNo","name":"防护战术 Warding Maneuver","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Mount_Charger.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         7级起，你学会如何抵御对你、你的坐骑和你附近角色的直接攻击。如果你或者在你5尺之内对你可视的一名角色被一次攻击击中，且你手持一把近战武器或者一面盾牌，你能以一个反应投一个[[/r 1d8]]，将骰值加入被攻击角色的AC中。如果这次攻击仍然击中，则被攻击目标对这次攻击伤害有抗性。</p>\n<p>         你能够使用该特性的次数等同于你的体质调整值（至少为1），而且你在长休后重新获得所有被消耗的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d8","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"骑兵等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ib0ifxFwCSyC0MQs","name":"壮大集群 Mighty Swarm","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_animaardenweald_buff.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.PTCrPW76ym8UFl6t]{蜂聚集群}通过以下方式变得更加强大：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>蜂聚集群的伤害提升到[[/r d8]]。</li>\n<li>如果一个生物在对抗被蜂聚集群移动的豁免检定中失败，你也能让集群将该生物击倒在地。</li>\n<li>当你被蜂聚集群移动时，直到你下个回合开始它使你获得半身掩护。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"集群守卫等级 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"iiNpYFVFDEWiGigt","name":"战斗准备 Battle Ready","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_ImprovedSteadyShot.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在第3级时，你的战斗训练和魔法实验为你带来了两种好处：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你得到军用武器的熟练。</li>\n<li>当你以魔法武器攻击时，你可以在攻击和伤害检定使用智力调整值，以代替力量或敏捷。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战地匠师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"C8LVcbvJ81HZ0fdG","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.weaponProf.value","mode":2,"value":"mar"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_ImprovedSteadyShot.png","label":"获得军用武器熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.iiNpYFVFDEWiGigt","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"iim2hoh4OGrRYZU0","name":"战术预估 Tactical Assessment","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/red_26.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你进行一次智力（调查）、智力（历史）或感知（洞悉）检定时，你能够消耗一枚卓越骰，将消耗的卓越骰加入此次属性检定中。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战斗大师等级 3，卓越技巧，战技专家","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"isja3NVg13Ebf1OV","name":"听声辨谎 Ear for Deceit","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Arcane_MindMastery.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         当你在3级选择此范型时，你的双耳变得锐利，能发现谎言。当你进行一次感知（洞察）检定来察觉一个生物是否在说谎时，你可以将[[/r d20]]投中7或更低的结果都视为8。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"审判官等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"j5MquMAXBmJjVtQE","name":"月光与阴影的炉心 Hearth of Moonlig","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_ElunesGrace.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>          6级起，无论你在何处设立营灶，那都是的你家园。在进行一次短休或长休时，你可以祈求薄暮庭院的幽影之力来保护你的营地不被外来者侵扰。在休息开始时，你接触空间中的一点，以那一点为中心一个隐形的、半径30尺的球体魔法般地出现。全掩护会阻断这个球体。</p>\n<p>          在这一领域内你和你的盟友在所有感知（观察）检定和敏捷（隐匿）检定中得到+5加值，并且由任何明火放射的光亮（营火，火把以及类似之物）从领域外是不可见的。</p>\n<p>          这些效果持续到休息结束或你离开这个领域。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"spec"},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"sphere"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"梦境之环等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jDdEN3Im7kyYhI69","name":"死亡领域 Death Domain（DMG）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Shadow_DeadofNight.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         死亡领域关注的是导致死亡的原力，以及唤起不死生物的负能量。其神祇诸如奇魔须Chemosh、米尔寇Myrkul和维婕丝Wee Jas等，都是死灵法师、死亡骑士、巫妖、木乃伊领主和吸血鬼的守护神。死亡领域的神灵还具现为谋杀（阿努比斯Anubis、巴尔Bhaal和匹里麻斯Pyremius），痛苦（鲁兹Iuz或劳薇塔Loviatar），疾病或毒药（英凯布居罗斯Incabulos、塔洛娜Talona或魔吉安Morgion），和冥界underworld（哈迪斯Hades和赫尔Hel）。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>牧师等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>1st</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.DEl8kc5vGwLCNYpR]{虚假生命}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.PZQqlG5R6G24aWtm]{致病射线}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>3rd</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.5GWYJBfc1aZ6415M]{目盲/耳聋术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.VRvKmIZL44nZWKaa]{衰弱射线}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>5th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.xYpJGRI4xcMa41kO]{操纵死尸}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.FKjra48NDHtB4518]{吸血鬼之触}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>7th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.AVumturalJuP4paw]{枯萎术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.4gLdaCM7rxoNhj8d]{防死结界}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>9th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.XK3IvcqPquyj1W3P]{防活物护罩}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.T39k39dbE2poIFc5]{死云术}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3><strong>附赠熟练项</strong> Bonus Proficiency</h3>\n<p>          该牧师在第1级选择该领域时将获得军用武器的熟练项。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"牧师等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"n8VXbPU4asCNuihT","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.weaponProf.value","mode":2,"value":"mar"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Shadow_DeadofNight.png","label":"获得军用武器熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.jDdEN3Im7kyYhI69","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jHxwPXj6zU9OtE78","name":"不移胜者 Invincible Conqueror","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_ReviveChampion.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在20级时，你得到驾驭特异武艺的能力。以一个动作，你可以魔法性的变成征服的化身，获得下述的好处，持续1分钟：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你对于所有伤害得到抗性。</li>\n<li>当你在你的回合进行攻击动作时，你可以进行一次额外的攻击，作为该动作的一部分。</li>\n<li>你的近战武器攻击在掷出19或20时即可造成重击。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>         一旦你使用了此特性，直到你完成了一次长休后不能再使用它。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"征服之誓等级 20","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"nALEmfghsTTK9D0o","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":";所有伤害"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":60},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_ReviveChampion.png","label":"获得所有抗性","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.jHxwPXj6zU9OtE78","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jOo7iDNLOWo0d2kW","name":"神圣之翼 Otherworldly wings","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Priest_Archangel.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>14级起，你可以使用一个附赠动作，在你的背部展现一对光翼。当光翼展现时，你具有30尺的飞行速度。它们会一直展现着，直到你失能、死亡、或者你以一个附赠动作遣散。</p>\n<p>你为你神圣魔法的特性所选择的亲和力，决定了光翼的外观：鹰翼属于善良或守序，蝠翼属于邪恶或混乱，中立则是蜻蜓的翅膀。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"神圣之魂等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"Qy2Kd6jZiRwyYLnW","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.movement.fly","mode":4,"value":"30"}],"disabled":true,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Priest_Archangel.png","label":"获得 30 尺飞行速度","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.jOo7iDNLOWo0d2kW","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jU2csiLThCt65oAq","name":"识破弱点 Eye for Weakness","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_MindSooth.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         17级时，你学会通过认真的研究一个生物的战术和移动来找到他的弱点的能力。当你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.J4PCHlmBmtS4CRSB]{战斗洞察}对一个生物使用时，你对该生物的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.AlFAC3Lz1ud2ry9T]{偷袭}伤害提高[[/r 3d6]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"审判官等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jVhNhMk1RTTsycau","name":"防护场 Defensive Field","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/defensive/barrier-shield-dome-pink.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在每个你的回合，你能以一个附赠动作获得等于你奇械师职业等级的临时生命值，这会取代你现有的任何临时生命值。如果你脱下装甲，你会失去这些临时生命值。你能执行此附赠动作熟练加值次，在完成一次长休后将恢复所有花费的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["@classes.artificer.levels","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"装甲师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ja5LpMic3gboQVSl","name":"神圣打击（锻造）Divine Strike","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/SPELL_HOLY_AVENGINEWRATH.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在8级，你获得将你锻造的火热力量灌输到武器打击中的能力。每个你自己的回合一次，当你的武器攻击命中，你可以对目标额外造成[[/r 1d8]]的火焰伤害。在14级，额外伤害上升到[[/r 2d8]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(min(max(floor(((@classes.cleric.levels)-2)/6),1),2))d8","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"锻造领域等级 8","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jbF707c18X2M5EYm","name":"灼烧烈焰 Cauterizing Flames","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/inv_tradeskillitem_lessersorcerersfire.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你获得将死亡转化为可以用于治疗或焚烧的魔法火焰的能力。</p>\n<p>当一个小型或更大生物在你或你的野火精魂 30 尺内死亡时，无害幽火从其死亡生物空间中涌现并在此处摇曳 1 分钟。当一个你可见的生物进入该空间时，你可以用反应扑灭那里的幽火并对该生物进行治疗或火焰伤害。伤害或治疗数值等于[[/r 2d10]]+你的感知调整值。</p>\n<p>你能使用该特性的次数等于你熟练加值，你在完成一次长休后会恢复所有已消耗使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"@mod","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"2d10 + @abilities.wis.mod","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"野火结社等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jwpAmhTIVnQnKPhC","name":"风语者 Wind Speaker","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Shaman_AncestralGuidance.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从1级起，你操纵的奥术魔法浸染着风元素之力。你可以听、说、读、写原初语 Primordial。（了解这种语言允许你了解这些说这种语言的种族，同时你说的话也被他们理解：水族语Aquan,气族语Auran,火族语Ignan,土族语Terran）。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"狂怒风暴等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"z6rTlgYXWv4On4bY","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.languages.value","mode":2,"value":"primordial"},{"key":"data.traits.languages.value","mode":2,"value":"aquan"},{"key":"data.traits.languages.value","mode":2,"value":"auran"},{"key":"data.traits.languages.value","mode":2,"value":"ignan"},{"key":"data.traits.languages.value","mode":2,"value":"terran"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Shaman_AncestralGuidance.png","label":"习得原初语、水族语、气族语、火族语、土族语","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.jwpAmhTIVnQnKPhC","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jxABfDaC7XGVji2k","name":"戏法公式  Cantrip Formulas","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/inv_fabric_celestial_cloth.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你在法术书中写下了一套奥法公式，并能借此在心中推演出一个戏法。每当你完成一次长休，你可以查阅法术书中所记的公式，以将你的一个已知法师戏法替换为另一个来自法师法术列表的戏法。  </p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":"","long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"法师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"k1rERcaymVW92mjN","name":"额外吟游诗人法术  Additional Bard Spells","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/002615.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>下表中的法术扩充了《玩家手册》中的吟游诗人法术列表，排序基于法术环阶而非角色等级。表中在可仪式施法的法术后方追记了仪式标签。若无*号标记，表中法术均来自《玩家手册》（有*标记的法术来自TCE第三章）。《姗娜萨的万事指南》也提供了更多法术。</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>法术环位</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.f9cAcIAOPQ46mkf6]{七彩喷射}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Ja6HpsLeGA9MQ0Rm]{命令术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.hAL0Dxp9w7gvkfZm]{援助术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.1bUnNgI45qffE1P9]{变巨/缩小术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.1EkQSAH6o8WMxUU3]{镜影术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.EPA95aL0TTwT4WCb]{智能壁垒*} @Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.6PTF3SN0jxkEqv6W]{群体治愈真言}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.2AgiR8EQ7IglGbci]{缓慢术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.BLNE7S7l2uTkx7w6]{魅影杀手}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.mdnvLsKRorF3cx5S]{拉瑞心灵联结（仪式）}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.bgKL1d85c4YYYeCO]{英雄宴}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.fVnBnVVjKm1Nnrh8]{蓝纱一梦*}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.oxvIiEKCQhht8JrO]{虹光喷射}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.NXHO4t01vJcJ8Ct8]{嫌恶/关怀术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9环</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.ESNeo2IdY8F19MMt]{虹光法墙}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":