{"_id":"kCC5qgpOyMTSHaeM","name":"活化表演 Animating Performance","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ABILITY_PALADIN_DIVINESTORM.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>以一个动作，你可以选择你30尺内一个你可以看见大型或者更小的非魔法物品，赋予其生命。这件活化的物品将会使用如下舞空物品的属性，并且使用你的熟练加值。这件物品将会对你以及你的伙伴保持友好，而且会听从你的命令。它将持续保持活性一个小时，如果期间其生命值降低为0，或者你死亡，则该物品失去活性。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>舞空物品 Dancing Item</em><br />大型或者更小体型的构装生物</p>\n<p>护甲等级 16（天生护甲）<br />生命值 10+5*你的吟游诗人等级<br />速度 30尺速度，30尺飞行速度（可以盘旋在空中）<br />力量18（+4）<br />敏捷14（+2）<br />体质16（+3）<br />智力4（-3）<br />感知10（+0）<br />魅力6（-2）<br />伤害免疫：毒素，心灵<br />状态免疫：魅惑，力竭，中毒，恐慌<br />感官能力：60尺黑暗视觉，被动感知10<br />语言能力：能听懂你所说的语言<br />挑战等级：舞空物品的熟练加值与你的等同<br />不变之形：该物品不会受到任何使它形态发生改变的法术或者其他效果的影响<br />难抑舞动：若一个生物在该舞空物品10尺内开始回合，那么他将可以增加或者减少10尺的步行移动力（由你来决定），直到他的下一个回合结束。舞空物品需要保持清醒来提供这一效果。<br />动作：力场猛击：近战武器攻击：使用你的法术攻击调整值，触及5尺，可以攻击你能看到的目标，造成1d10+熟练加值的力场伤害。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>在战斗中，该物品将会与你共用先攻，它会紧随在你的回合后行动。它可以自行移动并执行自己的反应，不过在它的回合它只会进行回避动作。除非使用附赠动作对它发出命令。他可以做其动作列表中的动作，当然你也可以命令它做其他事情。如果你的角色失能昏迷了，那么这件活化物品会做其他动作，不仅仅是回避动作。</p>\n<p>当你使用附赠动作发出诗人激励时，作为发出诗人激励的附赠动作的一部分，你同时也可以对这个活化物品发出指令。</p>\n<p>每当你用这一特性活化一件物品后，直到下一次长休结束前你都不能再次使用这个能力。你可以消耗一个3环或者更高级的法术位去重制这个能力的使用次数。你同时只能保持一件以此法被活化的物品。如果在你使用这个能力活化物品时已经有一件被活化的物品了，那么那个旧的物品会立刻停止不动，变回死物。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"object"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"创造学院等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"kFWjZzfEc2cVBPII","name":"潇洒气质 Panache","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003132.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         第9 级起，你变得更具魅力。你可以用一个动作进行一次魅力（游说）检定，以此对抗一个生物的感知（洞悉）检定。目标生物必须能听到你的声音，并且你们两个必须懂得同一门语言。</p>\n<p>         如果该生物对你敌对且你胜出对抗，则该生物对除你外其他目标发动攻击检定时具有劣势，且不能对除你外的目标发动借机攻击。该效应持续1分钟，你的队友对该目标发动攻击或以法术影响该目标，又或者你移动到远离目标 60 尺外时，该效应也将提前终止。</p>\n<p>         如果该生物对你非敌对且你胜出对抗，则该生物被你魅惑1 分钟。该生物被魅惑时会将你认作一个友好的熟人。该效应会在你或你的队友做出任何对目标的伤害后立即终止。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游荡剑客等级 9","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"kIUKnDJ9qdscR3zt","name":"猎人感知 Hunter's Sense","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Druid_PredatoryInstincts.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         3级起，你获得了观察生物并魔法性地分析出最佳狩猎方式的能力。以一个动作，选择一名60尺范围内对你可见的角色。你立刻知晓该角色的伤害免疫，抗性和易伤。如果该角色被预言系魔法覆盖，你感觉它没有任何伤害免疫，抗性和易伤。</p>\n<p>         你能使用该特性的次数等同于你的感知调整值（至少为1）。你重新获得所有使用过的次数当你完成一次长休时。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"max(@abilities.wis.mod,1)","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"怪物杀手等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"kQbdBnEVZWpyM4oT","name":"狂暴牵引 Violent Attraction","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003142.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         10级起，当一个除你以外，位于你60尺内且你可见的生物被武器攻击命中时，你能用你的反应加快这次攻击的速度，使得被攻击的目标额外受到[[/r 1d10]]的该武器类型所造成的伤害。</p>\n<p>          此外，如果一个位于你60尺内的生物遭受了坠落伤害，你能用你的反应来增加这次坠落所造成的伤害，增加值为[[/r 1d10]]。</p>\n<p>         你能使用本特性的次数等于你的智力调整值（最少一次）。当你完成一次长休后，你恢复所有的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EGtW","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"max(@abilities.int.mod,1)","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d10",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"重力魔法等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"kRh8aRVVJfLgEyHd","name":"书人合一 One With the Word","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/INV_Fabric_Netherweave_Bolt_Imbued.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>你和你的觉醒魔法书的联系已经变得如此深刻，以至于你的灵魂已经和它缠结在一起。携带这本书时，你在所有智力（奥秘）检定中具有优势，因为法术书能够帮助你记住魔法学识。</p>\n<p>此外，如果你在法术书的意识处于显现状态时受到伤害，你可以利用你的反应驱散灵体意识、利用其中的魔法来拯救自己，从而避免所有对你的伤害。之后，掷[[/r 3d6]]。法术书暂时失去由你自选的法术，其环阶之和必须大于或等于骰值。例如，如果骰值是9，则从书中消失的法术环阶之和至少为9——或许是一个9环法术，或是三个3环法术，或其他组合方式。如果书中没有足够的法术来支付这个代价，你就会降到0点生命。</p>\n<p>你必须完成[[/r 1d6]]次长休，才能再次施放失去的法术；在此期间，即使你在卷轴上或其他法术书中找到这些法术，也不能施展它们。完成所需的长休次数后，法术会重新出现在法术书中。</p>\n<p>用过这个反应之后，你必须完成一次长休才能再次使用。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"3d6","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"书士会等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
