{"_id":"kobL5XfjoDrnIupn","name":"守御之歌 Song of Defense","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Vehicle_ShellShieldGenerator.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        10级起，在剑歌激活期间，你可以导引你的魔法为你吸收伤害。当你受到伤害，你可以用你的反应动作消耗一个法术位，使你受到的伤害数值下降那个法术位环数的五倍。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"剑咏者等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"kpdFpp8QYwoOCnig","name":"防御者 Protector","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_PrayerOfFortitude.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>炮台释放出一股正能量，给予它自己和10尺距离内每个你选择的生物[[/r 1d8]]+你智力调整值的临时生命值（最低+1）。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"int","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+@mod","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魔炮师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"krzQeK2QuWmhc4C1","name":"心灵之刃 Psychic Blades","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_demonhunter_soulcleave.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         当你在3级加入低语学院时，你获得了让你的武器攻击毒害生物精神的魔法能力。</p>\n<p>         当你在一次武器攻击命中一个生物时，你可以消耗一次@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.FSr7TfaoWRPpUtkD]{诗人激励}的次数并对目标造成额外的[[/r 2d6]]点心灵伤害。你每轮在你的回合只能这样做一次。</p>\n<p>         额外的伤害将在你达到此职业的特定等级时得到提升，在5级时增加至[[/r 3d6]]、10级时[[/r 5d6]]、15级时[[/r 8d6]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(min((pow(floor(@classes.bard.levels/5+1),2)-floor(@classes.bard.levels/5+1))/2+2,8))d6","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"低语学院等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"kxT6i5CJyRj6PEdq","name":"救赎之誓 Oath of Redemption（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_DivineSpirit.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         救赎的誓言为圣武士提供了一条艰难的限制：不到最后关头就不能动用暴力。献身于救赎之誓的圣武士相信，任何人都可以得到救赎，仁慈与正义的路应当是所有人都可以走的。这些圣武士直面邪恶的生物，希望使他们弃暗投明，除非是为了在紧要关头救人，否则他们绝不会杀死自己的敌人。循此道者，便被称为救赎者。</p>\n<p>         救赎圣武士虽然可以说是理想主义者，但他们不是傻瓜。他们也明白不死生物、恶魔、魔鬼和其他一些超自然的威胁从本质上就是邪恶的。对于这些坚定不移的邪恶，遵循救赎之誓的圣武士随时准备用武器和法术来击垮他们。然而尽管如此，救赎圣武士也在心底祈祷着，总有一天，即使是如此的邪恶也能够自我救赎。</p>\n<h3><strong>救赎之信条</strong></h3>\n<p>         救赎之誓的信条要求圣武士高标准地保持和平与正义。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>和平：</strong>暴力是最后的手段，交流和理解才是持久和平的正解。</li>\n<li><strong>无辜：</strong>所有人生来都是无辜的，他们走向邪恶往往是环境或某些黑暗力量的影响。通过树立正确的榜样，治愈这个残缺世界的创伤，你可以令任何人走上正确的道路。</li>\n<li><strong>耐心：</strong>改变需要时间。犯下罪行的人必须被诚实与正义时刻提醒。一旦你播下正义的种子，你就必须日复一日地为其努力，直到最终开花结果。</li>\n<li><strong>睿智：</strong>你的心灵必须时刻保持清醒，而你最终也许会被迫承认失败。既然所有人都可以得到救赎，那么自然也会有人选择步入邪恶之巅。你别无选择，为了大义只能将其剿灭。任何这样的行动都应当经过仔细权衡并考虑清楚其后果，但你一旦做出决定，那么就做到最后。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>圣誓法术Oath Spells</strong></p>\n<p><em>你获得以下圣誓法术。</em></p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>圣骑士等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>3rd</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.FbxdKcDpSPWuGTLA]{庇护术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.hFHF7vm3FYyTN288]{睡眠术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>5th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.6MYwBtZurc8Zw1ac]{安定心神}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.syHHJlRPS4rVwCQA]{人类定身术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>9th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.895yeeloz2EhpEYC]{法术反制}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.BbpCbjCXt14a08Jp]{催眠图纹}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>13th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.cdeQPacCcm540OPy]{欧提路克弹力法球}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.8xmyW0Ynz0z7Kt3X]{石肤术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>17th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.abm5MgV3kejSatZt]{怪物定身术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.31jKHMGJ0vlqdvQU]{力场墙}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"圣武士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ky0dMTWSMVEztfGF","name":"救赎使节 Emissary of Redemption","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_DevineAegis.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在20级时，你成为了和平的化身，使你获得下述好处：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你对于其他生物造成的所有伤害具有抗性（它们的攻击、法术、和其他效果）。</li>\n<li>当一个生物以一次攻击对你造成伤害时，它受到等同于其对你造成的一半伤害的光耀伤害。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>         当你对一个生物攻击、施法或以此特性以外的方式造成伤害，那么在完成一次长休之前此特性对该生物无效。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"救赎之誓等级 20","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"l17hcUnMwg8jKByw","name":"崇高卫士 Exalted Champion","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_Conviction.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从20级起，对于那些献身于你所遵从的事业的人而言，你已经成为了一个鼓舞人心的完美典范。你可以用一个动作在接下来1个小时里得到如下好处：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你对非魔法武器所造成的钝击、穿刺、挥砍伤害具有抗性。</li>\n<li>在你30尺距离内的盟友在进行死亡豁免时具有优势。</li>\n<li>你和你30尺距离内的盟友在感知豁免上具有优势。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果你死亡或者进入失能状态，这个效果将提前结束。一旦你使用了这个能力，在你完成一次长休之前你不能再次使用。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"王冠之誓等级 20","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"Qt0n5FAwhS7O9Esf","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"physical"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_Conviction.png","label":"获得非魔法的钝击、刺穿、挥砍抗性","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.l17hcUnMwg8jKByw","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"l4lNH8vyG9P8hyPv","name":"超魔法：转化法术 Metamagic ： Transmuted Spell","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/emerald_09.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你施放一个能够造成以下列表中类型伤害的法术时，你可以使用1术法点将其改为列表中的另一种伤害类型：强酸、冷冻、火焰、闪电、毒素或雷鸣。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":"1 术法点。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"术士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"l8mUJYR3y1TSV5hk","name":"魔法物品专家 Magic Item Savant","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_FlashHeal.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         当你达到14级时，你在魔法物品方面的技巧愈发精进：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你一次最多可以同调五个魔法物品。</li>\n<li>你无视同调或使用魔法物品所需的任何职业、种族、法术和等级条件。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奇械师等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lFSt9wCshR8yCdUK","name":"序列意识 Trance of Order","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_broker_orb.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>14级起，你获得了将你的意识和机械境无尽的计算达成同步的能力。以一个附赠动作，你可以在1分钟内进入此种状态。在此期间，对你进行的攻击免受优势的影响，且每当你进行一次攻击检定、属性检定或豁免检定时，你可以将[[/r d20]]掷出的9或以下的数值视为10。</p>\n<p>一旦你使用了此能力，你在完成一次长休之前必须消耗5术法点以再次使用此能力。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"时械之魂等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lG7lOXsvmj7RXhkk","name":"星我之躯 Body of the Astral Self","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_bastion_monk.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你同时召唤@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.Qctmiuim4M9SfU1E]{星我之臂}和@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.vimr3VI7xsnK1ydv]{星我之容}时，你可以让你的星我之躯出现（不需要任何动作），这个幽光般的躯体如同一件盔甲般复盖着你的身体，与星我之臂和星我之容相连。你来决定它的外观。</p>\n<p>当星我之躯出现时，你将获得如下增益：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>拨挡能量</strong>。当你受到强酸、冷冻、火焰、力场、闪电或雷鸣伤害时，你可以用你的反应来偏转它，如果你这么做，则你所受的该次伤害减少[[/r 1D10]]+你的感知调整值（最小减少1）。</li>\n<li><strong>注能之臂</strong>。你的每回合中有一次机会，当你用星我之臂攻击命中目标时，你可以对目标造成额外伤害，相当于你的武艺骰。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["d(ceil(((@classes.monk.levels)+2)/6)*2+2)","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"max(1d10 + @abilities.wis.mod,1)","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"星我宗等级 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lMZsBil8DAG3LAHx","name":"无常反冲 Unstable Backlash","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Sha_ability_rogue_sturdyrecuperate.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在你@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.gLNFWGL05O0FUNTD]{狂暴}期间，如果你受到危险，你体内的魔法会猛烈爆发。每当你在狂暴时受到伤害或者没能通过豁免检定，你可以消耗一次反应动作再次触发狂野魔法浪涌，重新掷骰子并根据@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.qzKSooNxo2zww1oE]{狂野魔法列表}立刻产生一次新的魔法效果。这个魔法效果将会替代你当前拥有的狂野魔法效果。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"狂野魔法道途等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lNNvzg84YQ103b2W","name":"狂热专注 Zealous Focus","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_PureOfHeart.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在6级时，驱使你愤怒的神力也能庇护你免遭损害。若你在@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.gLNFWGL05O0FUNTD]{狂暴}时未通过一次豁免检定，你可以重新投掷该豁免检定，但你必须接受第二次投掷的数值。你每次狂暴只能使用此能力一次。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"狂热者等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lQSmrRreRFq0Q3aO","name":"先祖复仇 Vengeful Ancestors","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Priest_ReflectiveShield.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在14级时，你的先祖之魂变得强大到足以打击伤害你所保护之人的敌人。当你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.H5J2aANa4OhuuPmv]{精魂之盾}保护生物、降低一次攻击的伤害时，攻击者受到精魂之盾所降低的等量力场伤害。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(min((floor(@classes.barbarian.levels+2)/4),4))d6","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"先祖守卫等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lRPmBxHLeaBTnDC0","name":"扩散孢子 Spreading Spores","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_Shaman_convection.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在10级时，你获得了在一片区域内散布致命的孢子的能力。当你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.RakISgKJ0fWy44XM]{一体共生}特性处于开启状态下，你可以用一个附赠动作，将真菌孢子抛向至多30尺外，它们将漂浮在那里10尺见方的空间中，持续1分钟。若你再次使用此特性，或使用一个附赠动作取消掉，或你的一体共生特性不再起作用，这片孢子将提前消失。</p>\n<p>         任何在此空间内开始其回合的生物受到你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.XvZtgLjExeMcMxrd]{孢子光晕}伤害，除非其通过一个等同于你法术DC的体质豁免，一个生物每轮只能受到一次该伤害。<br />         只要这片孢子存在，你就不能使用你孢子光晕的反应动作。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GGR","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":10,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"孢子结社等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lWw9NHXiINtblmGx","name":"阳光箭 Radiant Sun Bolt","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Priest_Flashoflight.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从3级起，选择了这个范型的武僧可以投掷出灼热的箭矢。</p>\n<p>你可以在攻击动作中使用一种特殊的远程法术攻击（射程30尺）。你熟练于这次攻击，并且可以在攻击和伤害骰上加上敏捷调整值。它造成光耀伤害，伤害骰为[[/r 1d4]]。伤害骰会随着你的等级增长而改变，参考@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-table.mslFlzSOAGX87lXV]{武僧表}中的武艺栏。</p>\n<p>如果你在自己的回合内用攻击动作使用这种特殊攻击，你可以花费1点气，并且再用附赠动作用阳光箭进行两次额外的攻击。</p>\n<p>当你得到额外攻击能力时，你可以在作为攻击动作一部分的任意某次攻击中使用这种特殊攻击。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"dex","actionType":"rsak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d((floor((@classes.monk.levels+1)/6))*2+4)+@mod +",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"日魂宗等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lZRcPfZbmiHnYmTq","name":"狩猎呼唤 Call The Hunt","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ABILITY_HUNTER_BESTIALDISCIPLINE.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你内在的野兽已经成长的如此强大，你可以把你的其狂暴的战意散播到他人身上，并且这些加入你狩猎的人也会让你更加的强韧。当你进入@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.gLNFWGL05O0FUNTD]{狂暴}时，你可以选择你视野中，30尺以内，一定数量的（小于等于你的体质调整值，大于等于1），自愿接受该特性的生物。每个加入你狩猎的生物会给你5临时生命值。直到你的狂暴终止前，加入你狩猎的生物每回合一次进行攻击检定并造成伤害时，可以增加一个[[/r d6]]的伤害骰子。</p>\n<p>你每天可以使用该能力的次数等于你的熟练加值。每完成一次长休之后你补充齐所有已消耗的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":5,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["d6",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"野兽道途等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"leabhG1wc0d4vP8C","name":"欺诈箭 Beguiling Arrow","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_ImprovedSteadyShot.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你的附魔魔法会让箭暂时欺骗目标。被这发箭击中的角色会额外受到[[/r 2d6]]的心灵伤害，而且选择距离目标30尺内的一名队友。目标必须成功通过一个感知豁免，或者被选择的队友魅惑直到你的下一个回合开始。这个效果会在所选的盟友攻击被魅惑目标、对目标造成伤害、或强迫它进行豁免检定时提早结束。</p>\n<p>         当你的战士等级到18级时该心灵伤害增加到[[/r 4d6]]</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(ceil(@classes.fighter.levels/17)*2)d6","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"int"},"requirements":"魔射手等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"loa1FeErjePHZ0VG","name":"顽强精神 Unyielding Spirit","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/1ability_toughness%20.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从15级起，你在避免陷入震慑或者麻痹状态的豁免骰中得到优势。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"王冠之誓等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lpXTu82vnVcwUUIH","name":"炽烈回生 Blazing Revival","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Mage_FieryPayback.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>你与野火精魂的连接可以使你免于死亡。</p>\n<p>当你生命值降至 0 从而昏迷时，如果精魂在你的 120 尺内，你可以使精魂降至 0 生命值。之后你就会恢复一半生命值，并立刻站起来。</p>\n<p>一旦你使用这一特性，直到你结束一次长休前你不能再次使用。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":"生命值降至 0 从而昏迷时；精魂在 120 尺内。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"野火结社 Lv.14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lu8NYi2MWNx8h6ZX","name":"生死之触Physician’s Touch","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Mage_IncantersAbsorbtion.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以通过接触来进行更有效的治疗，你也可以利用你的知识来造成伤害。</p>\n<p>当你对一个生物使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.R9VbDJOCQk2Mb9eG]{予命之手}时，你还可以结束一种疾病或影响该生物的下列状态之一：目盲、耳聋、麻痹、中毒或震慑。</p>\n<p>当你对一个生物使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.bolUalIQ1Ad2I6Mg]{夺命之手}时，你可以使该生物处于中毒状态，直到你的下一回合结束。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"命流宗等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lvgd0LAWO41fbYRk","name":"追猎如风 Stalker's Flurry","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003279.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         11级时，你学会以出人意料的速度来发动攻击以至于你能够将一次失手转化为另一次攻击。你的每个回合一次，当你的一次武器攻击未命中时，你可以做出另一次武器攻击作为同一动作的一部分。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"幽域追踪者等级 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"m4xHGaSl3IeNSUQM","name":"畸变心智 Aberrant Mind（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_priest_shadow-mend.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>某种外来的影响曾经用它的卷须将你的意识缠绕裹拢，给予了你灵能之力。如今，你能够使用这股力量触碰他人的内心，或是用它操控多元宇宙的魔法能量颠复你周遭的世界。这种力量会从你身上如希望的灯塔一般照耀着旁人吗？抑或是使你成为恐惧之源，使他人得见你怪异的力量，受你的心灵所伤害呢？</p>\n<h3><strong>异常起源</strong></h3>\n<p>作为一名畸变心智术士，你能决定如何获得你的能力。这是你与生俱来的吗？还是后来发生的某件事使你展现出卓越的灵能？参考异常起源表以了解你可能的力量来源。</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>[[/r d6]]</th>\n<th>起源</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>你曾暴露在遥远国度扭曲的影响之下。你坚信着有触须在你身上生长，但其他人都看不到。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>一阵来自星界的灵能之风将心灵异能灌入你的体内。现在，当你使用这股力量时，你的身边会有微弱的光点闪烁。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>你曾受到底栖魔鱼的支配，它的力量在你的脑海中留下了一个精神碎片。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>你被植入了一只夺心魔蝌蚪，但蜕变一直没能完成。现在，其灵能力已经被你占为已有。当你使用灵能时，你的身体里会冒出奇怪的粘液。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>小时候，你有一个想象中的朋友，它看上去像是呋噜或是一只奇怪的鸭嘴兽形生物。某天，它赠与你灵能的力量，但它最终不再止步于想象。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>你的噩梦向你透露了真相：你的灵能不是来源于自身，而是从你未能成功出世的孪生兄弟/姐妹处抽取来的！</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3><strong>灵能法术</strong></h3>\n<p>当你升至相应的术士等级时，你习得下表中的额外法术。这些法术对你而言视为术士法术，且不受术士表上已知法术一栏的数量限制。</p>\n<p>每当你提升术士等级时，你可以选择一个等级相同的新法术来替换你因此特性习得的一个法术。该法术必须为术士、邪术师或法师法术列表中的一个预言系或惑控系法术。</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Eodwq0Zfd8ecEhdy]{哈达之臂}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.j8wwbcc1tlY9hLRf]{不谐低语}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Il0iA9nttKqh0ACr]{心灵之楔*}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.6MYwBtZurc8Zw1ac]{安定心神}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.YuGbz9k5JXA0kIgT]{侦测思想}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.eT0LfvbxuKfMuRbs]{哈达之欲}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.kRO1zjPXuOLm4qUU]{短讯术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.JMAmXdzvxTU27pP2]{艾伐黑触手}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.kkahnA5EClqV0LWA]{异怪召唤术*}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.mdnvLsKRorF3cx5S]{拉瑞心灵联结}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.MTNfEcCXSJZ2m2nG]{心灵遥控}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"术士等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"m58A5U9dXzc4PTBY","name":"幽暗之瞳 Eyes of the Dark","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Shadow_Charm.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>1级起你获得120尺黑暗视觉。</p>\n<p>当你在该职业3级时，你掌握了@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.UyQ9nYcQlFdEbmeV]{黑暗术}，这不会占用你术士已知法术数量。你可以用2点术法点或1个法术位来释放。当你用法术点施法时，你能够看穿该法术所制造的黑暗。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"幽影魔法等级 1，3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"uF41QTJnFhd2gdsr","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.senses.darkvision","mode":4,"value":"120"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Shadow_Charm.png","label":"获得 120 尺黑暗视觉","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.m58A5U9dXzc4PTBY","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"m9IA0eF0U0iEV2cv","name":"阴暗学识 Shadow Lore","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_BeastWithin.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         14级时，你学会了在言语中织入黑暗魔法激发一个生物最深的恐惧。</p>\n<p>         以一个动作，你对一个30尺内，能听见你的声音的生物发出一段魔法的低语。目标必须进行一次感知豁免检定，对抗你的法术豁免DC。若它与你没有共通的语言，或是它不能听见你的声音，它会自动在豁免中成功。在一次成功的豁免检定中，你的低语声听起来就像是不知所云的呢喃，并且没有效果。</p>\n<p>         若目标在豁免检定中失败，他将在接下来的8小时内被你魅惑，或直到你或你的盟友攻击了它、伤害了它，或是迫使它进行一次豁免检定。他认为这段低语描述了他最为困窘的秘密。尽管你不会了解到这个秘密，目标坚信你已经知道了。</p>\n<p>         当被以此法魅惑时，该生物因为畏惧你会公开他的秘密而遵循你的命令。他不会为了你让自己的生命受到威胁，或是为你战斗，除非他已经这么做。他偏向于你，并会像密友那样提供关爱和恩惠。</p>\n<p>         当此效果结束时，该生物不会明白为什么他会对你如此恐惧。</p>\n<p>         一旦你使用了此特性，直到你完成了一次长休前，你都不能再次使用它。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":8,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"低语学院等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mHDQAyXiAgvAldGc","name":"灵魂之刃：心灵传送 Soul Blades：Psychic Teleportation","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_bastion_monk1.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.yeqpLzvtDcAw6UBm]{念刃}现在成为了你那充盈灵能之灵魂的具现，这使你能够通过以下的方式更好地控制它：</p>\n<p>如果你的灵能天赋骰可用，你能通过投掷念刃来将自己魔法性地传送到其他地方。以一个附赠动作，你塑造一把念刃，消耗并掷一个灵能骰，将念刃投掷到至多距离灵能骰结果数字10倍尺数的可见空闲区域。你传送到目标位置，同时念刃消失。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"(d(floor((1+@classes.rogue.levels)/6)*2+6))*10","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魂刃等级 9","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mWchknyJMnozqbPO","name":"法师之笔 Wizardly Quill","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/inv_enchanting_70_pet_pen.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>以一个附赠动作，你能用魔法创造一支微型羽毛笔。这支魔法羽毛笔具有以下特性：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>这支毛笔不需要墨水。当你用它书写时，它会在用于书写的表面上自行生成墨水，颜色由你选择。</li>\n<li>若你使用这根羽毛笔来将法术抄入法术书，你只需花费每个法术等级2分钟的时间。</li>\n<li>若你用羽毛笔书写的文本在你身边5尺范围之内，你可以用一个附赠动作在文字上方晃动羽毛将其消除。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>这根羽毛笔将在你创造另一支笔或是死亡时消失。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"书士会等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mX6HNUMT8cphwRpE","name":"不朽之理 Undying Nature","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_DeathKnight_SoulReaper.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从10级起，你可以无限制地屏住呼吸，并且你不再需要食物、水和睡眠，虽然你仍旧需要休息来恢复疲惫并且从长/短休中获得收益。<br />        并且，你的年龄增长速度被放慢。每过去10年，你的身体只会衰老1年，并且你免疫魔法衰老。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"不朽者等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mZOKmbkP6wKtkH3r","name":"精魂图腾 Spirit Totem","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/000516.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         2级起，你获得了招现出自然精魂并借助它们影响你身边的世界的能力。以一个附赠动作，你可以魔法般地召唤一个虚体的精魂，到处于你周围60尺内、你能看到的一点处。此精魂创造出一道环绕该点的、30尺半径的光环。精魂不算作是生物，也不算作是物体，尽管它有着符合对应生物的幽魂般的外表。</p>\n<p>         以一个附赠动作，你可以移动此精魂至多60尺，到你能看到的一点处。</p>\n<p>         此精魂持续1分钟或直到你失能。一旦你使用了此特性，你无法再次使用它，直到你完成一次短休或长休为止。</p>\n<p>         此精魂的光环效果基于你召唤的精魂的类别，如下面的选项所示。</p>\n<p>         <strong>熊精魂</strong>：熊精魂授予你和你的伙伴它的力量和坚韧。在精魂出现时，每个处于此光环中、由你选择的生物，获得等于5+你的德鲁伊等级的临时生命值。此外，你和你的盟友在处于光环内时，在力量检定和力量豁免检定中获得优势。</p>\n<p>         <strong>鹰精魂</strong>： 鹰精魂是技艺精湛的猎手，用它敏锐的视力标记你的敌人。当一个生物对一个处于此精魂光环内的目标进行一次攻击检定时，你可以使用你的反应让这次攻击检定获得优势。此外，在光环内你和你的盟友得到感知（观察）检定的优势。</p>\n<p>          <strong>独角兽精魂</strong>：独角兽精魂为周围提供保护。你和你的盟友在用于侦测在此精魂光环内的生物所进行的所有属性检定中获得优势。此外，若你以一个法术位施展了一个为任何处于或不处于光环内的人恢复生命值的法术，每个处于光环内、由你选择的生物也恢复等于你德鲁伊等级的生命值。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"牧人之环等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mcEDXVrFUr2b0C4P","name":"战狂道途 Path of The Battlerager（SCAG）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_Dungeon_BlackrockCaverns_AscendantLordObsidius.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<h3><strong>限制：限定矮人</strong></h3>\n<p>只有矮人才可以选择战狂道途。在矮人的社会和文化中战狂占据了一个特殊的位置。</p>\n<p>你的DM可以调整这一规则使之更符合战役。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>        战狂道途通常被那些选择追随战争之神的矮人选择，在矮人语中他们被称作为“库扎尔夫”（意指“斧头笨蛋”）。他们常穿着厚重的、带刺的盔甲冲入战场，用他们自己的身体在战斗中挥洒怒火。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"矮人且野蛮人等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mu9IA3SphVBRiv63","name":"钢铁守卫 Steel Defender","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_siege_engineer_death_from_above.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在第3级，你闲暇的工匠时间让你创造出可靠的随从，一个钢铁守卫。它对你和你的同伴友好，并且服从你的命令。钢铁守卫的游戏数据见下。该生物的外观，两足步行还是四足步行皆由你决定；你的决定对游戏数据没有影响。</p>\n<p>         在战斗中，钢铁守卫使用你的先攻，并且在你的回合后立即行动。它能自由移动和执行反应，但除非你以一个附赠动作命令它进行数据中列出的动作或疾行、撤离、协力、躲藏、搜索动作，否则它在回合中只能进行闪避动作。</p>\n<p>         如果你对钢铁守卫施放@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.2LREP2D10afC4Y3V]{修复术}，它将恢复[[/r 2d6]]生命值。如果它在最近一小时内死亡，你能够以一个动作使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.B97AB85722BCF651]{铁匠工具}花费一个至少1环的法术位来在距离你5尺的空格内复活它。钢铁守卫会在1分钟后复活，在复活时会回满生命值。</p>\n<p>         当你在手头有铁匠工具的情况下完成一次长休时，你可以创造一个新的钢铁守卫。如果你已经通过此特性拥有一个钢铁守卫，则上一个会立即消失。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战地匠师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mvf3Cptm6e0BPxlP","name":"皇家特使 Royal Envoy","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_BG_trueAVshutout.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        从7级起，你熟练于游说技能。如果你已经对这项技能熟练，你可以选择以下列表中的一项技能熟练：驯兽，洞悉，威吓，表演。<br />        你在进行魅力（游说）检定时可以将双倍的熟练值加在上面。你始终获得这个好处，不管你是否从这个能力中得到了对于游说技能的熟练。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"紫龙骑士等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"B9LArZFxu0Y5UxO5","changes":[{"key":"data.skills.per.value","mode":4,"value":"1"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_BG_trueAVshutout.png","label":"获得游说熟练","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.mvf3Cptm6e0BPxlP","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"nLlDb604g3coSoQ4","name":"梦境之环 Circle of Dreams（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Druid_Flourish.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>梦境之环的德鲁伊们通常来自与妖精荒野有着很强联系的地区。他们与善良阵营的妖精组成了联盟共通守卫自然世界。这些德鲁伊追求光明和欢乐，并希望它们充满这个世界。他们的魔法能抚平创伤，为沮丧的人带来欢笑；他们守护的土地永远熠熠发光，丰硕富饶，在那里梦境和现实的边界变得模糊，任何疲惫的人都能找到休憩的场所。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"德鲁伊等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"nPHVVZk27pA42YF0","name":"权威之音 Voice of Authority","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Paladin_templarsverdict.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从 1 级起，你可以调用律法的力量来驱使一位盟友进攻。如果你施展了一个一环或高于一环并目标是一位盟友的法术，那位盟友可以在法术后立即使用她们的反应来对你指定且能看见的一名目标进行一次武器攻击。</p>\n<p>        如果法术指定了超过一名盟友，则由你来选择发动攻击的盟友。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GGR","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"秩序领域等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"nQnwOjutRDrXuq8v","name":"怪物杀手 Monster Slayer（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Druid_Mangle.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你专注于猎杀那些黑夜中的怪物和邪恶魔法的使用者。怪物杀手会找出吸血鬼，龙，邪恶精灵，魔裔以及其他魔法威胁。为了训练出高超技巧来击败这些怪物，怪物杀手精通于找出并击败那些强大且神秘的敌人。</p>\n<h3><strong>怪物杀手魔法</strong></h3>\n<p>         3级起，当你到达指定游侠等级时你学会一个额外法术，如怪物杀手法术列表所示。这些法术对你视为游侠法术，它不计入你的已知法术总数中。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>职业等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.IuzXxwP3EhWGhtXC]{防护善恶}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.T4zFq0zTHnzZeO9t]{诚实之域}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Vrzu8xpLMvOvOnx6]{防护法阵}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.lopw7wVkPoE7gbNu]{放逐术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.abm5MgV3kejSatZt]{怪物定身术}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游侠等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"name":"回力武器","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2>回力武器</h2>\n<p><em>物品：一把带有投掷属性的简易或军用武器</span></em><br></span>　　该魔法武器在攻击和伤害检定中具有</span>+1</span>加值，在使用它进行远程攻击后，它会立即回到持有者的手中。</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_monk_roll.png","_id":"nTzVQzQGCnGoQRKH"}
{"_id":"nVVkNjWXJYpSgNHB","name":"奥法火器 Arcane Firearm","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Fire_SearingTotem.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在第5级，你知道如何把魔杖、法杖或权杖变成一件奥法火器，一个传送你的毁灭性法术的管道。当你完成一次长休后，你可以用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.A4B41FB9DAE8B865]{木匠工具}在一根魔杖、法杖或权杖上刻印一个特殊印记，从而把它变成你的奥法火器。印记会一直存在，除非你之后在另一件物品上刻上这种印记，这样的话，之前物体上印记就会消失。</p>\n<p>         你可以将你的奥法火器作为你奇械师法术的法器。当你通过奥法火器施放一个奇械师法术时，掷一个[[/r d8]]，你在法术的一次伤害检定中获得与掷骰结果相同的加值。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d8",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魔炮师等级 5","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"nXNzOQmtv0e6egnX","name":"战斗风格：投掷武器战斗","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/mech_15.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>        </strong>你可以在使用一件带有投掷属性武器进行进攻时，将那件武器作为攻击的一部分而拔出。另外，在你以一件投掷武器于远程攻击中命中对手时，你的伤害掷骰+2。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":"","long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"战士等级 1，勇士等级 10，游侠等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"nkWhDnMPtZYewwyF","name":"魔法指引Magical Guidance","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Mage_MissileBarrage.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你能够挖掘内在的魔力源泉，从失败中召唤成功。当你进行一次属性检定并失败时，你可以使用1术法点重投之。你必须使用重投的结果。此举可能使该检定改为成功。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"术士等级 5","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"nkp511Gfd16b3d2g","name":"魔能祈唤：魔能意志Eldritch Invocation：Eldritch Mind","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/red_01.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>你在保持专注的体质豁免检定上有优势，可以让你维持对某个法术的专注。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"邪术师等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"noPzCDRAbqNUFwC7","name":"雄辩学院 College of Eloquence（MOT）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_DivineHymn.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         雄辩学院的追随者们掌握辩论的艺术。游说被认为是一种高等的艺术，一个经过充分论证、口齿伶俐的论点往往比事实更具说服力。这些吟游诗人将逻辑和戏剧性的语言结合在一起，运用逻辑论证战胜怀疑者与批评者，同时拨动观众的心弦并引领他们的情绪。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MOT","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"吟游诗人等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"noTXi9zM4UR6s18f","name":"回收潜能 Reclaim Potential","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_Invisibilty.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从15级起，你已经学会吸收你回音上转瞬即逝的魔力。当你的一个回音因承受伤害而被摧毁，而你也没有临时生命值时，你获得相当于[[/r 2d6]]+体质调整值点数的临时生命值。<br />        你能使用本特性的次数等于你的体质调整值（最少一次）。当你完成一次长休后，你恢复所有的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EGtW","activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"max(@abilities.con.mod,1)","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d6+@abilities.con.mod","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"回音骑士等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"nuM7CwcvvLx2uQaO","name":"醉拳法门 Drunken Technique","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_Invisibilty.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你3级时，选择了这个范型的武僧使得你学会了如何在疾风连打中快速的扭转与行动躯体。每当你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.vLuoFN1x3tRWTPdm]{疾风连击}时，你将获得撤离动作的好处，而你的步行速度增加 10 尺直到当前回合结束。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"醉拳宗等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"CSt6BEGVerNp2sIr","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.movement.walk","mode":2,"value":"10"}],"disabled":true,"duration":{"startTime":null,"turns":1},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_Invisibilty.png","label":"增加 10 尺步行速度","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.nuM7CwcvvLx2uQaO","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"name":"斥力之盾","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2>斥力之盾</h2>\n        <p><em>先决条件；</span></em><em>6</span></em><em>级奇械师</span></em><em><br></span></em><em>物品：一个盾牌（需调谐）</span></em><br></span>　　持握该盾牌的生物</span>AC</span>获得</span>+1</span>加值</span><br></span>　　该盾牌有</span>4</span>发充能，当持用者被近战攻击命中时，以一个反应消耗一发充能，其可以将攻击者击退至多</span>15</span>尺远。该盾牌在次日黎明时会恢复</span>1d4</span>发充能。</span><br></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Warrior_ShieldReflection.png","_id":"o71qOD8b8xxWoD7i"}
{"_id":"oGTDEbOPlsTke4PS","name":"称手工具 The Right Tool For The Job","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpcloud3steamusercontentcomugc842586004367101824420E371B2A511858B3A2D378EE560C835BA09747.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>          在第3级，你将学习如何精确地制作你所需要的工具：使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.E20CE7D30DE58B23]{修理工具}，你可以在离你5尺内的未占据空间中魔法性地制作出一套工匠工具。这一制造需要1小时不间断的工作，可以在短休或长休的过程中进行。这套工具是魔法的产物，但其本身是非魔法的，当你再次使用此特性时，之前制造的工具就会消失。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"hour","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奇械师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"oHj6AFAm66d9qYd7","name":"引导神力：和平抚慰 Balm of Peace","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/005210.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>你可以用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.WPevnsjK8Cjd9Fcl]{引导神力}来减轻痛苦，慰籍心灵。以一个动作，你可以移动等同于你速度的距离，此次移动不会引发借机攻击。当你在此动作期间移动到了任何其他生物5尺内时，你可以恢复其[[/r 2d6]]+你的感知调整值（最低1）的生命值。你采取此动作时，一个生物只能被治疗一次。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d6+max((@abilities.wis.mod),1)","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"和平领域等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"oYxStwPYwZvJAczj","name":"狂野魔法道途 Path of Wild Magic（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/sha_spell_shaman_lavaburst_nightborne.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>这个多元宇宙的许多地方充满了美丽，强烈的情感，以及狂野而难以控制的魔力。妖精荒野，上层位面，以及其他辐射着超自然力量的领域都以这股力量深深的影响着人们。我们情感丰富而激烈的老伙计们——野蛮人尤其容易受这些狂野的扰动影响。其中又一些人接受了狂野魔法的浸洗而转变，变形。这些被魔力染上一抹亮色的野蛮人所走的，便是狂野魔法道途。精类，提夫林，阿斯莫和元素裔的野蛮人中不乏选择狂野魔法道途的，希求显耀他们先祖的那不属于这个世界的魔力。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"野蛮人等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ocvcBCV6uWcdfnIu","name":"绝对统御 Unbreakable Majesty","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpcloud3steamusercontentcomugc84258513611610574219070A1F97FB9AB9097E2A1CE5DF05A9FDC769ED.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         14级时，你的容貌变得更加脱俗，这让你的美更加漂亮且强烈。</p>\n<p>         此外，一个附赠动作，你展现魔法的壮美仪度直至1分钟或你失能，期间任何生物在每回合第一次试图对你进行攻击时都必须要进行一次魅力豁免检定对抗你的法术豁免DC。若失败，则该生物不能在这个回合内攻击你，且必须要选定一个新的目标，否则就要失去本次的攻击。若这回合豁免检定成功，该生物能够攻击你，但在对抗你的下个回合施展的法术时在所有豁免检定中具有劣势。</p>\n<p>         一旦你使用此特性，直到你完成了一次短休或长休前，你都不能再次使用它。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"cha","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"迷惑学院等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"odSeRNvb2P8PIUOp","name":"引导神力:恐怖显现 Dreadful Aspect","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Arcane_StarFire.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         作为一个动作项，该圣骑士引导最黑暗的情感并将其凝聚爆发为一场魔法的胁迫之息。该圣骑士周边 30尺内，其指定的每个能看到该圣武士的生物必须进行一次感知豁免。豁免失败的目标将陷入 1分钟对该 圣武士恐慌的状态。因该效应陷入恐慌的生物如果在距离该圣武士 30尺外的位置结束其自己回合，则其可以尝试再进行一次该感知豁免，豁免成功则终止其自己身上的该效应。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"破誓者等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ojRsd7cWm1eb2SkQ","name":"斥候 Scout（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Stealth.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你擅长在远离城市和街道的地方潜行和生存，这让你在探险中能离开你的同伴带头侦查。这一泛型的斥候许多都以荒野为家，与野蛮人和游侠同行，也有许多斥候充当着战争地带的眼睛和耳朵。伏击兵，间谍，赏金猎人。这些只是斥候在世界范围内所扮演的少数角色。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游荡者等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"p3ygdJ5jnwNfzLQL","name":"神圣打击（秩序） Divine Strike","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_AvengineWrath.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从 8 级起，你可以使你的武器充满神圣能量。你的每回合一次，在用一次武器攻击命中某一名生物时，你可以使该攻击造成额外的[[/r 1d8]] 心灵伤害。当你达到 14 级时，该伤害提升到[[/r 2d8]] 。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GGR","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(min(max(floor(((@classes.cleric.levels)-2)/6),1),2))d8","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"秩序领域等级 8","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"p7OsDJ8ZBJvkvkTs","name":"午夜飞步 Steps of Night","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Fire_BurningSpeed1.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你使用夜晚的神秘力量来飞上空中。当你处于微光光照或黑暗时，你能以一个附赠动作用魔法使自己获得等于自身步行速度的飞行速度，持续1分钟。你可以使用此特性的次数等同于你的熟练加值，当你完成一次长休时恢复所有使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"暮光领域等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pAZgHzJITmplpYbQ","name":"光辉护盾 Sun Shield","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_AuraMastery.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从17级起，武僧可以完全将自己包覆在魔法性的强光之中。</p>\n<p>你发散出30尺的明亮照明和额外30尺的昏暗照明。你可以以一个附赠动作将这个光芒熄灭或者恢复。</p>\n<p>如果一个被光芒照耀的生物对你进行近战攻击并击中了你，你可以用你的反应对这个生物造成5+你的感知调整值的光耀伤害。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["5 +@abilities.wis.mod","radiant"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"日魂宗等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pJzyebuSKqOCNpAN","name":"狂热存在 Zealous Presence","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_Crusade.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在10级时，你学会了引导神力，让其他人也被狂热所感染。以一个附赠动作，你愤怒的怒吼并释放出一道蕴含神圣能量的战吼。选择至多10个距离你60尺以内并且能听到你吼叫的其他生物（不包括你自己），直到你的下个回合开始，在攻击检定和豁免检定中获得优势。</p>\n<p>一旦你使用了此特性，你不能再次使用它，直到你完成了一次长休。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":10,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"狂热者等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pLTSRjy7SLsMcuhm","name":"光耀之魂 Radiant Soul","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_Fanaticism.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从6级开始，你所连接的天界宗主允许你成为光耀能量释放的渠道。你获得对光耀伤害的抗性，当你施展一个造成光耀或火焰伤害的法术时，你可以将你的魅力调整值加到法术对其中一个目标造成的一次光耀或火焰伤害骰上。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"天界宗主等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"VMMYc83NjapCkaEc","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"radiant"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_Fanaticism.png","label":"获得光耀抗性","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.pLTSRjy7SLsMcuhm","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pU6qJVr775dkEIwk","name":"阴影殉道者 Shadow Martyr","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_Displacement.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从10级起，在一个除你以外的，且你可见的生物受到攻击前，你能让你的回音冲向该生物。在攻击检定投掷前，你能用你的反应动作来传送回音到目标生物周围5尺内，尚未被占据的空间。触发该反应的攻击检定将由你的回音代为承受。<br />         一旦你使用本特性，直到你完成一次短休或长休前，你不能再次使用。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EGtW","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"回音骑士等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pe25DA4ut0EIbs7s","name":"闪现打击 Distant Strike","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/002503.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在11级时，你能够在眨眼之间穿梭于两个位置。当你进行攻击动作时，你能够在每一次攻击前传送10尺到一片对你可见的空地上。</p>\n<p>         如果你用一个动作攻击了至少两名不同的角色，你可以额外攻击一次第三名角色。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"space"},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"边界行者等级 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pgFefXyCH8wgE0xN","name":"魔法激励  Magical Inspiration","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_SacredCleansing.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>如果一个生物拥有来自你的诗人激励骰子，在他释放一个恢复生命值或者造成伤害的法术时，他可以掷出激励骰子并选择法术的其中一个被法术影响的目标，在对该目标的恢复或者伤害数值上加上诗人激励骰的掷骰结果。这个诗人激励骰子随即被消耗。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"吟游诗人等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pkGt4Q7woUwRpSM3","name":"法律化身 Embodiment of the Law","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_AuraMastery.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从 6 级起，你变得十分擅于引导魔法能量来强迫他人。</p>\n<p>         如果你用一个 1 环或更高的法术位施展一个附魔学派的法术，倘若这个法术的施法时间是 1 动作，你可以在这次施法时将法术的施法时间改为 1 附赠动作。</p>\n<p>         你可以使用该特性的次数等于你的感知调整值（最少一次）。完成一次长休后，你将重获其所有消耗掉的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"GGR","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"max(@abilities.wis.mod,1)","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"秩序领域等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pv3tLoLy9ENwld0e","name":"引导神力：守望者的意志 Channel Divinity： Watcher's Will","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Paladin_HolyPrism.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以使用你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.3eyfqXMTJMG9AxYH]{引导神力}，将信仰的守护力量融入你的存在之中。以一个动作，你可以选择30尺内你可见的生物，数量至多等同于你的魅力调整值（至少为1）。在1分钟内，你和所有被选择的生物在智力、感知和魅力豁免上都获得优势。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"守望之誓等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pvJpTWoLaE9fDaYk","name":"剑歌之术 Training In War And Song","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/INV_Knife_1h_PanDung_C_01.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         2级起，你可唤起一种特殊的精灵魔法——剑歌之术——只要你并未穿着中甲、重甲或使用盾牌。它赐予你超自然的速度、敏捷与专注。<br />        你可以用一个附赠动作开始剑歌，它将持续1分钟。如果你陷入失能，或穿上中甲、重甲或盾牌，或你用双手发动一次武器攻击，你的剑歌将提前结束。你也可以随时解消剑歌（不需要动作）。<br />在剑歌激活期间，你获得以下好处：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你的AC获得等于你智力调整值的加值（最少+1）。</li>\n<li>你的陆地移动速度增加10 尺。</li>\n<li>你在敏捷（杂技）检定上获得优势。</li>\n<li>你在为维持法术专注所进行的体质豁免检定上获得加值，加值等于你的智力调整值（最少+1）。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>你可以使用两次本能力。完成一次短休或长休后你重获所有已用的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"2","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"剑咏者等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"q3eNDUv8ger0r7lQ","name":"迷惑学院 College of Glamour（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Priest_Darkness.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         迷惑学院向那些在充满生机又处处致命的妖精国度里学习技艺的吟游诗人们敞开了大门。被半羊人，艾拉德琳和其他精类生物指导，这些吟游诗人学会了使用魔法来取悦并吸引他人。</p>\n<p>         此学院的吟游诗人通常会带来敬畏与恐惧。他们的表演近乎传奇。此学院的吟游诗人风情万种，只是一场表演便足以让绑架者乖乖离开，让愤怒的巨龙归于平静。同样的魔法让他们在操弄他人心智的同时，也能掌控野兽。恶劣的迷惑学院诗人可以混入一个社群几周，用魔法让主人变成奴隶；英勇的迷惑学院诗人反而利用这种力量打击压迫者，为被压迫的人们带来快乐。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"吟游诗人等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"q7fXUTdWClL20wOS","name":"永亡宗 Way of The Long Death（SCAG）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Creature_Cursed_05%20-%201.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>永亡宗的武僧迷醉于死亡的结构和意义。他们拘束生物并用精心准备的实验去捕捉，记录，理解他们死亡的瞬间。他们用这些知识去指导他们的武术，从而产生了致命的战斗风格。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"武僧等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qCQtq2qCdWT5wduu","name":"圣杯座 Chalice","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_Faction_Celestials.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>一只赋予生命的圣杯形态的星座于你身上浮现。每当你使用法术位施展法术来恢复一个生物的生命值，你或你30尺内的另一生物可以回复等同于[[/r 1d8]]+你的感知调整值的生命值。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"wis","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+ @abilities.wis.mod","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"星辰结社等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qLumQRvZFx7QwuNy","name":"巧舌如簧 Silver Tongue","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/httpsvignettewikianocookienetwowimages999Spellmiscemotionhappypngrevisionlatestcb20090317211041pathprefixru.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         3级起，你是在正确之时言说正确之话的大师。当你进行一个魅力（游说）或（欺瞒）检定时，你可以将[[/r d20]]骰掷9或以下的结果都视为10。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MOT","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"雄辩学院等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qUzTbACHrzXHj4c1","name":"凶兆猎犬 Hound of ill Omen","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_shadow_summonfelhunter.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>6级时，你获得一种能力，你能够驱使嚎叫的幽暗生物来折磨你的敌人的。你可以以一个附赠动作消耗3点术法点选择一个120尺内你可见的生物作为目标，用魔法召唤一头凶兆猎犬的猎犬去猎杀它。凶兆猎犬用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.EYiQZ3rFL25fEJY5]{恐狼 Dire Wolf}的模板但有以下变化：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>猎犬的体型由大体型变为中等体型，猎犬视作怪兽而不是野兽。</li>\n<li>当猎犬被召唤时获得等同于你术士等级一半的临时生命值。</li>\n<li>猎犬可以像穿越困难地形一样穿过其他生物或物体。如果当猎犬的回合结束时处于某个物体内则会受到5点的力场伤害。</li>\n<li>当猎犬的回合开始时，自动知晓猎物的所在。如果目标处于躲藏状态，它对猎犬来说不再处于该状态。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>猎犬被召唤时出现在目标30尺内一个由你选择的空间。为猎犬投掷先攻。当猎犬行动时，它只能以最短路径冲向目标猎物，以及只能在攻击目标猎物时执行动作。猎犬可以使用借机攻击，但对象只能是目标猎物。此外，当凶兆猎犬在目标猎物5尺内时，目标对你所释放的任何法术的豁免上都承受劣势。凶兆猎犬会在它自己降为0血、猎物降为0血或5分钟后消失。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":"3术法点。"},"duration":{"value":5,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":120,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"幽影魔法等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qbFSJVzyStMuTGX8","name":"警戒呵斥 Vigilant Rebuke","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Crown_of_the_Heavens_Icon.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>15级起，你学会了如何惩罚那些对你与受你守护之人施行欺瞒的家伙。当你或你30尺内一个你可见的生物在一次智力、感知或魅力豁免上成功时，你可以用反应对迫使你或该生物进行豁免检定的生物造成力场伤害，数值等同于你的魅力调整值加上[[/r 2d8]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d8+@abilities.cha.mod","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"守望之誓等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qzKSooNxo2zww1oE","name":"狂野浪潮 Wild Surge","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/sha_spell_warlock_demonsoul_nightborne.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你体内那翻滚不息的魔法能量又是会从你身上爆发出来。当你进入@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.gLNFWGL05O0FUNTD]{狂暴}状态时，掷骰子并根据以下狂野魔法列表中决定所产生的狂野魔法。 如果这个狂野魔法需要进行豁免检定，则其DC等于8+你的熟练加值+你的体质调整值。</p>\n<h3><strong>狂野魔法</strong></h3>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>[[/r D8]]</th>\n<th>魔法效果</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>阴暗的卷须在你身边疯狂挥舞。在你能看到的30尺内，你选择若干生物，他们都必须进行一次体质豁免，如果失败，则将收到[[/r 1d12]]的暗蚀伤害。你获得[[/r 1d12]]的临时生命值</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>你可以传送到30尺内的一个未被占据的，你可以看到的地方。直到你的狂暴终止，你的每一个回合都可以消耗一个附赠动作再次发动这个效果。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>一个无形的灵体，看起来像一个呋噜或者皮克精（由你决定），出现在一个你30尺内可以看到的生物的5尺以内。并且在当前回合结束时，这个灵体会爆炸，所有5尺以内的生物必须进行一次敏捷豁免，如果失败，将承受[[/r 1d6]]的力场伤害。直到你的狂暴结束前，你每个回合都可以消耗一次附赠动作来再次发动这个效果。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>魔力与牛所选择的一把你正持握着的武器相融在一起。直到你的狂暴结束前，这把武器的伤害类型转变为力场伤害，并且获得轻型和投掷（20尺/60尺）的属性。如果你手中不在持握有这把武器，它会在当前回合结束的时候重新出现在你的手中。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>在你的狂暴结束前，每当一个生物以攻击检定的方式对你进行攻击并命中，你身上的魔力抽打反击对其造成[[/r 1d6]]的力场伤害。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>在你的狂暴结束前，你周身围绕着彩色的防护光芒。你的AC加一，并且在你10尺内的伙伴也可以享受到这一加成。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>你身边暂时生长出花朵与藤蔓。在你的狂暴结束前，你周围15尺的地面对你的敌人视作困难地形。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>一束光从你胸膛射出。你所选择的30尺内的你可以看到的另一个生物必须进行一次体质豁免检定，如果失败，将会收到[[/r 1d6]]的光耀伤害并且直到你的下一个回合开始前他将一直处于失明状态。直到你的狂暴结束前，你每个回合都可以消耗一次附赠动作来再次发动这个效果。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"d8","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"狂野魔法道途等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"r0PYs1ZzHMS20cU7","name":"传心谈话 Telepathic Speech","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_warlock_soullink.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>1级起，你能够在自己与他人的意识中构建一道心灵感应的链接。以一个附赠动作，你可以选择30尺内一个你可见的生物，只要你与其距离的里数不超过你的魅力调整值（至少1里），你与其能够通过心灵感应方式进行交流。你们必须使用对方知晓的语言进行心灵交流才能使其理解你通过心灵感应传达的话语。</p>\n<p>心灵感应的链接持续等同于你术士等级的分钟数。当你失能或死亡，或你使用此能力与其他生物构建链接时，其提前结束。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":1,"long":null,"units":"mi"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"畸变心智等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"r3tVSxF9RqK4P2Bf","name":"装甲师 Armorer","type":"feat","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-helmet-metal.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>　　对于装甲师专业的奇械师来说，装甲就像是第二层皮肤。这一装甲能够增强奇械师的魔法，释放强力的攻击，产生绝佳的防护。这些奇械师与他们的装甲之间有着强力的纽带，在他们经过实验并改进装甲的魔法性能后，甚至能够合二为一。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>经典的奇械师逻辑困局： “如果，我们的发明出了那种会爆炸的问题时我们正在里面该怎么办？ ”</p>\n<p><em> ——塔夏</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>本职工具 Tools of the Trade</strong></p>\n<p>　　你获得重甲的熟练。你同时获得@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.B97AB85722BCF651]{铁匠工具}的熟练，如果你已经熟练于此工具，作为代替，你能获得另一种工匠工具的熟练。</p>\n<p><strong>装甲师法术 Armorer Spells</strong></p>\n<p>　　只要你达到相应的职业等级，装甲师法术表格中的法术总是被视为已准备。这些法术对你来说是奇械师法术，且不会计入你可以准备法术的总数。</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th><strong>奇械师等级</strong></th>\n<th><strong>法术</strong></th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.q0FYQJX9EBseJ9KN]{魔法飞弹}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.8GM6YBgYFPIcFXKg]{雷鸣波}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.1EkQSAH6o8WMxUU3]{镜影术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.3m0QZZAQfR4jXS9q]{粉碎音波}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.BbpCbjCXt14a08Jp]{催眠图纹}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.dHg72reVMXYFu4lR]{闪电束}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13级</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.AdWubx1kFJLe8QDa]{火焰护盾}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Au584WRiGch84PXI]{高等隐形术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.EoIuyVnLAF4DyTO7]{穿墙术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.31jKHMGJ0vlqdvQU]{力场墙}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奇械师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"IwQxpJreN0IYMUOm","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.toolProf.value","mode":2,"value":"smith"},{"key":"data.traits.armorProf.value","mode":2,"value":"hvy"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-helmet-metal.webp","label":"获得重甲、铁匠工具熟练","origin":"Item.r3tVSxF9RqK4P2Bf","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"rmKcEP7VcSnuiE1I","name":"魔法物品熟稔 Magic Item Adept","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_HealingAura.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         当你达到10级时，你对如何使用和制作魔法物品有了深刻的理解：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你一次最多可以同调四个魔法物品。</li>\n<li>如果你制作一件稀有度为普通或非普通的魔法物品，时间花费只需通常的四分之一，而且金钱花费只有通常的一半。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奇械师等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"rt2w2oWZgdNmOm3n","name":"尘世壁垒 Mortal Bulwark","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/002505.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>20级起，你展现出神圣力量的火花，以捍卫凡人的世界。以一个附赠动作，你在1分钟内获得以下增益：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你获得120尺的真实视觉。</li>\n<li>当你对异怪、天界生物、元素、精类或邪魔进行攻击检定时，你获得优势。</li>\n<li>当你对一个生物进行攻击并击中，并对其造成伤害时，你可以使其进行一次魅力豁免。若其失败且其不属于此位面，其将被魔法性地放逐到其原本的位面。若目标豁免成功，其在24小时内不能再被此能力放逐。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>一旦你使用了此能力，你在完成一次长休之前必须消耗一个5环法术位以再次使用此能力。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"守望之誓等级 20","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"1qNIImlL9UawRXN2","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.senses.truesight","mode":4,"value":"120"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/002505.png","label":"获得120尺真实视觉","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.rt2w2oWZgdNmOm3n","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"rydtC4xFzhhmfXsT","name":"魔射手学识 Arcane Archer Lore","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_HuntingParty.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在3级时，你作为精灵军事传统的研习者学会了魔法理论或者自然知识。你从奥秘或者自然中选择一个技能获得熟练，而且从@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.zaUmr54yGtLyvUVC]{魔法伎俩}或者@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Q6muyDarRcXMcuKv]{德鲁伊伎俩}中选择一个戏法并学会。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魔射手等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"s8snvQrvRsN7YeaH","name":"治愈之光 Healing Light","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_BlindingHeal.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在1级时，你得到了引导天界能量以治疗伤口的能力。你获得了一个[[/r d6]]骰池，用以使用此治愈能力。骰池的总数等于1+你的邪术士等级。</p>\n<p>以一个附赠动作，你可以消耗骰池，治疗一个你视线中的、距你60尺以内的生物。单独一次能消耗的最大骰子数量等于你的魅力调整值（最小为1）。投掷你消耗的骰子，将骰值相加来决定所能恢复的生命值总量。</p>\n<p>当你完成一次长休后，骰池重获所有已消耗的骰子。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"1+@classes.warlock.levels","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","healing"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"天界宗主等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"sE0eWBfIdzrqoNWO","name":"灵能力量 Psionic Power","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_socererking_arcanemines.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你内心拥有一个灵能力量的源泉。这股能量表现为每个[[/r d6]]的灵能骰。你拥有两倍熟练加值的灵能骰数量，且它们为你所拥有的各种心灵异能提供能量，详情如下。</p>\n<p>你在使用一些能力时需要消耗灵能骰，如异能描述中所述，如果一些异能在你的灵能骰全部掷完后还需要你使用一个灵能骰，你就不能使用该异能。你可以在完成一次长休后恢复所有已使用的灵能骰。此外，你可以使用一个附赠动作重新获得一个已使用的灵能骰，但你在完成一次短休或长休之前不能再次获得。</p>\n<p>当你升级到特定战士等级时，你的灵能骰大小有所增长：第5级[[/r d8]]，第11级[[/r d10]]，第17级[[/r d12]]。</p>\n<p>可以在以下异能使用你的灵能骰：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.IGFbodPoYQ6aujAT]{庇护力场 Protective Field}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.uaPefnuz8mYlc7Th]{灵能击打 Psionic Strike}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.w6wzRcoxxL5rrnxe]{念力控物 Telekinetic Movement}</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":4,"max":"2*@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"灵能武士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"sFmMs3sZixTozZcC","name":"神性之怒 Divine Fury","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_RetributionAura.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从你在3级选择此道途开始，你可以引导神性之怒注入武器打击中。当你处于狂暴中，你在自己回合中用武器攻击命中的第一个生物会受到额外伤害，数值等于[[/r 1d6]]+你野蛮人等级的一半。此伤害的类型为黯蚀或光耀；你在你得到此特性时选择它的类型。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d6+floor(@classes.barbarian.levels/2)","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"狂热者等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"sGggioh8w6WTNUbD","name":"实验性灵药 Experimental Elixir","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Racial_BetterLivingThroughChemistry.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从第3级起，每当你完成一次长休，你能在一个你接触的空瓶中魔法性的制造出一剂实验性灵药。当某人饮用灵药时，通过实验性灵药表来掷骰决定灵药的效果。以一个动作，一个生物能自己饮用灵药，或是将灵药给一个失能生物饮用。</p>\n<p>         你需要拥有@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.EFBBAE8B63126638]{炼金工具}才能制造实验性灵药，你通过此特征创造的所有灵药会一直存在到被饮用，或是你一下次长休结束时。</p>\n<p>         当你达到某些特定等级时，将能够在长休结束时制造更多灵药：6级时2剂，15级时3剂。每剂灵药都需要掷骰决定效果。每一剂灵药都需要用独立的烧瓶盛放。</p>\n<p>         你能通过消耗一枚1环或更高环的法术位来制造额外的实验性灵药。要这么做的话，你需要以一个动作接触一个空烧瓶来制造灵药，然后从实验性灵药表中选择这剂灵药的效果。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>[[/r d6]]</th>\n<th>效果</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>治疗。饮用者恢复[[/r 2d4]]+你智力调整值的生命值。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>疾速。饮用者在1小时内速度增加10尺。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>韧性。饮用者在10分钟内AC+1。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>勇气。饮用者在1分钟内，能够在每个攻击检定和豁免检定中增加一个[[/r d4]]。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>飞行。饮用者在10分钟内获得10尺飞行速度。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>变形。饮用者的身体像被施展了法术@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.RzU9orr1mmUeZOcl]{变身术 Alter Self}。饮用者选择其变化效应，效果持续10分钟。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"炼金师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"sYXqPwtRX6En37x5","name":"暮光守护 Twilight Shroud","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_shadow_twilight.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>暮光拥抱着你并提供保护：处于你@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.RF3cORN1AMVCqgJu]{暮光圣域}的球体内的你和你的盟友处于半身掩护。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"暮光领域等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"sZd00Pspnz3w6xkN","name":"血肉启示 Revelation In Flesh","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_priest_voidform.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>14级起，你能够释放出潜藏在你内部扭曲的真实形态。以一个附赠动作，你使用至少1术法点以魔法性地转变形态，持续10分钟。你每因此使用了1术法点，你便可以在转变形态期间选择并获得以下一种增益：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你能看见60尺内的隐形生物，前提是其对你不为全遮蔽。</li>\n<li>你获得等同于你行走速度的飞行速度，并能停留在空中。当你飞行时，你的皮肤表面流出发光的粘液或是散发出超凡脱俗的光芒。</li>\n<li>你获得等同于你两倍行走速度的游泳速度，且你能在水下呼吸。此外，腮从你的脖子上长出来，或从耳后呈扇状翻出，你的手指变成蹼趾，或有卷曲的细毛从你的衣服底下翻腾而出。</li>\n<li>你的身体和你携带的装备都变得柔韧粘滑。你能够轻松穿过最窄1寸宽的狭窄空间而不用挤进去，且你可以消耗5尺移动速度以逃离非魔法的束缚或擒抱。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":"至少 1 术法点。"},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"畸变心智等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"sdMfUcD65aN7rUkO","name":"怒火侵蚀 Infectious Fury","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_druid_freshwound.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你在@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.gLNFWGL05O0FUNTD]{狂暴}中用你的天生武器击中一个生物时，你内在的野兽可以诅咒你的目标变得如狂犬病似得病态癫狂。该生物需进行一次感知豁免（DC为8+你的熟练加值+你的体质调整值），如果失败，将必须承受以下的一种效果（尤你来决定）：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>目标必须消耗他的反应动作对你所选择的一个能看到的目标的进行一次近战攻击。</li>\n<li>目标承受[[/r 2d12]]的心灵伤害</li>\n</ul>\n<p>你每天可以使用该能力的次数等于你的熟练加值。每完成一次长休之后你补充齐所有已消耗的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":"狂暴中用天生武器击中生物。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":4,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d12","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"con"},"requirements":"野兽道途等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"t26Nd728fW5zskrC","name":"魔能祈唤选项 Eldritch Invocation Options","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/violet_28.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你选择魔能祈唤时，你可以选用这些额外的内容。</p>\n<p><strong>祈唤列表：</strong></p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>魔能祈唤</th>\n<th>先决条件</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.TieC6BcmIWTOYzQC]{魔能祈唤：护符牵绊}</td>\n<td>第12级，@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.GTSTP2qr10wmyLDC]{符之魔契}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.nkp511Gfd16b3d2g]{魔能祈唤：魔能意志}</td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.BhZ1smcVbehFTyZ4]{魔能祈唤：遥远音讯}</td>\n<td>第5级，@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.jffAWIaUzgNdPQvM]{书之魔契}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.w7YF2HtdcugREsx4]{魔能祈唤：守护馈赠}</td>\n<td>第9级，@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.jffAWIaUzgNdPQvM]{书之魔契}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.a1JCKCXb7pCgs9wT]{魔能祈唤：链主赋能}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.wZTuyqjaVEmZgykR]{链之魔契}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.EzFJHWfeZ4YNEn5L]{魔能祈唤：护符庇佑}</td>\n<td>第7级，@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.GTSTP2qr10wmyLDC]{符之魔契}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.8ELKR6Qzmagy4RYK]{魔能祈唤：符令责斥}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.GTSTP2qr10wmyLDC]{符之魔契}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.QkDzUSuaqmTa1rwN]{魔能祈唤：永恒奴役}</td>\n<td>第5级</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts"