{"_id":"tInzXFrwzNnbXE8h","name":"魔法工艺 Magical Tinkering","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_RewindTime.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         在第1级，你将学习如何在平凡的物品中注入魔法的火花。要使用这个能力，你必须手持@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.E20CE7D30DE58B23]{修理工具}，或其他工匠工具。然后花费一个动作触摸一个微小的非魔法物体，从以下魔法属性中选择一个赋予它：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>该物体提供5尺半径的明亮照明，以及该范围外5尺范围的微光照明。</li>\n<li>无论何时，只要该物品被生物触碰，就会发出可在10尺外听到的录音信息。录入的信息在你将此属性赋予对象时决定，且时长不可超过6秒。</li>\n<li>物品不断地发出一种气味或一种非语言的声音（风声、浪声、鸟叫或类似的声音）。这一现象最多能传播10尺远。</li>\n<li>一个静态的视觉效果出现在物体的表面上。这个效果可以是一幅图片，最多25个单词的文本，线条和形状，或者这些元素的混合，如你所愿。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>         所选的魔法属性持续时间无限。你能够以一个动作触摸对象来消除这一魔法属性。</p>\n<p>         你能够通过此特性将魔力赋予多个物品，每次使用该特性时都需要触摸一个物品，并且单个物品一次只能承载一种魔法属性。你能够使用该特性影响的物品的最大数量等于你的智力调整值（最少一个物品）。如果你试图超过最大值，最老的魔法属性将立即结束，然后新的魔法属性生效。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"object"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"max(@abilities.int.mod,1)","per":"charges"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"奇械师等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"tKsjZaCSEX4KUBYN","name":"耐久魔法 Durable Magic","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Arcane_ArcanePotency.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>从10级起，你引导的魔法也能阻绝伤害。当你于一个法术上维持专注时，你在AC和所有豁免上获得+2加值。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战争法师等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"tPHWK8263xEiA9ke","name":"星我宗 Way of the Astral Self（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_bastion_druid.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<blockquote>\n<p>自我谨记：创造一个法术来让你用你的魂体来猛击敌人的喉咙。</p>\n<p><em>—— 塔莎</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>   一个遵循星我宗的武僧相信他们的身体是一种幻觉，他们把气视为他们真实形态的代表，即为星我。星我这个形态，用之以善则正，用之以恶则邪，一些宗派训练学徒使用他们的力量来保护弱者，还有的宗派则教导那些欲追名逐利的学徒在为上位者服务时，能展现他们的真我。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"武僧等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"tVe8Dhk12i9A1mOd","name":"墓穴惊嚎Wails From The Grave","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_rogue_deadlymomentum.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你将某人推向墓穴时，你也可以沟通死亡之力，使得亡者的嚎哭短暂环绕着新的目标。当你在你的回合对于一个生物造成了偷袭伤害之后，你可以立即选择该生物30尺内第二个可见生物，掷你一半的偷袭骰（向上取整），对其造成等同于结果的暗蚀伤害。</p>\n<p>你可以使用此特性的次数等同于你的熟练加值，当你完成一次长休时恢复所有使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(floor((-1+@classes.rogue.levels)/4)+1)d6","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"鬼魅等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"teODKKtETrQCBQJT","name":"剑圣之途 Path of the Kensei","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_DeathKnight_SpellDeflection.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         当你在3级时选择此宗派时，你特殊的武术训练让精通于你特定武器的使用。这条道途同时也包括了书画技艺的指导。你获得下列好处。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong> 剑圣武器。</strong>选择二种武器做为你的剑圣武器：一种近战武器和一种远程武器。这些武器可以是任何没有重型或特殊属性的简易或军用武器，包括@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.3EE9A77945B5824F]{长弓}也是可选选项之一。若你尚未熟练于这些武器，则你获得它们的熟练。所选的武器种类对你而言将被视为武僧武器。这个宗派的许多能力都只会作用于你的剑圣武器。当你在此职业升至6级、11级、和17级时，你可以遵循上述的条件，再选择另一种武器种类——近战或远程皆可——做为你的剑圣武器。</li>\n<li><strong>灵巧格档。</strong>若你在你的回合以 攻击动作的一部份进行了一次徒手打击，且你正持握一把剑圣武器，则若该武器是一把近战武器，你将可以用它来保护自己。当该武器在你中且你未陷入无力状态，你的AC获得+2加值直到你的下个回合开始。</li>\n<li><strong>持弓审固。</strong>你可以在你的回合使用一个附赠动作让你透过剑圣武器所进行远程攻击变得更加致命。当你这么做时，任何被你以剑圣武器所进行的远程攻击命中的目标将会受到额外的 [[/r 1d4]]该武器伤害类型的伤害。你保留这个好处直到该回合结束。</li>\n<li><strong> 书画之道。</strong>你从@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.580EEA755E3DAB97]{书法工具}或@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.A1B72AD159DC12C6]{画家工具}中选择并获得其中一项的熟练。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"剑圣宗等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"to46aUxJL6QaSqWj","name":"破誓者 Oathbreaker（DMG）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_FocusedMind.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         成为破誓者的圣武士打破了自己的神圣誓言，而去追求黑暗的野心或为邪恶力量服务。圣武士心中燃烧的光耀已经熄灭，只剩下一片黑暗。</p>\n<p>         只有至少达到 3 级的邪恶圣武士才能成为一名破誓者。</p>\n<p>         该圣武士将用破誓者特性替换其所有对应神圣誓言的特性。</p>\n<p><strong>破誓者法术 Oathbreaker Spells</strong></p>\n<p>         一名破誓者圣武士失去所有之前获得的圣誓法术，并在达到相应圣武士等级时获得下列破誓者法术作为替代。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>圣骑士等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>3rd</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Qh8PTvCxR44isqVO]{炼狱叱喝}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Fl4lOWHo82WLp3g7]{致伤术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>5th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.otAaRLMc7OfxRYAw]{疯狂冠冕}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.UyQ9nYcQlFdEbmeV]{黑暗术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>9th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.xYpJGRI4xcMa41kO]{操纵死尸}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.kqh0eV640hXk4flg]{降咒}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>13th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.AVumturalJuP4paw]{枯萎术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.MZ1jwLEJukFjSv1a]{困惑术}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>17th</strong></td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.gbHBG4jYU3I06JQO]{疫病术}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.JudswpO6E5GBlyfQ]{支配人类}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"圣武士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"f