{"_id":"u36lfdx0Yx9OWBes","name":"胜利之歌 Song of Victory (TCE)","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/002612.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>14级起，在你的剑歌激活期间，你将你的智力调整值（最低+1）加在你的近战武器伤害上。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"剑咏者等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"u9QvNzysMbM5He3g","name":"风暴先驱 Path of The Storm Herald（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_BG_KillFlagCarriers_grabFlag_CapIt.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<h4>      所有野蛮人内心都有一股怒火。他们的怒气使他们拥有超强的力量、耐力和速度。跟随风暴先驱之路的野蛮人学会将狂暴转化为原初魔力灵光，围绕着他们旋转。在愤怒的时候，这条路上的野蛮人会利用大自然的力量来创造强大的魔法效果。</h4>\n<h4>      风暴先驱是典型的精英斗士，他们和德鲁伊、游骑兵和其他宣誓要保护自然的人一起训练。其他风暴先驱在饱受风暴侵袭的地区、世界尽头冰冻地区或最热沙漠的深处磨练他们的技艺。</h4>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"野蛮人等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"u9tfHLloCMBfZfmA","name":"事件视界 Event Horizon","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003140.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         14级起， 使用一个动作，你能魔法地发散出由重力能量引起的强大力场，力场能把其他生物拖拽至多1分钟，或在你的专注终止（如同你专注法术一样）时结束。在持续时间内，当一个位于你30尺内，且与你敌对的生物开始回合时，该生物必须进行一次力量豁免对抗你的法术DC。当豁免失败时，该生物受到[[/r 2d10]]的力场伤害，并且移动速度降低至0尺，减速持续直到该生物的下一个回合开始。当豁免成功时，该生物受到一半的伤害，并且每移动一尺就需要额外花费2尺的移动力。</p>\n<p>          一旦你使用了本特性，你不能再次使用，直到你完成了一次长休或花费一个3环或更高的法术位来再次启动。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EGtW","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d10","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"str","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"重力魔法等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"uCwcaFGcyIGftJr4","name":"凋零箭 Enfeebling Arrow","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_ChimeraShot2.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你在你的箭上施展死灵魔法。被这发箭击中的角色会额外受到[[/r 2d6]]的黯蚀伤害。目标必须成功通过一个体质豁免，或者他的武器攻击造成的伤害在你的下一个回合开始之前减半。</p>\n<p>         当你的战士等级到18级时该黯蚀伤害增加到[[/r 4d6]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(ceil(@classes.fighter.levels/17)*2)d6","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"int"},"requirements":"魔射手等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"uKC9fBR0OtBRSxRP","name":"时间变幻 Chornal Shift","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003553.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从2级起，你可以魔法地获取对单一生物周围的时间流动的有限控制。在你或者30尺内你可以看见的一个生物进行一次攻击检定，属性检定或者豁免检定后，你可以以一个反应迫使该生物重投。你可以在得知该检定是否成功后做出这一反应。该生物必须使用第二次的结果。</p>\n<p>         你可以使用这一特性两次。你在完成一次长休后重获所有已消耗的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EGtW","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":2,"max":"2","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"时间魔法等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
