{"_id":"vimr3VI7xsnK1ydv","name":"星我之容 Visage of the Astral Self","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_bastion_priest.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以召唤你的星我之容，以一个附赠动作，或者作为你召唤@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.Qctmiuim4M9SfU1E]{星我之臂}时的附赠动作中的一部分，你可以花费1点气来召唤星我之容，持续10分钟，如果你失能或死亡，则它会立即消失。</p>\n<p>幽光般的头盔或面具遮挡着你的脸，你来决定它的外观。</p>\n<p>当星我之容存在时，你将获得如下增益：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>星之视觉</strong>。你在黑暗中拥有120尺的可视距离，而无论其属于魔法黑暗还是非魔法黑暗。</li>\n<li><strong>灵魂感知</strong>。你的感知（洞悉）和魅力（威吓）检定具有优势。</li>\n<li><strong>灵魂之语</strong>。当你说话时，你可以将你的话语指向你选择的一个60尺范围内的可视生物，这种情况下只有这个生物才能听到你的声音。 或者你可以放大你的声音，这种情况下600尺内的所有生物都能听到你的声音。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":"1 点气。"},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"星我宗等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"ZbkZlyE5gsHPADH0","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.senses.darkvision","mode":4,"value":"120"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_bastion_priest.jpg","label":"获得 120 尺黑暗视野。","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.vimr3VI7xsnK1ydv","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"vm6YnuatC67kIL5z","name":"梦境行者 Walker in Dreams","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Nature_Tranquility.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>          14级起，妖精荒野的魔力让你能物理性或精神性地穿越梦境空间。</p>\n<p>          当你完成了一次短休，你可以施展以下法术之一，无需消耗法术位也无需材料成分：@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.40z4HpFVUux7h03S]{托梦术}（以你作为信使）、@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.OA4mCsVxg6nUrLjV]{探知}、或@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.mcQ5lehafMClomzc]{传送法阵}。</p>\n<p>          以这种方法使用的传送法阵是特别的。取代了打开入口通往永久性传送法阵的能力，它将打开入口通往你在现存位面上完成最后一次长休的所在地。如果你没有在现存位面上进行过长休，这个法术会失败但不会浪费。</p>\n<p>          一旦你使用这个能力，直到你结束长休之前你不能再次使用。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"梦境之环等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"vpKflKr85FPEv4nk","name":"日魂宗 Way of the Sun Soul（SCAG）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Paladin_BlindingLight2.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>日魂宗的武僧学习如何引导出自己的生命能量并将它们转换为炽热的光芒。他们相信在每一个活着的生物的灵魂中都有这样不熄的光芒存在，并且教导他们以一种特殊的冥想方式去解锁。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"武僧等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"vzqFME5OV7DyzHmy","name":"引导神力:斥喝暴力 Rebuke the Violent","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Warrior_RallyingCry.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你可以使用你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.3eyfqXMTJMG9AxYH]{引导神力}来斥喝那些使用暴力的人。当一个处于你周围30尺内的敌人以一次攻击对一个你之外的生物造成伤害时，以一个反应，你强迫攻击者进行一次感知豁免检定。检定失败则攻击者受到等同于其刚刚造成的伤害的光耀伤害。成功则受到一半伤害。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"周围30尺内的敌人以一次攻击对一个你之外的生物造成伤害。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"救赎之誓等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
