{"_id":"w3EVK3XBgi1HZ5K2","name":"奥术射击 Arcane Shot","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_ZenArchery.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         3级时，你学会在射击时施放一些特殊的魔法效果。当你获得这个特性时，你学会两种你选择的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.HqwYiStgiunCmEG7]{奥术射击选项}。</p>\n<p>         每个回合，当你以一个攻击动作的一部分来用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.567A278AA577CF7D]{短弓}或者@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.3EE9A77945B5824F]{长弓}射出箭矢时，你可以为你的箭矢挑选一个你拥有的奥术射击选项。你可以在箭矢击中一名角色时决定是否使用该选项，除非该选项不包括一个攻击骰。你拥有两次使用该特性的机会，而且你在完成一次短休或长休后重新获得所有被消耗的的使用次数。</p>\n<p>         当你到达一定战士等级时（7级、10级、15级、18级）你会获得一个额外的你选择的奥术射击选项。所有的选项在你成为18级战士时都会提升。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魔射手等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"w6wzRcoxxL5rrnxe","name":"念力控物 Telekinetic Movement","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/movement/abstract-ribbons-red-orange.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以用意念移动一个物体或生物。你可以使用一个动作选中一个最多大型的物体或一个除你以外的自愿生物。如果目标在对你30尺内且可视，你可以将其移动至多30尺至一个对你可见的空地。另外，如果目标是一个小物件，你可以从你的手中给出或收回。无论采取哪种方式，你都可以或水平、或垂直、或两者都使用地移动它。</p>\n<p>当你使用该异能时，你无法再使用该能力直到你完成一次短休或长休，除非你消耗一个灵能骰来再次使用该异能。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"object"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"灵能武士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"w7YF2HtdcugREsx4","name":"魔能祈唤：守护馈赠Eldritch Invocation：Gift of the Protectors","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/blue_35.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>一张新的书页出现在你的影之书中。在你的允许之下，一个生物可以使用一个动作来将他的名字写在这一页上，这一页能包括的名字数量等于你的熟练加值。 当一个名字在这一页上的生物生命值降为0，但是还没有完全死亡，这个生物的生命值魔法化的变为1点。一旦这个魔法效应被触发，直到你完成一次长休，该效应无法再被任何生物触发。</p>\n<p>你可以使用一个动作，以触摸的形式魔法化地消除一个在书页上的名字。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"邪术师等级 9， 书之魔契","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"wCe7pIUg2M1g8Wws","name":"战斗风格：拦截","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/weapon_16.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>        </strong>当一个你可见的生物攻击距离你5尺以内你以外的目标时，你能以一个反应将目标受到的伤害减少[[/r 1d10]]+你熟练加值（最多减到0伤害）。当你手持一面盾牌或者一把简单或军用武器时才能执行此反应。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d10+@prof","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"战士等级 1，勇士等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
