{"_id":"wM1qG9WzNzrQYqeI","name":"清风之灵 Wind Soul","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Mage_IceFlows.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>18级时，你获得60尺飞行速度，且免疫闪电与雷鸣伤害。</p>\n<p>以一个动作，你可以将你的飞行速度降低到30尺，持续一小时。当你这么做时，你可以指定在你身边30尺内的，3+你的魅力调整值个生物。这些被选定的生物获得30尺飞行速度，持续1小时。你不能在一次短休或者长休前再一次使用此能力。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":3,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"狂怒风暴等级 18","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"IodPunRrjTFHMqae","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.movement.fly","mode":4,"value":"60"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Mage_IceFlows.png","label":"获得 60 尺飞行速度","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.wM1qG9WzNzrQYqeI","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null},{"_id":"WL4jceyYGTNxwFSI","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.di.value","mode":2,"value":"lightning"},{"key":"data.traits.di.value","mode":2,"value":"thunder"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Mage_IceFlows.png","label":"获得闪电、雷鸣免疫","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.wM1qG9WzNzrQYqeI","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"name":"增强武器","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2>增强武器</h2>\n<p><em>物品：一把简易或军用武器</span></em><br /></span>　　该魔法武器在攻击和伤害检定中具有</span>+1</span>加值。</span><br /></span>　　当你拥有</span>10</span>个奇械师等级时，该加值变成</span>+2</span>。</span><br /></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_DeathKnight_FrozenRuneWeapon.png","_id":"wMAuU3oeWrKC1v5a"}
