{"_id":"wefEDw2QaHeaBZig","name":"奥能装甲 Arcane Armor","type":"feat","img":"icons/commodities/tech/metal-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你对冶金的钻研让你的盔甲成为了实现你奇械师魔法的渠道。只要你手持@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.B97AB85722BCF651]{铁匠工具}，就能以一个动作将你正穿着的一套重甲变成奥能装甲。在穿着奥能装甲时，你获得以下好处：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>如果你的盔甲通常对穿戴者的力量有要求，奥能装甲能让你无视它。</li>\n<li>你能够将奥能装甲作为你奇械师法术的法器。</li>\n<li>穿在你身上的奥能装甲除非你自愿，否则无法移除。同时，奥能装甲能够扩展到复盖你的整个身体，并替换你所有缺失的肢体，替换肢体的部分拥有和正常肢体一样的功能。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>转化为奥能装甲的盔甲会一直保有其功能，直到你脱下它、装上另一套盔甲、或你死亡。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"装甲师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"wfzlpRPC5owayAq5","name":"额外战斗风格（TCE）Fighting Style Options","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Warrior_Challange.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>      当你在选择战斗风格时，下列选项加入你的可选战斗风格中。 </p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>战士选项</th>\n<th>圣武士选项</th>\n<th>游侠选项</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.wCe7pIUg2M1g8Wws]{战斗风格：拦截} @Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.5M9eFqLMIbkwKy0b]{战斗风格：盲斗} @Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.nXNzOQmtv0e6egnX]{战斗风格：投掷武器战斗} @Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.B38xqQQ5E8HdqNzQ]{战斗风格：徒手战斗} @Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.XDsHOwUjo6dJSK4b]{战斗风格：卓越技巧}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.z7ImpZVtgqAgUsO5]{战斗风格：受祝福的勇士} @Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.5M9eFqLMIbkwKy0b]{战斗风格：盲斗} @Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.wCe7pIUg2M1g8Wws]{战斗风格：拦截}</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.ZyhSlbXVK3UETRBb]{战斗风格：德鲁伊教战士} @Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.5M9eFqLMIbkwKy0b]{战斗风格：盲斗} @Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.nXNzOQmtv0e6egnX]{战斗风格：投掷武器战斗}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战士等级 1，圣武士等级 2，游侠等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"x59pCLlBTi0kYjkD","name":"优雅战技 Elegant Maneuver","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Rogue_QuickRecovery.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         13 级起，你可以在自己回合内用一个附赠动作来使同一回合里的下次敏捷（体操）或力量（运动）检定具有优势。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游荡剑客等级 13","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"x5BlmsznCsW5gADs","name":"奥法暂滞 Arcane Abeyance","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_Readiness.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从10级起，当你消耗一个四环或更低的法术位来施展法术时，你可以将该法术的法力浓缩至一抹微尘中。该法术将冻结在施展的那一刻，并被保存在一个灰色的小珠中，持续一小时。这个小珠是一个拥有15AC和1点生命值的物件，并免疫毒素和心灵伤害。在持续时间结束或者珠子被摧毁时，它会在光芒一闪中消失，而法术将会失去。</p>\n<p>         持握着小珠的生物可以使用他的动作来释放其内的法术，随后小珠将会消失。该法术使用你的法术攻击加值和豁免DC，而在其他方面视为由释放它的生物施展。</p>\n<p>         在你以此特性创造一个小珠后，你在完成一次短休或长休前不能再次这样做。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EGtW","activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"时间魔法等级 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"x5rkrFYjoYkkY1jj","name":"翻腾浪涌 Writhing Tide","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Druid_Cyclone.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你能将你的集群的一部分凝聚成一股集中的力量，来将你托起。以一个附赠动作，你获得10尺飞行速度并且能悬浮在空中。该效应持续1分钟或直到你陷入失能状态。</p>\n<p>你能使用该特性的次数等于你的熟练加值，而你在结束一次长休后重新获得所有消耗的次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":3,"max":"@prof._baseProficiency","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"集群守卫等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"NiKJ3dSgrm1Zdcej","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.movement.fly","mode":4,"value":"10"},{"key":"data.attributes.movement.hover","mode":5,"value":"true"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":60},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Druid_Cyclone.png","label":"获得 10 尺飞行速度","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.x5rkrFYjoYkkY1jj","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"x7alcczxY6oUVuGq","name":"奥秘领域 Arcana Domain（SCAG）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Achievement_Reputation_KirinTor.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>        魔法在制造毁灭的同时也带来新生。作为一种能量，它弥散在多元宇宙的每一个角落。而掌管奥秘领域的神祗知晓魔法的秘密和潜能。对于一些神而言，魔法知识是一种重要的理解现实本质的途径；而另一些神单单只把魔法视为纯粹的能量，并拿它用来做他们认为适当做的事情。</p>\n<p>        这一领域的神祗往往和知识领域有联系，毕竟学习和奥术力量的关系往往亲密无间。在这个范围中，掌管这个领域的神祗包括阿祖斯和密斯特拉，还有精灵之神柯瑞隆。在其他世界，这个领域包括赫卡忒，麦斯麦索威，还有伊西斯；克莱恩的三月神索林那瑞，努林塔瑞和努塔瑞；灰鹰的博卡布，维克那和维婕斯。</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>牧师等级</th>\n<th>法术</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.cGO3m3Xu4mtPegr4]{侦测魔法}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.q0FYQJX9EBseJ9KN]{魔法飞弹}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.JXjHc37DKcHrPtNz]{涅斯图魔法灵光}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.14a3v5NF5h5Lgm9J]{魔化武器}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.as6xgBANCbyoWPXX]{解除魔法}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Vrzu8xpLMvOvOnx6]{防护法阵}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.uF6bn9CQaLwvmxwv]{秘法眼}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Xvbp5UwtqRWUmxqB]{李欧蒙秘藏箱}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.PmucSbzqmGhwisuE]{异界誓缚}@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.mcQ5lehafMClomzc]{传送法阵}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"牧师等级 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags