{"_id":"xY023jpDjfgyXQ1Q","name":"阴影视野 Umbral Sight","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Creature_Cursed_05.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         3级起，你获得60尺黑暗视觉。如果你已经从种族特性中获得了黑暗视觉，它的范围增加30尺。</p>\n<p>         你还擅长回避依赖黑暗视觉的角色。在黑暗中，你对于任何靠黑暗视觉观察你的角色是隐形的。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"幽域追踪者等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"wjeVQ3tOEW9NdJ1C","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.senses.darkvision","mode":4,"value":"60"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Creature_Cursed_05.png","label":"获得 60 尺黑暗视觉","origin":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.xY023jpDjfgyXQ1Q","transfer":true,"flags":{},"tint":null}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"xYMe0gbACvbti3Is","name":"低语学院 College of Whispers（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Arcane_FocusedPower.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         大多数村民都乐于招待吟游诗人。而来自低语学院的诗人们正是利用了这一点。他们看起来就像是其他的吟游诗人那样，分享新闻，一展歌喉，向观众们讲述搜罗来的轶事。但实际上，低语学院教会学生们的是：他们应该是披着羊皮的狼。这些诗人用他们的知识和魔法来揭露秘密，并用这些秘密来恐吓或是勒索他人。</p>\n<p>         许多其他的吟游诗人痛恨低语，认为他们是利用吟游诗人的名誉来为自己赢取金钱与权力的害群之马。因此，这些诗人很少会揭露出自己的真实面目，除非确有必要。他们通常声称来自其他学院，或谨慎的隐藏自己，好混入皇室或其他权力中心。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"吟游诗人等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"xbOa0YKgVBU7Ytlf","name":"亡者余声Whispers Of The Dead","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_DeathKnight_SoulReaper.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>死者的回响依附着你，一个幽灵般的存在会向你分享它的知识。每当你完成一次短休或长休时，你可以选择一项你没有熟练的工具或者技能并且获得该熟练，当你用这个能力来选择一项不同的熟练时，你会失去原来的熟练项。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"鬼魅等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"xdlaTQFWzEe9LMq6","name":"无畏无惧 Rakish Audacity","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Warrior_RallyingCry.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         第3级起，你万无一失的自信驱使着你的战斗。你可以将自己的魅力调整值加入你的先攻掷骰中。 另外，你发动@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.AlFAC3Lz1ud2ry9T]{偷袭}时可以忽视对方身边 5 尺必须有其他生物的条件。但偷袭特性需求的其他规则仍然适用于你。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"游荡剑客等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"xe5xbHMQAWZ9q2ET","name":"统御光环 Mantle of Majesty","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_Silence.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         6级时，你得到了用精类魔法笼罩自己的能力，让他人想要服侍你。以一个附赠动作，你可以施展@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Ja6HpsLeGA9MQ0Rm]{命令术}而无需消耗法术位，并且同时你变化为超凡的美貌外表，持续1分钟或直到你专注结束（就像你专注一个法术）。在这段时间内，你可以在你的每个回合以一个附赠动作施展命令术，且无需消耗法术位。</p>\n<p>         任何被你魅惑的生物将自动的在它们对抗此能力的豁免检定中失败。</p>\n<p>         一旦你使用此特性，直到你完成了一次长休前，你都不能再次使用它。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"迷惑学院等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"xzAp6LCqoEml2umc","name":"替换戏法 Cantrip Versatility","type":"feat","img":"icons/magic/nature/beam-hand-leaves-green.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>每当你达到该职业提升属性值的等级时，你就可以用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.spell-table.owJ94hrYlzU4BsBd]{德鲁伊法术列表}中的另一个戏法来替换你从该职业的施法特性中学到的一个戏法。</p>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"德鲁伊等级 4","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yGK1lxcpwIjRMIV2","name":"恐惧之王 Dread Lord","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/spell_shadow_twistedfaith.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         20 级时，作为一个动作项，该圣骑士可以使自己在 1分钟内环绕于阴郁的灵光中。该灵光可以将该圣武士周边30尺半径的亮光光照减弱为微光光照。任何受该圣武士恐慌的敌人在该灵光内开始其自己回合时将受到[[/r 4d10]]的心灵伤害。</p>\n<p>         此外，该圣武士以及由其指定的身处灵光中的生物都将笼罩于更深的幽影中。依赖视觉的生物对笼罩于该幽影中的生物发动攻击检定时具有劣势。 灵光持续时，该圣骑士可以在其自己回合内用一个附赠 动作令该灵光内的幽影攻击一个生物。该圣武士对该目标发动一次近战法术攻击。若攻击命中，则该目标受到的黯蚀伤害等于 3d10＋该圣武士的魅力调整值。</p>\n<p>         激活该灵光后，该圣骑士必须完成一次长休才能再次使 用该特性。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"enemy"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"cha","actionType":"msak","attackBonus":"","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["3d10+@abilities.cha.mod","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"4d10","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"破誓者等级 20","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yPeP0tufzv0uoZBT","name":"武士 Samurai（XGE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003176.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 武士是一种以坚决战斗意志击溃敌人的战士。武士的信念几乎坚不可摧，且挡在武士道路前的敌人只有两种选择：投降，或者死战方休。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"战士等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yQGz7bYFsOumtt2M","name":"爆裂箭 Bursting Arrow","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_Assassinate2.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         你将从塑能魔法中汲取的力场能量注入到箭中，这股能量会在你攻击后爆炸。当箭击中目标后，目标和其10尺内所有的角色都受到[[/r 2d6]]的力场伤害。</p>\n<p>         当你的战士等级到18级时该力场伤害增加到[[/r 4d6]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":10,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(ceil(@classes.fighter.levels/17)*2)d6","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魔射手等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yTvrp3vJbgTI2DnP","name":"调节密度 Adjust Density","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/003126.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         2级起，使用一个动作，你能魔法地改一个物件或生物的重量，目标必须变位于你30尺内，且你能看见目标。物件和生物必须为大型或更小的。目标的重量减半或者翻倍，持续时间至多一分钟，或在你的专注终止（如同你专注法术一样）时提前结束。</p>\n<p>         当一个生物的重量通过该效果减半时，该生物的移动速度增加10尺，跳跃距离变为正常的两倍，并且在进行力量检定或者力量豁免时具有劣势。当一个生物的重量通过该效果翻倍时，该生物的移动速度减少10尺，并且在进行力量检定或者力量豁免时具有优势。</p>\n<p>         当在该职业到达10级时，你能对一个巨型或更小的物件或生物使用本特性。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EGtW","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"重力魔法等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yaiCR2TIRre4E5Yi","name":"奥能炮台 Eldritch Cannon","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_vehicle_liquidpyrite_blue.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>　　在第 3级，你习得了如何制造一个魔法炮台。只要你手持@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.A4B41FB9DAE8B865]{木匠工具}或@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.itempack.B97AB85722BCF651]{铁匠工具}，你能以一个动作在距离你 5尺且没被占据的水平空格内魔法性地召唤出一架小型或微型炮台。小型奥能炮台会占据它所在的方格，而微型炮台能直接拿在手里。</p>\n<p>　　你每天能够免费召唤一次炮台，你在这么做后，必须完成一次长休才能再次进行。但是你也可以通过消费一个至少 1环的法术位来制造炮台。你一次只能有一个炮台，当你的炮台已经被制造时，你不能再制造一个炮台。</p>\n<p>　　无论炮台有多大，它都是魔法物件。它的 ac是 18，生命值是你奇械师等级的 5倍。它对毒素伤害、心灵伤害和所有状态都免疫。如果它被迫进行属性检定或豁免检定，则将其所有属性都视为 10(+0)。如果对炮台施展@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.2LREP2D10afC4Y3V]{修复术}，它将恢复[[/r 2d6]]生命值。炮台在生命值降低到 0 或者 1 小时后消失。你能够以一个动作来提早让它消失。</p>\n<p>　　当你制造炮台时，你可以决定它的外观以及是否有腿，并且需要从奥能炮台列表中选择它的类型。在你的每个回合中，只要你离炮台不到 60 尺，就能以一个附赠动作来激活炮台。作为同一动作的一部分，你可以引导有腿的炮台步行或攀爬到 15 尺内的一个未占用的空间中。</p>\n<p><strong>奥能炮台</strong></p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>炮台</th>\n<th>描述</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.Lrza2kTrMaxpVtAn]{投火机}</td>\n<td>炮台在你指定的一个 15 尺锥形范围内发射火焰。该区域内的每个生物必须对你的法术豁免 DC 做一次敏捷豁免检定，如果豁免失败则受到[[/r 2d8]]火焰伤害，成功的豁免检定将使伤害减半。火焰会点燃该地区内任何未被穿戴或携带的易燃物品。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.OdvtbOfnUru8HxOx]{力场弩炮}</td>\n<td>对一个距离炮台 120 尺以内的生物或物体进行远程法术攻击。击中时，目标受到[[/r 2d8]]力场伤害，如果目标是一个生物，它将向远离炮台的方向推开 5 尺。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.kpdFpp8QYwoOCnig]{防御者}</td>\n<td>炮台释放出一股正能量，给予它自己和 10 尺距离内每个你选择的生物[[/r 1d8]]+ 你智力调整值的临时生命值（最低 +1 ）。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"space"},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魔炮师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yeMhKp4bjF7K2T52","name":"误导 Misdirection","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_BeastSoothe.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         从13级起，你的急才有时候能让另一个生物代替你承受攻击。每当你成为一次攻击的目标，并且在你的5尺距离内有生物为你对抗这次攻击提供了掩蔽，你可以使用你的反应将这次攻击的目标转移给这个生物。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"spec","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"策士等级 13","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yeqpLzvtDcAw6UBm","name":"念刃Psychic Blades","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_demonhunter_soulcleave3.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>　　你能将自己的心灵异能塑造为由灵能构成的闪亮刀刃。当你准备对一个生物进行近战或远程武器攻击时，你能以空闲的手中塑造灵能之刃，并使用它来进行攻击。念刃是一种简易近战武器，具有灵巧和投掷特性。它的常规射程为60尺，没有最大射程，在命中后造成[[/r 1d6]]+你用于攻击的属性调整值的心灵伤害。念刃会在击中或未击中目标后立即消失，如果它造成伤害，其伤害不会在目标上留下痕迹。</p>\n<p>　　当你使用念刃攻击后，只要你的另一只手空闲，就能以一个附赠动作塑造第二把念刃再进行一次近战或远程武器攻击。此附赠攻击的伤害骰是[[/r 1d4]]，而不是[[/r 1d6]]。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d6+@mod","psychic"]],"versatile":"1d4+@mod"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"魂刃等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ynHB1r1UmBgTYP2t","name":"雷霆战拳 Thunder Gauntlets","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/images/gloves_s01.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>每一只装甲附带的手套在没有持握任何物品时皆可被视为一件简单近战武器，命中后会造成[[/r 1d8]]雷鸣伤害。被战拳击中的生物，会被装甲释放的魔法性干扰脉冲影响，使其对除你之外的目标攻击时有劣势，直到你的下个回合到来。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8","thunder"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"装甲师等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yud3aTvGQY7OsCsx","name":"额外攻击 Extra Attack（TCE）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/INV_Weapon_Shortblade_37.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你在自己回合执行&ldquo;攻击&rdquo;动作时可以发动两次攻击而非一次攻击。此外，你还可以施展一个戏法以替代其中一次攻击。</p>\n<p>（*众所周知的歧义。不过根据译者的理解，原文指的应该是只能替换一次，且仅能替换法师戏法。）</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":"","long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"剑咏者等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"z7ImpZVtgqAgUsO5","name":"战斗风格：受祝福的勇士","type":"feat","img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/light_05.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>　　你从@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.spell-table.eBGgxFH3n6PcbtjG]{牧师法术列表}中选择两种戏法习得。这些戏法对你来说是圣武士法术，这些戏法的施法关键属性是魅力。当你提升此职业的等级时，你能够将一个已知戏法替换为牧师法术列表中的另一个戏法。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":"","long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"圣武士等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"zAUzDT6vLeJjvnUT","name":"专用武器Dedicated Weapon","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Monk_Sparring.png","data":{"description":{"value":"\n<p>你训练自己使用各种武器作为武僧武器，而不仅仅是简易近战武器和短剑。每当你完成短休或长休时，可以碰触一件武器，将气集中在它之中，然后该武器就视为武僧武器，直到你再次使用这个能力。</p>\n<p>所选武器必须符合以下标准：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>武器必须是简易武器或军用武器。</li>\n<li>你必须拥有其熟练项。</li>\n<li>不能拥有重型或特殊属性。</li>\n</ul>\n","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"武僧等级 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"zJRRsdKNnidyjqQD","name":"狩猎开始 Slayer's Prey","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Hunter_SniperTraining.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         3级起，你能够专注于你的一名敌人，来增加你对它的伤害。以一个附赠动作，你选择一名60尺范围内对你可见角色作为该特性的目标。每回合你以一次武器攻击第一次击中该目标，它额外受到[[/r 1d6]]的武器伤害。</p>\n<p>         该收益持续到你完成一次短休或者长休。如果你选择一名不同的目标，它会提前结束。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d6",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"怪物杀手等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"zOSOTnM4IZ7DmLmY","name":"人剑合一 One with the Blade","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Ability_Rogue_Waylay.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>在6级时，能将“气”灌注到剑圣武器之中，这为你带来以下好处：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong> 剑气。</strong>在克服对非魔法攻击和伤害的抗性和免疫能力时，你以剑圣武器所进行的攻击被视作魔法攻击。</li>\n<li><strong> 巧劲。</strong>当你使用剑圣武器命中目标时，你可以消耗1点“气”使得该武器对该目标造成额外伤害，数值等于你的“武艺”投骰 。 该特性你每回合只能使用一次。</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d((floor((@classes.monk.levels+1)/6))*2+4)",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"剑圣宗等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"zQWK8f7vSXGh4fp4","name":"雾行漫游 Misty Wanderer","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_ardenweald_monk.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以在眨眼之间穿梭妖精荒原以进行移动：你可以施展@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Cnzcy1Tu7gt6xYHm]{迷踪步}而不需要消耗法术位。你可以这么做的次数等于你的感知调整值(最低一次)，你在完成一次长休后重获所有的使用次数。另外，每当你施展迷踪步时，你可以携带一个五尺以内你看得见的自愿生物与你一起移动。那个生物会被传送到由你选择的，位于你的目标位置五尺以内的未被占据空间。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"max(@abilities.wis.mod,1)","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"妖精漫游者等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"zWcXri77krJizuaE","name":"灵魂投射Spirit Projection","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_venthyr_doorofshadows.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你的灵魂能脱离你物理形态的约束。作为一个动作，你可以从你的身体投射出你的灵魂。你脱离的身体陷入昏迷，并处于人事不省状态。</p>\n<p>你的灵魂与你的常人形态各个方面高度相似，复制你的游戏数据，但不包括你的携带物。任何对你的灵魂或物理身体造成的伤害或其他效果会传递到另一方。你的灵魂可以在你的身体之外停留长达1小时，或者直到你的专注中断（就像专注于一个法术）。当你的投射结束时，你的灵魂会回到你的身体，或者你的身体会魔法地的传送到你灵魂所在的空间（取决于你的选择）。</p>\n<p>当投射你的灵魂时，你获得以下好处。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>你的灵魂和身体获得对钝击、穿刺和挥砍伤害的抗性。</li>\n<li>当你施放一个咒法学派或死灵学派的法术时，该法术不需要语言、姿势或不消耗金币的材料成分。</li>\n<li>你获得等于你步行速度的飞行速度，并且可以盘旋。你可以穿过生物和物体，就像它们是困难地形一样，但如果你在生物或物件内结束自己回合，你会受到[[/r 1d10]]的力场伤害。</li>\n<li>当你使用@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.39YlsyoJXTtDSGf4]{战栗形态}时，在你的每个回合中只有一次，当你对一个生物造成暗蚀伤害时，你会恢复相当于暗蚀伤害量一半的生命值。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>一旦你使用了这个特性，你就不能再这样做，直到你完成了一次长休。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"VRGR","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"死灵宗主等级 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"IQE6hAV3ygaTICtD":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.QDdiLinrHSTLMFya"}}}
{"_id":"zuBT4TqrEvO2Tanv","name":"撕裂心智Rend Mind","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_demonhunter_soulcleave2.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>　　你能让你的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.yeqpLzvtDcAw6UBm]{念刃}直接切削一个生物的心智。当你使用念刃对一个生物造成@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.class-abilityphb.AlFAC3Lz1ud2ry9T]{偷袭}伤害时，你能迫使其进行一次感知豁免检定（DC=8+你的熟练加值+你的敏捷调整值）。若豁免失败，目标将在一分钟里前陷入震慑。被震慑的目标可以在他的回合结束时重复豁免，如果成功将会移除这个效果在他身上的影响</p>\n<p>　　一旦你使用了此特性，除非你消耗3个灵能骰否则将无法再次使用，直到你完成一次长休。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"dex"},"requirements":"魂刃等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"noPzCDRAbqNUFwC7","name":"雄辩学院 College of Eloquence（MOT）","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/Spell_Holy_DivineHymn.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>         雄辩学院的追随者们掌握辩论的艺术。游说被认为是一种高等的艺术，一个经过充分论证、口齿伶俐的论点往往比事实更具说服力。这些吟游诗人将逻辑和戏剧性的语言结合在一起，运用逻辑论证战胜怀疑者与批评者，同时拨动观众的心弦并引领他们的情绪。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"MOT","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"吟游诗人等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}}}
