{"name":"龙兽伙伴Drake Companion","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/inv_salamanderwaterbaby_orange.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>使用一个动作，你能魔法地召唤与你联结的@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.monsterspack.S1jWOb9Mcj0rmrjz]{龙兽}。龙兽会出现在你<span>30</span>尺内一处由你选择的未被占据的空间里。<span><br /><br /></span>龙兽听从你的指令，并且对你和你的同伴友善。从龙兽伙伴数据卡中查看龙兽的游戏数据，其中有几处使用了你的熟练值（<span>PB</span>）。当你召唤龙兽时，从龙族精粹特性的列表中选择伤害类型。你能自订龙兽的外观特征，如颜色，鳞片纹理，和龙族精粹的视觉效果；你的外观选择对游戏数据没有影响。<span><br /><br /></span>战斗中，龙兽与你共享先攻，会在你的回合结束之后立即进行自己的回合。龙兽能自己独自移动和使用反应动作，除非你在你的回合里使用附赠动作命令龙兽执行一个动作，否则龙兽只会使用回避动作。执行的动作可以是数据卡上的，也可以是其他的。当你失能时，龙兽能独自进行任何动作选项，而不是只能回避。<span><br /><br /></span>龙兽持续直到它的生命值降为<span>0</span>，或你使用本特性召唤另一只龙兽，或你死亡。当龙兽消失时，它穿戴和携带的物品会留在原地。<span><br /><br /></span>当你召唤龙兽后，你需要完成一次长休才能再次这样做。你也能使用一个一环或更高的法术位来召唤龙兽。<span><br /></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 style=\"border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-underline-header)\"><span>龙兽伙伴Drake Companion</span></h2>\n<p>小型龙<span><br /></span><strong>护甲等级</strong><span> 14+PB</span>（天生护甲）<span><br /></span><strong>生命值</strong><span> 5+</span>你游侠等级<span>*5</span>（龙兽有与你游侠等级相同数量的<span>d10</span>生命骰）<span><br /></span><strong>速度</strong><span> 40</span>尺</p>\n<div><hr style=\"border-top:1px solid var(--color-border-light-primary);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border-light-highlight)\" /></div>\n<p>力量<span>16</span>（<span>+3</span>） 敏捷<span>12</span>（<span>+1</span>） 体质<span>15</span>（<span>+2</span>）<span><br /></span>智力<span>8</span>（<span>-1</span>）<span>  </span>感知<span>14</span>（<span>+2</span>） 魅力<span>8</span>（<span>-1</span>）</p>\n<div><hr style=\"border-top:1px solid var(--color-border-light-primary);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border-light-highlight)\" /></div>\n<p><strong>豁免</strong> 敏捷<span>+1+PB  </span>感知<span>+2+PB<br /></span><strong>伤害免疫</strong> 由龙族精粹特性决定<span><br /></span><strong>感官</strong> 黑暗视觉<span>40</span>尺 被动感知<span>12<br /></span><strong>语言</strong> 龙语<span><br /></span><strong>挑战等级<span>–</span>熟练值（<span>PB</span>）</strong>与你熟练值相同<span><br /><br /></span><strong>龙族精粹<span>Draconic Essence</span>。</strong>当你召唤龙兽时，选择一种伤害类型<span>:</span>强酸，寒冷，闪电，火焰，毒性。该伤害类型会影响伤害免疫和注能打击的伤害。</p>\n<div><hr style=\"border-top:1px solid var(--color-border-light-primary);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border-light-highlight)\" /></div>\n<h3>动作</h3>\n<p><strong>啃咬<span>Bite</span>。</strong>近战武器攻击<span>:</span>命中<span>+3+PB</span>，触及<span>5</span>尺，单一目标，伤害<span>:1d6+PB</span>穿刺伤害。</p>\n<div><hr style=\"border-top:1px solid var(--color-border-light-primary);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border-light-highlight)\" /></div>\n<h3>反应<span><br /></span></h3>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>注能打击<span>Infused Strikes</span>。</strong>当龙兽<span>30</span>尺内一个龙兽可见的生物用武器攻击命中一个生物时，龙兽能用它的精粹注能本次打击，使目标额外受到<span>d6</span>伤害，伤害类型与龙族精粹相同。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"FTD","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"当你召唤龙兽后，你需要完成一次长休才能再次这样做。你也能使用一个一环或更高的法术位来召唤龙兽。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"龙兽守卫等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"O8xZpxv5LtjyqFrE":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.0MMEa2Ks0eC5Gvs9"},"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"_id":"WwDrnmKdKk2ZRJtX"}
{"name":"龙兽吐息Drake’s Breath","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_evoker_oppressingroar2.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>使用一个动作，你能喷吐<span>30</span>尺锥形的伤害吐息，或者你也能将喷射起点设为你的龙兽。选择强酸，寒冷，闪电，火焰，或毒性伤害。（你的选择和龙族精粹特性无关。）锥形范围内的生物进行一次敏捷豁免对抗你的法术<span>DC</span>，豁免失败时受到<span>8d6</span>伤害，成功时受到一半的伤害。<span><br /><br /></span>当你<span>15</span>级时，伤害增长到<span>10d6</span>。<span><br /><br /></span>当你使用本特性后，你需要完成一次长休才能再次这样做。你也能使用一个三环或更高的法术位来再次使用。<span><br /></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"FTD","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"当你使用本特性后，你需要完成一次长休才能再次这样做。你也能使用一个三环或更高的法术位来再次使用。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"cone"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["8d6",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"龙兽守卫等级 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"O8xZpxv5LtjyqFrE":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.DcQOhZPhVZbslq9W"},"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"_id":"DzvyvtxhhUM3DEqZ"}
{"name":"完美联结Perfected Bond","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_racial_visage.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你与龙兽的联结抵达其力量的巅峰。当召唤的龙兽在场时，你和龙兽获得以下增益<span>:<br /></span></p>\n<p><strong>增强啃咬<span>Empowered Bite</span>。</strong></p>\n<p>龙兽的啃咬攻击额外造成与龙族精粹属性相同的<span>d6</span>伤害。（总共<span>2d6</span>额外伤害。）<span><br /></span></p>\n<p><strong>大型龙兽<span>Large Drake</span>。</strong></p>\n<p>你的龙兽成长为大型。当你骑乘龙兽时，使用飞行速度不再受限于牙鳞之联。<span><br /></span></p>\n<p><strong>反射抗性<span>Reflexive Resistance</span>。</strong></p>\n<p>当你与龙兽相距<span>30</span>尺内，你或你的龙兽受到伤害时，你能使用你的反应为你或你的龙兽对这次伤害提供抗性。你能使用本反应的次数与你的熟练值相等，当你完成一次长休后恢复所有的使用次数。</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"FTD","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"max(@abilities.wis.mod,1)","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"龙兽守卫等级 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"O8xZpxv5LtjyqFrE":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.zQWK8f7vSXGh4fp4"},"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"_id":"4LdeTVs2LPa1njJa"}
{"name":"龙族赠礼Draconic Gift","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_evoker_discerningeye.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>通过与你龙兽的联结，你获得与龙族之间的联系，增强你的气场，赋予你知识，你获得以下增益<span>:</span></p>\n<p><strong>奇术<span>Thaumaturgy</span>。</strong></p>\n<p>你习得戏法@Compendium[dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.9utDFSqFjS9QRpNw]{奇术}，这对你而言是一个游侠法术。</p>\n<p><strong>龙舌<span>Tongue of Dragons</span>。</strong></p>\n<p>你学会说，读，写龙语或另一门你选择的语言。<span><br /></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"FTD","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"龙兽守卫等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"O8xZpxv5LtjyqFrE":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.4sBphHebB1yIIcaO"},"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"_id":"laH2AbENhxxXtv5Q"}
{"name":"牙鳞之联Bond of Fang and Scale","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/inv_10_inscription_vantusrune_color4.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你与龙兽之间的纽带加强，激发龙兽的狂怒，为你提供保护。当你召唤龙兽时，其获得与步行速度相等的游泳速度，并且能在水里或空气中呼吸，或其获得与步行速度相等的飞行速度。（由你选择）<span><br /><br /></span>此外，当召唤的龙兽在场时，你和龙兽获得以下增益<span>:<br /></span></p>\n<p><strong>龙兽坐骑<span>Drake Mount</span>。</strong></p>\n<p>龙兽成长为中等体型。作为你特别联结的反映，你能够将龙兽当做坐骑骑乘，即使你的体型也为中型。当你骑乘龙兽时，龙兽不能使用从本特性中获得的飞行速度。<span><br /></span></p>\n<p><strong>魔法獠牙<span>Magic Fang</span>。</strong></p>\n<p>龙兽的啃咬攻击额外造成与龙族精粹伤害类型相同的<span>d6</span>伤害。<span><br /></span></p>\n<p><strong>抗性<span>Resistance</span>。</strong></p>\n<p>你获得与龙族精粹伤害类型相同的伤害抗性。<span><br /></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"FTD","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"龙兽守卫等级 7","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"O8xZpxv5LtjyqFrE":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.J3kFXzNNsl6MAAYH"},"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"_id":"0RCItmL2McA6zEJz"}
