{"name":"龙之徒 Draconic Disciple","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_evoker_masterylifebinder_bronze.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\">通过引导你的龙之气，你可以将龙息的精华注入到你的徒手打击之中并依靠你与龙的牵绊来强化自身的气势。你获得以下好处：</p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">龙之威仪。</span></strong>如果你在一次魅力（威吓）或一次魅力（游说）检定中失败，你可以显现出巨龙的威仪，并用你的反应来重骰此检定。一旦此特性将一次检定结果从失败变为成功，直到你完成一次长休息你无法再使用此特性。</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">龙之打击。</span></strong>当你以一次徒手攻击对一个目标造成伤害时，你可以将伤害类型改变为强酸，冷冻，火焰，闪电或毒素。</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">龙之言语。</span></strong>你可以说、读、写龙语或其他一种你选择的语言。  </li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ftd","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"神龙宗等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"O8xZpxv5LtjyqFrE":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.R9VbDJOCQk2Mb9eG"},"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"_id":"UflAd2LB6LVjmSN6"}
{"name":"龙之息 Breath of the Dragon","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/inv_10_enchanting2_magicswirl_bronze.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>你可以引导气来将其化为毁灭性的能量波，如同你所模仿的巨龙。当你在你的回合进行攻击动作，你可以将其中一次攻击替换为喷吐出一团<span>20</span>尺锥状或<span>30</span>尺长<span>5</span>尺宽线状（由你选择）的龙类能量。选择以下一种伤害类型：强酸，冷冻，火焰，闪电或毒素。范围内的每个生物必须通过一次对抗你的气豁免<span>DC</span>的敏捷豁免，豁免失败者将于受到等同两个你武艺骰的对应类型的伤害，豁免成功则伤害减半。</p>\n<p><span><br /></span>第<span>11</span>级时，你的吐息伤害提升到三个你的武艺骰。</p>\n<p><span><br /></span>你可以使用此特性的次数等同于你的熟练加值（<span>PB</span>），且在完成一次长休后恢复所有使用次数。当你没有使用次数时，你可以花费<span>2</span>点气来使用此特性。<span><br /></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"FTD","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":"当你在你的回合进行攻击动作；当你没有使用次数时，2点气。"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d(ceil(((@classes.monk.levels)+2)/6)*2+2)",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"神龙宗等级 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"O8xZpxv5LtjyqFrE":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.bolUalIQ1Ad2I6Mg"},"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"_id":"VAAuWjcHIfJOamhV"}
{"name":"龙翼翱翔 Wings Unfurled","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_evoker_hoverblack.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>当你使用飞檐走壁时，你可以在背后展开虚幻的龙翼，其在你回合结束时消失。当龙翼存在时，你获得与你的步行速度相同的飞行速度。</p>\n<p><span><br /></span>你可以使用此特性的次数等同于你的熟练加值，且在完成一次长休后恢复所有使用次数。<span><br /></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ftd","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":"当你使用飞檐走壁时"},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"神龙宗等级 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"O8xZpxv5LtjyqFrE":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.lu8NYi2MWNx8h6ZX"},"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"_id":"HnaSOy2vbi9f6gW8"}
{"name":"古龙姿 Aspect of the Wyrm","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_evoker_timespiral.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\">龙气力量从你体内散发，守护你的盟友并惩罚一切敢于对它们动武之徒。以一个附赠动作，你可以在你身边<span>10</span>尺内具现出一股持续<span>1</span>分钟的龙力灵光。在持续时间内，你获得以下<span>1</span>种好处：</p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">骇人威仪。</span></strong>当你散发出此灵光时，或在维持此灵光时用一个附赠动作，选择灵光范围内的一个生物。目标必须成功通过相当于你气豁免<span>DC</span>的感知豁免，否则对你恐慌<span>1</span>分钟。目标可以在每次自己回合结束时重复一次豁免，豁免成功则效应中止。</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">抗性。</span></strong>你启动此灵光时选择一种伤害类型：强酸，冷冻，火焰，闪电或毒素。你和你灵光内的盟友对所选伤害类型具有抗性。</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">一旦你散发出此灵光，直到你完成一次长休你都无法再这么做，除非你花费<span>3</span>点气来再次使用它。<span><br /></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ftd","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":10,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"神龙宗等级 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"O8xZpxv5LtjyqFrE":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.5XXA79JOX0zakWef"},"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"_id":"zYjrQpr51HKryzCY"}
{"name":"神龙身 Ascendant Aspect","type":"feat","img":"modules/dnd5e_classpack/Nicons/ability_evoker_blessingofthebronze.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\">你的龙之魂巅峰造极。你获得以下好处：</p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">强化吐息。</span></strong>当你使用你的龙之息时，你可以消耗<span>1</span>点气对其塑形并增强其威力。你呼出的龙类能量增长至<span>60</span>尺锥状或<span>90</span>尺长<span>5</span>尺宽线状（由你选择），且范围内的每个生物豁免失败时会受到等同四个你武艺骰的对应类型的伤害，豁免成功则伤害减半。</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">盲视。</span></strong>你获得<span>10</span>尺盲视。在盲视范围内，即使你目盲或处于黑暗中，你仍可以清晰地看到任何不处于全身掩护的事物。而且，你可以在盲视范围内看到隐形生物，除非此生物对你躲藏成功。</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">怒气爆发。</span></strong>当你使用古龙之姿时，龙族之怒从你体内爆发。选择你灵光内可见的任意数量的生物，<span class=\"bbccolor\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:red;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">每个生物必须通过一次对抗你的气豁免<span>DC</span>的敏捷豁免，豁免失败者</span></span>受到<span>3d10</span>强酸，冷冻，火焰，闪电或毒素伤害（由你选择）。 </li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ftd","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"神龙宗等级 17","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"attunement":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"O8xZpxv5LtjyqFrE":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.extra-ability.gDsqXKtRpltzhHLP"},"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"_id":"9Ii4jeF6MDSzL1r8"}
